  ('23936eaf-19bd-4cd0-ba57-e46e11f3e000-ex1', '23936eaf-19bd-4cd0-ba57-e46e11f3e000', 'so-called', 'The so-called shortcut took twice as long.', '所谓的捷径反而花了两倍时间。'),
  ('23936eaf-19bd-4cd0-ba57-e46e11f3e000-ex2', '23936eaf-19bd-4cd0-ba57-e46e11f3e000', 'so-called', 'The so-called voluntary code in practice bound no signatory to anything.', '这套所谓的自律准则实际上对任何签署方都没有约束力。'),
  ('6b9498b8-f7da-4446-99ce-9691e71501d5-ex1', '6b9498b8-f7da-4446-99ce-9691e71501d5', 'constant', 'The fridge makes a constant humming noise.', '冰箱发出持续的嗡嗡声。'),
  ('6b9498b8-f7da-4446-99ce-9691e71501d5-ex2', '6b9498b8-f7da-4446-99ce-9691e71501d5', 'constant', 'Constant vigilance by supervisors is the price of systemic stability.', '监管者的时刻警惕是系统稳定的代价。'),
  ('8da7c9ba-2bd7-422a-96b4-51704acf3523-ex1', '8da7c9ba-2bd7-422a-96b4-51704acf3523', 'clinic', 'The clinic opens at eight.', '诊所八点开门。'),
  ('8da7c9ba-2bd7-422a-96b4-51704acf3523-ex2', '8da7c9ba-2bd7-422a-96b4-51704acf3523', 'clinic', 'The mobile clinics extend primary care to chronically underserved districts.', '流动诊所将初级医疗服务延伸到长期缺医的地区。'),
  ('0c49ec7a-501a-4da3-a423-ccee2ff0db29-ex1', '0c49ec7a-501a-4da3-a423-ccee2ff0db29', 'veteran', 'My grandfather is a war veteran.', '我祖父是一名战争老兵。'),
  ('0c49ec7a-501a-4da3-a423-ccee2ff0db29-ex2', '0c49ec7a-501a-4da3-a423-ccee2ff0db29', 'veteran', 'The statute guarantees veterans preferential consideration in public employment.', '该法规保障退伍军人在公共就业中获得优先考虑。'),
  ('c4a6102a-1efe-44b4-b3c4-debd86601e9e-ex1', 'c4a6102a-1efe-44b4-b3c4-debd86601e9e', 'smell', 'I love the smell of fresh bread.', '我喜欢新鲜面包的香味。'),
  ('c4a6102a-1efe-44b4-b3c4-debd86601e9e-ex2', 'c4a6102a-1efe-44b4-b3c4-debd86601e9e', 'smell', 'The transactions carried the unmistakable smell of coordinated manipulation.', '这些交易带有明显的协同操纵的味道。'),
  ('7e45a90b-9eef-417c-970e-399063e16caa-ex1', '7e45a90b-9eef-417c-970e-399063e16caa', 'tablespoon', 'Add a tablespoon of sugar to the mix.', '在混合物中加一汤匙糖。'),
  ('7e45a90b-9eef-417c-970e-399063e16caa-ex2', '7e45a90b-9eef-417c-970e-399063e16caa', 'tablespoon', 'The labeling standard defines a tablespoon by precise metric volume.', '标签标准以精确的公制容量定义汤匙这一计量单位。'),
  ('5f9c471f-3232-4634-ab93-ddb0557c2d0e-ex1', '5f9c471f-3232-4634-ab93-ddb0557c2d0e', 'capable', 'She is capable of solving hard problems.', '她有能力解决难题。'),
  ('5f9c471f-3232-4634-ab93-ddb0557c2d0e-ex2', '5f9c471f-3232-4634-ab93-ddb0557c2d0e', 'capable', 'Only institutions capable of absorbing severe losses may underwrite such exposures.', '只有能够吸收重大损失的机构才可承接此类风险敞口。'),
  ('01cb3a56-2d2a-41cd-b7c0-ec533f1b320e-ex1', '01cb3a56-2d2a-41cd-b7c0-ec533f1b320e', 'nervous', 'I was nervous before the interview.', '面试前我很紧张。'),
  ('01cb3a56-2d2a-41cd-b7c0-ec533f1b320e-ex2', '01cb3a56-2d2a-41cd-b7c0-ec533f1b320e', 'nervous', 'Nervous markets amplified the disclosure into a full-fledged confidence crisis.', '紧张的市场把这次披露放大成一场全面的信心危机。'),
  ('16bd6080-5566-47f5-88be-819f67c8cda8-ex1', '16bd6080-5566-47f5-88be-819f67c8cda8', 'tourist', 'The city attracts millions of tourists.', '这座城市吸引了数百万游客。'),
  ('16bd6080-5566-47f5-88be-819f67c8cda8-ex2', '16bd6080-5566-47f5-88be-819f67c8cda8', 'tourist', 'The tourist levy funds conservation of the heritage sites visitors frequent.', '旅游税为游客常去的遗产地保护提供资金。'),
  ('faa2d669-87b1-4994-a9e3-e5414aa4a360-ex1', 'faa2d669-87b1-4994-a9e3-e5414aa4a360', 'toss', 'Toss the salad before serving.', '上菜前把沙拉拌一拌。'),
  ('faa2d669-87b1-4994-a9e3-e5414aa4a360-ex2', 'faa2d669-87b1-4994-a9e3-e5414aa4a360', 'toss', 'The court declined to toss the claims at the preliminary stage.', '法院拒绝在初步阶段驳回这些诉求。'),
  ('2a095abd-1f7d-485e-8fcd-47739ffc4353-ex1', '2a095abd-1f7d-485e-8fcd-47739ffc4353', 'crucial', 'Sleep is crucial for good health.', '睡眠对健康至关重要。'),
  ('2a095abd-1f7d-485e-8fcd-47739ffc4353-ex2', '2a095abd-1f7d-485e-8fcd-47739ffc4353', 'crucial', 'The crucial question is whether the safeguards operated as designed.', '关键问题在于这些保障措施是否按设计运作。'),
  ('07a73fd0-31af-493e-bc8a-f3b76bfc4d15-ex1', '07a73fd0-31af-493e-bc8a-f3b76bfc4d15', 'bury', 'The dog buried its bone in the garden.', '狗把骨头埋在了花园里。'),
  ('07a73fd0-31af-493e-bc8a-f3b76bfc4d15-ex2', '07a73fd0-31af-493e-bc8a-f3b76bfc4d15', 'bury', 'The disclosures were buried in footnotes no ordinary reader would locate.', '这些披露被埋在普通读者根本找不到的脚注里。'),
  ('8373811b-bb5a-4c43-9b4f-052c7b3f351b-ex1', '8373811b-bb5a-4c43-9b4f-052c7b3f351b', 'pray', 'They pray together before meals.', '他们饭前一起祷告。'),
  ('8373811b-bb5a-4c43-9b4f-052c7b3f351b-ex2', '8373811b-bb5a-4c43-9b4f-052c7b3f351b', 'pray', 'The petitioners pray for relief in the form of declaratory judgment.', '请愿人请求以确认判决的形式给予救济。'),
  ('dd6c9075-2d95-41d5-a23d-7058bfdc877f-ex1', 'dd6c9075-2d95-41d5-a23d-7058bfdc877f', 'tomato', 'Add fresh tomatoes to the salad.', '在沙拉里加新鲜番茄。'),
  ('dd6c9075-2d95-41d5-a23d-7058bfdc877f-ex2', 'dd6c9075-2d95-41d5-a23d-7058bfdc877f', 'tomato', 'The tomato import quotas became the flashpoint of the trade negotiation.', '番茄进口配额成了贸易谈判的引爆点。'),
  ('aadaa9d4-c04a-464d-835a-1020d0a24ad6-ex1', 'aadaa9d4-c04a-464d-835a-1020d0a24ad6', 'exception', 'Everyone came, without exception.', '所有人无一例外都来了。'),
  ('aadaa9d4-c04a-464d-835a-1020d0a24ad6-ex2', 'aadaa9d4-c04a-464d-835a-1020d0a24ad6', 'exception', 'The exception is construed narrowly lest it swallow the general rule.', '该例外条款须从严解释，以免架空一般规则。'),
  ('8d6b720d-5412-4a77-880c-243b60149343-ex1', '8d6b720d-5412-4a77-880c-243b60149343', 'butter', 'Spread some butter on the toast.', '在吐司上抹点黄油。'),
  ('8d6b720d-5412-4a77-880c-243b60149343-ex2', '8d6b720d-5412-4a77-880c-243b60149343', 'butter', 'The dairy tariffs raised butter prices across the import-dependent markets.', '乳制品关税推高了依赖进口市场的黄油价格。'),
  ('ea170865-d030-4e1c-bb60-bd61638ee573-ex1', 'ea170865-d030-4e1c-bb60-bd61638ee573', 'deficit', 'The team overcame a two-goal deficit.', '球队扳回了两球的落后。'),
  ('ea170865-d030-4e1c-bb60-bd61638ee573-ex2', 'ea170865-d030-4e1c-bb60-bd61638ee573', 'deficit', 'The structural deficit persists even at full employment output levels.', '即使在充分就业的产出水平下，结构性赤字依然存在。'),
  ('88fe63a0-eaa7-4cca-ad55-9c1aa640b12b-ex1', '88fe63a0-eaa7-4cca-ad55-9c1aa640b12b', 'bathroom', 'The bathroom is down the hall.', '卫生间在走廊尽头。'),
  ('88fe63a0-eaa7-4cca-ad55-9c1aa640b12b-ex2', '88fe63a0-eaa7-4cca-ad55-9c1aa640b12b', 'bathroom', 'The accessibility code mandates compliant bathrooms in all public buildings.', '无障碍规范要求所有公共建筑配备合规的卫生间。'),
  ('58e4d3eb-fe53-464c-ae2c-3648bcfd8eff-ex1', '58e4d3eb-fe53-464c-ae2c-3648bcfd8eff', 'objective', 'My objective is to finish by Friday.', '我的目标是周五前完成。'),
  ('58e4d3eb-fe53-464c-ae2c-3648bcfd8eff-ex2', '58e4d3eb-fe53-464c-ae2c-3648bcfd8eff', 'objective', 'The tribunal applies an objective standard divorced from the parties'' subjective intent.', '法庭适用脱离当事人主观意图的客观标准。'),
  ('5bddde31-f336-4911-bf79-93a83d6c29ec-ex1', '5bddde31-f336-4911-bf79-93a83d6c29ec', 'electronic', 'Please turn off electronic devices.', '请关闭电子设备。'),
  ('5bddde31-f336-4911-bf79-93a83d6c29ec-ex2', '5bddde31-f336-4911-bf79-93a83d6c29ec', 'electronic', 'Electronic signatures carry full legal effect under the commerce act.', '根据商务法，电子签名具有完全的法律效力。'),
  ('c266cd9f-c22c-4995-b3aa-d56cac2690dc-ex1', 'c266cd9f-c22c-4995-b3aa-d56cac2690dc', 'ally', 'She is my closest ally at work.', '她是我工作中最亲密的盟友。'),
  ('c266cd9f-c22c-4995-b3aa-d56cac2690dc-ex2', 'c266cd9f-c22c-4995-b3aa-d56cac2690dc', 'ally', 'Treaty allies are bound to mutual defense upon armed attack.', '条约盟国在遭受武装攻击时负有共同防御义务。'),
  ('2cf24420-fe3d-4dfb-95dc-8ef12407603d-ex1', '2cf24420-fe3d-4dfb-95dc-8ef12407603d', 'journey', 'The journey takes three hours by train.', '坐火车要三个小时的路程。'),
  ('2cf24420-fe3d-4dfb-95dc-8ef12407603d-ex2', '2cf24420-fe3d-4dfb-95dc-8ef12407603d', 'journey', 'The legislation completed its journey through both chambers without amendment.', '该立法未经修改便走完了两院的全部立法程序。'),
  ('3973d308-d829-41dc-a043-bb0e31964639-ex1', '3973d308-d829-41dc-a043-bb0e31964639', 'reputation', 'The restaurant has a good reputation.', '这家餐厅口碑很好。'),
  ('3973d308-d829-41dc-a043-bb0e31964639-ex2', '3973d308-d829-41dc-a043-bb0e31964639', 'reputation', 'Reputational sanctions often bite harder than formal regulatory penalties.', '声誉制裁的杀伤力往往比正式监管处罚更大。'),
  ('3ce89ced-b5b7-4d56-a9a5-6b9b3473482b-ex1', '3ce89ced-b5b7-4d56-a9a5-6b9b3473482b', 'mixture', 'Pour the mixture into the pan.', '把混合物倒进锅里。'),
  ('3ce89ced-b5b7-4d56-a9a5-6b9b3473482b-ex2', '3ce89ced-b5b7-4d56-a9a5-6b9b3473482b', 'mixture', 'The policy is a mixture of mandates and incentives calibrated by sector.', '该政策是按行业调配的强制要求与激励措施的混合体。'),
  ('b0a107dc-0858-41a4-acff-9835be7c61f3-ex1', 'b0a107dc-0858-41a4-acff-9835be7c61f3', 'surely', 'Surely you don''t believe that story!', '你肯定不会相信那个故事吧！'),
  ('b0a107dc-0858-41a4-acff-9835be7c61f3-ex2', 'b0a107dc-0858-41a4-acff-9835be7c61f3', 'surely', 'Surely the drafters did not intend the exemption to extend so far.', '起草者想必无意让该豁免延伸至如此程度。'),
  ('7629a83b-0805-49b1-a4bd-c3834c27f34c-ex1', '7629a83b-0805-49b1-a4bd-c3834c27f34c', 'tower', 'The tower offers a view of the whole city.', '从塔上可以俯瞰全城。'),
  ('7629a83b-0805-49b1-a4bd-c3834c27f34c-ex2', '7629a83b-0805-49b1-a4bd-c3834c27f34c', 'tower', 'The transmission towers required easements negotiated with hundreds of landowners.', '输电塔需要与数百名土地所有者协商地役权。'),
  ('7c50d863-1f68-434d-ac53-083cadd70808-ex1', '7c50d863-1f68-434d-ac53-083cadd70808', 'smoke', 'There is no smoking in the building.', '楼内禁止吸烟。'),
  ('7c50d863-1f68-434d-ac53-083cadd70808-ex2', '7c50d863-1f68-434d-ac53-083cadd70808', 'smoke', 'The disclosures were dismissed as smoke obscuring the underlying solvency.', '这些披露被斥为掩盖实际偿付能力的烟幕。'),
  ('a4b9ad45-b07f-4f57-ac84-dc20cea28d48-ex1', 'a4b9ad45-b07f-4f57-ac84-dc20cea28d48', 'confront', 'You need to confront your fears.', '你需要直面自己的恐惧。'),
  ('a4b9ad45-b07f-4f57-ac84-dc20cea28d48-ex2', 'a4b9ad45-b07f-4f57-ac84-dc20cea28d48', 'confront', 'The accused enjoys the right to confront adverse witnesses at trial.', '被告人享有在庭审中与不利证人对质的权利。'),
  ('dc269431-8b16-43df-b995-b9858b5525f0-ex1', 'dc269431-8b16-43df-b995-b9858b5525f0', 'pure', 'The mountain air is pure and fresh.', '山里的空气纯净清新。'),
  ('dc269431-8b16-43df-b995-b9858b5525f0-ex2', 'dc269431-8b16-43df-b995-b9858b5525f0', 'pure', 'The certification attests that the product is pure within prescribed tolerances.', '该认证证明产品纯度在规定容差范围之内。'),
  ('56b44d01-4609-415e-a9d7-68c584243221-ex1', '56b44d01-4609-415e-a9d7-68c584243221', 'glance', 'She gave me a quick glance.', '她飞快地瞥了我一眼。'),
  ('56b44d01-4609-415e-a9d7-68c584243221-ex2', '56b44d01-4609-415e-a9d7-68c584243221', 'glance', 'Even a cursory glance at the accounts revealed the misclassification.', '哪怕粗略一瞥账目，也能发现这一分类错误。'),
  ('d7c5c8d5-ece6-4534-b30c-e05a79ea2712-ex1', 'd7c5c8d5-ece6-4534-b30c-e05a79ea2712', 'dimension', 'Measure the dimensions of the room.', '量一下房间的尺寸。'),
  ('d7c5c8d5-ece6-4534-b30c-e05a79ea2712-ex2', 'd7c5c8d5-ece6-4534-b30c-e05a79ea2712', 'dimension', 'The dispute acquired a constitutional dimension once fundamental rights were invoked.', '一经援引基本权利，这场争端便具有了宪法层面的意义。'),
  ('084d6591-1b40-4cc1-945b-d41586152f3f-ex1', '084d6591-1b40-4cc1-945b-d41586152f3f', 'toy', 'The baby loves her new toy.', '宝宝很喜欢她的新玩具。'),
  ('084d6591-1b40-4cc1-945b-d41586152f3f-ex2', '084d6591-1b40-4cc1-945b-d41586152f3f', 'toy', 'The safety recall covered every toy containing the prohibited plasticizer.', '安全召回涵盖了所有含违禁增塑剂的玩具。'),
  ('67dc44a3-f83f-408b-97d2-8c7cbbaa00ba-ex1', '67dc44a3-f83f-408b-97d2-8c7cbbaa00ba', 'prisoner', 'The prisoner was released after five years.', '那名囚犯五年后获释。'),
  ('67dc44a3-f83f-408b-97d2-8c7cbbaa00ba-ex2', '67dc44a3-f83f-408b-97d2-8c7cbbaa00ba', 'prisoner', 'Every prisoner retains rights that incarceration does not extinguish.', '每名在押人员仍保有不因监禁而消灭的权利。'),
  ('62ae6bea-deb2-4ab3-b084-21470d628850-ex1', '62ae6bea-deb2-4ab3-b084-21470d628850', 'fellow', 'He is a friendly fellow.', '他是个友善的人。'),
  ('62ae6bea-deb2-4ab3-b084-21470d628850-ex2', '62ae6bea-deb2-4ab3-b084-21470d628850', 'fellow', 'The research fellow holds a appointment funded by the endowed chair.', '这位研究员的职位由捐赠教席资助。'),
  ('e52ee35a-9d6f-4df8-a542-0410a6a82ee5-ex1', 'e52ee35a-9d6f-4df8-a542-0410a6a82ee5', 'smooth', 'The road is smooth and easy to drive.', '这条路平坦好开。'),
  ('e52ee35a-9d6f-4df8-a542-0410a6a82ee5-ex2', 'e52ee35a-9d6f-4df8-a542-0410a6a82ee5', 'smooth', 'The transition proved remarkably smooth owing to meticulous contingency planning.', '由于周密的应急规划，过渡进行得异常顺利。'),
  ('63b78b24-f560-479d-8803-0821e2aef716-ex1', '63b78b24-f560-479d-8803-0821e2aef716', 'nearby', 'There is a park nearby.', '附近有个公园。'),
  ('63b78b24-f560-479d-8803-0821e2aef716-ex2', '63b78b24-f560-479d-8803-0821e2aef716', 'nearby', 'Residents of nearby parcels enjoy standing to challenge the rezoning.', '邻近地块的居民有权对重新规划提出异议。'),
  ('332f7312-89ed-4f70-9cc0-6bc2754edc87-ex1', '332f7312-89ed-4f70-9cc0-6bc2754edc87', 'peer', 'Teenagers care about peer opinions.', '青少年在意同伴的看法。'),
  ('332f7312-89ed-4f70-9cc0-6bc2754edc87-ex2', '332f7312-89ed-4f70-9cc0-6bc2754edc87', 'peer', 'The findings survived rigorous peer review before publication.', '这些发现经过严格的同行评审后才得以发表。'),
  ('dc9d31bc-17eb-4db5-a359-fd8978908ac0-ex1', 'dc9d31bc-17eb-4db5-a359-fd8978908ac0', 'designer', 'The designer created a beautiful dress.', '设计师设计了一条漂亮的裙子。'),
  ('dc9d31bc-17eb-4db5-a359-fd8978908ac0-ex2', 'dc9d31bc-17eb-4db5-a359-fd8978908ac0', 'designer', 'The designer bears liability for defects inherent in the approved plans.', '设计方对获批图纸中固有的缺陷承担责任。'),
  ('e7a85185-626b-431d-b278-c6285ce0fe9f-ex1', 'e7a85185-626b-431d-b278-c6285ce0fe9f', 'personnel', 'All personnel must wear ID badges.', '所有员工必须佩戴工牌。'),
  ('e7a85185-626b-431d-b278-c6285ce0fe9f-ex2', 'e7a85185-626b-431d-b278-c6285ce0fe9f', 'personnel', 'Personnel records are shielded from disclosure absent compelling justification.', '如无充分正当理由，人事档案不得披露。'),
  ('a12f4547-7eca-4e73-bcc6-8392e6335ebf-ex1', 'a12f4547-7eca-4e73-bcc6-8392e6335ebf', 'educator', 'She is a respected educator.', '她是一位受人尊敬的教育工作者。'),
  ('a12f4547-7eca-4e73-bcc6-8392e6335ebf-ex2', 'a12f4547-7eca-4e73-bcc6-8392e6335ebf', 'educator', 'The licensure board disciplines educators for breaches of professional standards.', '执业委员会对违反职业标准的教育工作者进行惩戒。'),
  ('4194c017-0bcf-4d05-b532-fc227e5e243c-ex1', '4194c017-0bcf-4d05-b532-fc227e5e243c', 'relative', 'We visited relatives during the holiday.', '假期里我们走亲访友。'),
  ('4194c017-0bcf-4d05-b532-fc227e5e243c-ex2', '4194c017-0bcf-4d05-b532-fc227e5e243c', 'relative', 'The analysis weighs relative fault in apportioning the damages.', '该分析在分配损害赔偿时衡量相对过错。'),
  ('7ddb9c3a-ebb1-44f9-8570-18c75a68b7c9-ex1', '7ddb9c3a-ebb1-44f9-8570-18c75a68b7c9', 'immigration', 'The immigration line at the airport was long.', '机场的入境队伍排得很长。'),
  ('7ddb9c3a-ebb1-44f9-8570-18c75a68b7c9-ex2', '7ddb9c3a-ebb1-44f9-8570-18c75a68b7c9', 'immigration', 'Immigration adjudication backlogs now stretch across multiple years.', '移民案件审理积压如今已长达数年。'),
  ('2b8173f4-c29a-42c3-bc4b-f94277a905f3-ex1', '2b8173f4-c29a-42c3-bc4b-f94277a905f3', 'belt', 'He tightened his belt after the holidays.', '假期过后他勒紧了腰带。'),
  ('2b8173f4-c29a-42c3-bc4b-f94277a905f3-ex2', '2b8173f4-c29a-42c3-bc4b-f94277a905f3', 'belt', 'The green belt designation forecloses development absent exceptional circumstances.', '绿带划定排除了开发的可能，特殊情况除外。'),
  ('706cff8a-0f4e-4afb-849e-8eee5e421371-ex1', '706cff8a-0f4e-4afb-849e-8eee5e421371', 'teaspoon', 'Add half a teaspoon of salt.', '加半茶匙盐。'),
  ('706cff8a-0f4e-4afb-849e-8eee5e421371-ex2', '706cff8a-0f4e-4afb-849e-8eee5e421371', 'teaspoon', 'Dosage instructions specify a metric teaspoon to avoid administration errors.', '用药说明规定使用公制茶匙，以避免给药误差。'),
  ('80a6640d-2beb-41b3-9ff0-964aa23ea2de-ex1', '80a6640d-2beb-41b3-9ff0-964aa23ea2de', 'birthday', 'Happy birthday! Make a wish.', '生日快乐！许个愿吧。'),
  ('80a6640d-2beb-41b3-9ff0-964aa23ea2de-ex2', '80a6640d-2beb-41b3-9ff0-964aa23ea2de', 'birthday', 'The data rules restrict processing of birthdays as identifying information.', '数据规则限制将出生日期作为身份识别信息处理。'),
  ('cf15e420-9981-4e7f-b4d5-fd4268a28b24-ex1', 'cf15e420-9981-4e7f-b4d5-fd4268a28b24', 'implication', 'I don''t like the implication of your question.', '我不喜欢你这个问题的言外之意。'),
  ('cf15e420-9981-4e7f-b4d5-fd4268a28b24-ex2', 'cf15e420-9981-4e7f-b4d5-fd4268a28b24', 'implication', 'The ruling''s implications extend to every contract drafted on the standard form.', '该裁决的影响波及所有按标准格式起草的合同。'),
  ('515b96b0-ef5c-4f7b-a73e-61a3e9d8290c-ex1', '515b96b0-ef5c-4f7b-a73e-61a3e9d8290c', 'perfectly', 'The dress fits perfectly.', '这条裙子非常合身。'),
  ('515b96b0-ef5c-4f7b-a73e-61a3e9d8290c-ex2', '515b96b0-ef5c-4f7b-a73e-61a3e9d8290c', 'perfectly', 'The conduct, though perfectly lawful, raised serious ethical concerns.', '这一行为虽然完全合法，却引发了严重的伦理疑虑。'),
  ('60de9588-8934-4226-ac60-7d08f102c691-ex1', '60de9588-8934-4226-ac60-7d08f102c691', 'coast', 'We drove along the coast at sunset.', '日落时我们沿着海岸开车。'),
  ('60de9588-8934-4226-ac60-7d08f102c691-ex2', '60de9588-8934-4226-ac60-7d08f102c691', 'coast', 'The setback rules restrict construction along the eroding coast.', '退线规定限制在受侵蚀海岸沿线施工。'),
  ('535b3ef5-7145-4f13-96a4-6852f7d0c5c6-ex1', '535b3ef5-7145-4f13-96a4-6852f7d0c5c6', 'supporter', 'She is a strong supporter of the school team.', '她是校队的忠实支持者。'),
  ('535b3ef5-7145-4f13-96a4-6852f7d0c5c6-ex2', '535b3ef5-7145-4f13-96a4-6852f7d0c5c6', 'supporter', 'Even the bill''s staunchest supporters conceded its fiscal assumptions were optimistic.', '连该法案最坚定的支持者也承认其财政假设过于乐观。'),
  ('85ed57ee-ce62-4966-b26f-ed855189c834-ex1', '85ed57ee-ce62-4966-b26f-ed855189c834', 'accompany', 'Children must be accompanied by an adult.', '儿童必须由成人陪同。'),
  ('85ed57ee-ce62-4966-b26f-ed855189c834-ex2', '85ed57ee-ce62-4966-b26f-ed855189c834', 'accompany', 'Each application must be accompanied by audited financial statements.', '每份申请都必须附有经审计的财务报表。'),
  ('da8601f7-9062-4e2f-a627-57862d2264f1-ex1', 'da8601f7-9062-4e2f-a627-57862d2264f1', 'silver', 'She won the silver medal.', '她获得了银牌。'),
  ('da8601f7-9062-4e2f-a627-57862d2264f1-ex2', 'da8601f7-9062-4e2f-a627-57862d2264f1', 'silver', 'The silver market manipulation case established enduring enforcement precedents.', '白银市场操纵案确立了影响深远的执法先例。'),
  ('c524519f-0545-4edb-b13a-d475fdc151ec-ex1', 'c524519f-0545-4edb-b13a-d475fdc151ec', 'teenager', 'The teenager helps out at the shop on weekends.', '这个少年周末在店里帮忙。'),
  ('c524519f-0545-4edb-b13a-d475fdc151ec-ex2', 'c524519f-0545-4edb-b13a-d475fdc151ec', 'teenager', 'The privacy code imposes heightened duties toward teenagers online.', '隐私准则对网络平台课以对青少年的更高义务。'),
  ('e470583c-222e-4f30-b189-604164f4206e-ex1', 'e470583c-222e-4f30-b189-604164f4206e', 'recognition', 'She received recognition for her hard work.', '她的辛勤工作得到了认可。'),
  ('e470583c-222e-4f30-b189-604164f4206e-ex2', 'e470583c-222e-4f30-b189-604164f4206e', 'recognition', 'Mutual recognition of judgments underpins the regional enforcement regime.', '判决的相互承认是区域执行机制的基石。'),
  ('b1f5adb2-4173-4e8d-b9fb-c5d3d253226f-ex1', 'b1f5adb2-4173-4e8d-b9fb-c5d3d253226f', 'retirement', 'He is enjoying his retirement by the sea.', '他在海边安享退休生活。'),
  ('b1f5adb2-4173-4e8d-b9fb-c5d3d253226f-ex2', 'b1f5adb2-4173-4e8d-b9fb-c5d3d253226f', 'retirement', 'The retirement system''s unfunded liabilities dwarf the municipal budget.', '退休体系的未拨备负债远超市政预算。'),
  ('4277e08e-9c13-4320-ac74-b951f57b6cf7-ex1', '4277e08e-9c13-4320-ac74-b951f57b6cf7', 'flag', 'The flag waves in the wind.', '旗帜在风中飘扬。'),
  ('4277e08e-9c13-4320-ac74-b951f57b6cf7-ex2', '4277e08e-9c13-4320-ac74-b951f57b6cf7', 'flag', 'The compliance system failed to flag transactions matching known typologies.', '合规系统未能标记出符合已知风险特征的交易。'),
  ('54c352bd-82eb-4aa4-98bc-e961e98392d7-ex1', '54c352bd-82eb-4aa4-98bc-e961e98392d7', 'recovery', 'I wish you a quick recovery.', '祝你早日康复。'),
  ('54c352bd-82eb-4aa4-98bc-e961e98392d7-ex2', '54c352bd-82eb-4aa4-98bc-e961e98392d7', 'recovery', 'The recovery of misappropriated assets spans proceedings in four jurisdictions.', '被侵占资产的追回涉及四个司法管辖区的诉讼。'),
  ('225c4935-6155-4737-b58a-141020ebdd14-ex1', '225c4935-6155-4737-b58a-141020ebdd14', 'whisper', 'She spoke in a whisper.', '她低声说话。'),
  ('225c4935-6155-4737-b58a-141020ebdd14-ex2', '225c4935-6155-4737-b58a-141020ebdd14', 'whisper', 'Market whispers of an impending downgrade preceded the official announcement.', '在官方宣布之前，市场早有降级在即的风声。'),
  ('af677853-d31b-438a-b77f-6abb03bec13d-ex1', 'af677853-d31b-438a-b77f-6abb03bec13d', 'gentleman', 'He is a true gentleman.', '他是位真正的绅士。'),
  ('af677853-d31b-438a-b77f-6abb03bec13d-ex2', 'af677853-d31b-438a-b77f-6abb03bec13d', 'gentleman', 'The gentleman''s agreement collapsed precisely because it bound no one.', '这份君子协定恰恰因为对谁都没有约束力而瓦解。'),
  ('65984a8c-b364-4477-bbb7-4545a9cec1a5-ex1', '65984a8c-b364-4477-bbb7-4545a9cec1a5', 'corn', 'We grilled corn at the barbecue.', '烧烤时我们烤了玉米。'),
  ('65984a8c-b364-4477-bbb7-4545a9cec1a5-ex2', '65984a8c-b364-4477-bbb7-4545a9cec1a5', 'corn', 'The corn subsidies distort planting decisions across the entire belt.', '玉米补贴扭曲了整个种植带的耕种决策。'),
  ('ed726993-dc26-460d-ad51-0a8784920227-ex1', 'ed726993-dc26-460d-ad51-0a8784920227', 'moon', 'The moon is bright tonight.', '今晚月色明亮。'),
  ('ed726993-dc26-460d-ad51-0a8784920227-ex2', 'ed726993-dc26-460d-ad51-0a8784920227', 'moon', 'The treaty bars sovereign appropriation of the moon and celestial bodies.', '该条约禁止对月球及天体主张主权占有。'),
  ('0a674c2f-418b-493c-a9bc-263f1ae45fd2-ex1', '0a674c2f-418b-493c-a9bc-263f1ae45fd2', 'inner', 'The inner room is quieter.', '里间更安静。'),
  ('0a674c2f-418b-493c-a9bc-263f1ae45fd2-ex2', '0a674c2f-418b-493c-a9bc-263f1ae45fd2', 'inner', 'The inner workings of the committee remain shielded from public scrutiny.', '该委员会的内部运作仍不受公众监督。'),
  ('87735366-3fed-4dd0-9434-d22771353a08-ex1', '87735366-3fed-4dd0-9434-d22771353a08', 'junior', 'She is a junior at the university.', '她是大学三年级学生。'),
  ('87735366-3fed-4dd0-9434-d22771353a08-ex2', '87735366-3fed-4dd0-9434-d22771353a08', 'junior', 'Junior creditors absorb losses before any senior tranche is impaired.', '次级债权人先于任何优先级份额吸收损失。'),
  ('7d41404a-26d1-44f0-a106-6f4c354819d7-ex1', '7d41404a-26d1-44f0-a106-6f4c354819d7', 'throat', 'I have a sore throat today.', '我今天嗓子疼。'),
  ('7d41404a-26d1-44f0-a106-6f4c354819d7-ex2', '7d41404a-26d1-44f0-a106-6f4c354819d7', 'throat', 'The new tariffs seized the export sector by the throat.', '新关税扼住了出口行业的咽喉。'),
  ('cbbc6aa6-1e5b-4650-99f1-2678e5c81204-ex1', 'cbbc6aa6-1e5b-4650-99f1-2678e5c81204', 'salary', 'The job offers a good salary.', '这份工作薪水不错。'),
  ('cbbc6aa6-1e5b-4650-99f1-2678e5c81204-ex2', 'cbbc6aa6-1e5b-4650-99f1-2678e5c81204', 'salary', 'Executive salary disclosures are mandated for all listed issuers.', '所有上市发行人都必须披露高管薪酬。'),
  ('d4359166-4b2f-4ebc-9452-c499483793d5-ex1', 'd4359166-4b2f-4ebc-9452-c499483793d5', 'swing', 'The kids love the swing in the park.', '孩子们喜欢公园里的秋千。'),
  ('d4359166-4b2f-4ebc-9452-c499483793d5-ex2', 'd4359166-4b2f-4ebc-9452-c499483793d5', 'swing', 'A modest swing in turnout would have reversed the entire outcome.', '投票率的小幅波动就足以逆转整个选举结果。'),
  ('e764d0fd-8556-441f-98bc-25aa5dbc54ba-ex1', 'e764d0fd-8556-441f-98bc-25aa5dbc54ba', 'observer', 'He is a careful observer of nature.', '他是大自然细心的观察者。'),
  ('e764d0fd-8556-441f-98bc-25aa5dbc54ba-ex2', 'e764d0fd-8556-441f-98bc-25aa5dbc54ba', 'observer', 'Accredited observers monitored every stage of the ballot counting.', '经认证的观察员监督了计票的每一个环节。'),
  ('c0f7fae6-1124-4164-9d49-95ac817cc883-ex1', 'c0f7fae6-1124-4164-9d49-95ac817cc883', 'publication', 'The magazine is a weekly publication.', '这本杂志是周刊。'),
  ('c0f7fae6-1124-4164-9d49-95ac817cc883-ex2', 'c0f7fae6-1124-4164-9d49-95ac817cc883', 'publication', 'The injunction restrained publication pending the confidentiality appeal.', '在保密上诉审结之前，禁令禁止相关内容发表。'),
  ('3e4ae4a6-1ec5-4a6f-b5f5-837b479d37a0-ex1', '3e4ae4a6-1ec5-4a6f-b5f5-837b479d37a0', 'crop', 'The corn crop was good this year.', '今年玉米收成不错。'),
  ('3e4ae4a6-1ec5-4a6f-b5f5-837b479d37a0-ex2', '3e4ae4a6-1ec5-4a6f-b5f5-837b479d37a0', 'crop', 'Crop insurance payouts reached records following the consecutive droughts.', '连年干旱之后，农作物保险赔付创下纪录。'),
  ('61143f22-9100-4b47-8036-68df31ee4f73-ex1', '61143f22-9100-4b47-8036-68df31ee4f73', 'dig', 'The dog loves to dig in the yard.', '这只狗喜欢在院子里刨土。'),
  ('61143f22-9100-4b47-8036-68df31ee4f73-ex2', '61143f22-9100-4b47-8036-68df31ee4f73', 'dig', 'Investigators continued to dig through layers of nominee shareholdings.', '调查人员继续深挖层层代持的股权结构。'),
  ('78d20813-3774-42e2-ad11-c489c865e97a-ex1', '78d20813-3774-42e2-ad11-c489c865e97a', 'permanent', 'She got a permanent job at the bank.', '她在银行得到了一份固定工作。'),
  ('78d20813-3774-42e2-ad11-c489c865e97a-ex2', '78d20813-3774-42e2-ad11-c489c865e97a', 'permanent', 'The tribunal''s rulings form a permanent part of the jurisprudence.', '该法庭的裁决构成判例体系的永久组成部分。'),
  ('bb2b28ac-5c47-4b66-9e57-e3d53765442a-ex1', 'bb2b28ac-5c47-4b66-9e57-e3d53765442a', 'phenomenon', 'Lightning is a natural phenomenon.', '闪电是一种自然现象。'),
  ('bb2b28ac-5c47-4b66-9e57-e3d53765442a-ex2', 'bb2b28ac-5c47-4b66-9e57-e3d53765442a', 'phenomenon', 'Regulatory arbitrage is a phenomenon that harmonization alone cannot eliminate.', '监管套利是仅靠规则统一无法消除的现象。'),
  ('e2081216-ee2b-435b-9404-da0342787038-ex1', 'e2081216-ee2b-435b-9404-da0342787038', 'anxiety', 'Exercise helps reduce anxiety.', '锻炼有助于减轻焦虑。'),
  ('e2081216-ee2b-435b-9404-da0342787038-ex2', 'e2081216-ee2b-435b-9404-da0342787038', 'anxiety', 'Market anxiety deepened as the guidance was repeatedly deferred.', '随着指引一再推迟发布，市场焦虑不断加深。'),
  ('f692f56c-bedc-4f05-869e-76f4e29b9137-ex1', 'f692f56c-bedc-4f05-869e-76f4e29b9137', 'unlike', 'Unlike his brother, he is very quiet.', '和他哥哥不同，他非常安静。'),
  ('f692f56c-bedc-4f05-869e-76f4e29b9137-ex2', 'f692f56c-bedc-4f05-869e-76f4e29b9137', 'unlike', 'Unlike its predecessors, the framework carries binding enforcement provisions.', '与以往不同，该框架载有具约束力的执行条款。'),
  ('031c952c-c1b5-47aa-bdd3-6119db1682bf-ex1', '031c952c-c1b5-47aa-bdd3-6119db1682bf', 'wet', 'The grass is wet from the rain.', '草地被雨水打湿了。'),
  ('031c952c-c1b5-47aa-bdd3-6119db1682bf-ex2', '031c952c-c1b5-47aa-bdd3-6119db1682bf', 'wet', 'The wetlands designation forecloses drainage and development alike.', '湿地认定同时排除了排水和开发的可能。'),
  ('c645f931-97c9-4505-bb60-8c97c53f1b3b-ex1', 'c645f931-97c9-4505-bb60-8c97c53f1b3b', 'literally', 'I literally fell asleep at my desk.', '我真的趴在桌上睡着了。'),
  ('c645f931-97c9-4505-bb60-8c97c53f1b3b-ex2', 'c645f931-97c9-4505-bb60-8c97c53f1b3b', 'literally', 'The clause, read literally, would produce consequences the drafters cannot have intended.', '若按字面解读，该条款将产生起草者不可能有意造成的后果。'),
  ('b483b875-f3a6-45a4-86ad-12ce5713addb-ex1', 'b483b875-f3a6-45a4-86ad-12ce5713addb', 'resist', 'I can''t resist chocolate.', '我无法抗拒巧克力。'),
  ('b483b875-f3a6-45a4-86ad-12ce5713addb-ex2', 'b483b875-f3a6-45a4-86ad-12ce5713addb', 'resist', 'The agency continued to resist disclosure until compelled by court order.', '该机构一直抗拒披露，直到被法院命令强制执行。'),
  ('e7a70081-ba84-4078-bc7c-6f2f8754f49d-ex1', 'e7a70081-ba84-4078-bc7c-6f2f8754f49d', 'convention', 'The city hosts a comic convention every year.', '这座城市每年举办动漫展。'),
  ('e7a70081-ba84-4078-bc7c-6f2f8754f49d-ex2', 'e7a70081-ba84-4078-bc7c-6f2f8754f49d', 'convention', 'The convention obliges parties to criminalize transnational bribery.', '该公约要求缔约方将跨国贿赂定为犯罪。')
INSERT INTO vocab_examples (id, vocabulary_id, word, sentence_en, sentence_zh) VALUES
  ('8bee5fba-922b-444f-a575-4802f23bcf15-ex1', '8bee5fba-922b-444f-a575-4802f23bcf15', 'embrace', 'She embraced her old friend warmly.', '她热情地拥抱了老朋友。'),
  ('8bee5fba-922b-444f-a575-4802f23bcf15-ex2', '8bee5fba-922b-444f-a575-4802f23bcf15', 'embrace', 'The judiciary has been slow to embrace remote proceedings as a permanent fixture.', '司法系统迟迟未将远程庭审作为常设制度加以接纳。'),
  ('248dda2c-0440-4a66-a34d-5e171238048d-ex1', '248dda2c-0440-4a66-a34d-5e171238048d', 'assist', 'Can I assist you with your bags?', '我帮您拿包好吗？'),
  ('248dda2c-0440-4a66-a34d-5e171238048d-ex2', '248dda2c-0440-4a66-a34d-5e171238048d', 'assist', 'The secretariat exists to assist member states in implementing their obligations.', '秘书处的职能是协助成员国履行其义务。'),
  ('0bfbcbc4-57aa-4fe9-bbb7-e95131eabfd6-ex1', '0bfbcbc4-57aa-4fe9-bbb7-e95131eabfd6', 'exhibition', 'The art exhibition opens on Friday.', '艺术展周五开幕。'),
  ('0bfbcbc4-57aa-4fe9-bbb7-e95131eabfd6-ex2', '0bfbcbc4-57aa-4fe9-bbb7-e95131eabfd6', 'exhibition', 'The exhibition assembles loans negotiated with museums across four continents.', '这次展览汇集了与四大洲博物馆协商借展的展品。'),
  ('8e976372-3082-401b-a277-b8085ce2b07e-ex1', '8e976372-3082-401b-a277-b8085ce2b07e', 'construct', 'The workers will construct a new bridge.', '工人们将建造一座新桥。'),
  ('8e976372-3082-401b-a277-b8085ce2b07e-ex2', '8e976372-3082-401b-a277-b8085ce2b07e', 'construct', 'Courts construct ambiguous terms against the party that drafted them.', '对含糊条款，法院作不利于起草方的解释。'),
  ('1e9fd078-ef1b-4ac6-bc98-f16751aef15c-ex1', '1e9fd078-ef1b-4ac6-bc98-f16751aef15c', 'viewer', 'The show attracts millions of viewers.', '这个节目吸引了数百万观众。'),
  ('1e9fd078-ef1b-4ac6-bc98-f16751aef15c-ex2', '1e9fd078-ef1b-4ac6-bc98-f16751aef15c', 'viewer', 'The advertising rules protect viewers from undisclosed paid promotion.', '广告规则保护观众免受未披露的付费推广误导。'),
  ('ced90682-246e-4d08-8e09-da41cc24bde1-ex1', 'ced90682-246e-4d08-8e09-da41cc24bde1', 'pan', 'Heat some oil in the pan.', '在锅里热点油。'),
  ('ced90682-246e-4d08-8e09-da41cc24bde1-ex2', 'ced90682-246e-4d08-8e09-da41cc24bde1', 'pan', 'Critics panned the proposal as fiscally reckless and administratively naive.', '批评者抨击该提案在财政上鲁莽、在行政上天真。'),
  ('f5676cc8-e423-46be-8343-bdb22b6edb7a-ex1', 'f5676cc8-e423-46be-8343-bdb22b6edb7a', 'consultant', 'She works as a marketing consultant.', '她是一名营销顾问。'),
  ('f5676cc8-e423-46be-8343-bdb22b6edb7a-ex2', 'f5676cc8-e423-46be-8343-bdb22b6edb7a', 'consultant', 'The consultant''s undisclosed retainer created a disqualifying conflict of interest.', '这名顾问未披露的聘用关系构成了应予回避的利益冲突。'),
  ('5b5a7d9e-fe3a-4188-8b3e-f2c95b00eff2-ex1', '5b5a7d9e-fe3a-4188-8b3e-f2c95b00eff2', 'administrator', 'The school administrator handles schedules.', '学校行政人员负责安排日程。'),
  ('5b5a7d9e-fe3a-4188-8b3e-f2c95b00eff2-ex2', '5b5a7d9e-fe3a-4188-8b3e-f2c95b00eff2', 'administrator', 'The court-appointed administrator assumed control of the insolvent estate.', '法院指定的管理人接管了破产财产。'),
  ('d21ea2f9-b890-45fe-9d9f-10085c3bd455-ex1', 'd21ea2f9-b890-45fe-9d9f-10085c3bd455', 'occasionally', 'I occasionally eat out on weekends.', '我周末偶尔在外面吃饭。'),
  ('d21ea2f9-b890-45fe-9d9f-10085c3bd455-ex2', 'd21ea2f9-b890-45fe-9d9f-10085c3bd455', 'occasionally', 'Even well-designed controls occasionally fail under correlated stress.', '即使设计良好的控制机制，在关联性压力下也偶有失灵。'),
  ('f9dada8f-7027-448b-b05c-701e22a8219c-ex1', 'f9dada8f-7027-448b-b05c-701e22a8219c', 'mayor', 'The mayor opened the new library.', '市长为新图书馆揭幕。'),
  ('f9dada8f-7027-448b-b05c-701e22a8219c-ex2', 'f9dada8f-7027-448b-b05c-701e22a8219c', 'mayor', 'The mayor''s emergency powers lapse absent council ratification within thirty days.', '市长的紧急权力若未在三十天内获议会追认即告失效。'),
  ('5a3d2d2e-df18-4c7d-bcdb-0ff7b541a4af-ex1', '5a3d2d2e-df18-4c7d-bcdb-0ff7b541a4af', 'consideration', 'Thank you for your consideration.', '感谢您的考虑。'),
  ('5a3d2d2e-df18-4c7d-bcdb-0ff7b541a4af-ex2', '5a3d2d2e-df18-4c7d-bcdb-0ff7b541a4af', 'consideration', 'A promise unsupported by consideration is unenforceable at common law.', '按普通法，无对价支持的允诺不具强制执行力。'),
  ('bbcf6d70-c36c-4db4-a01a-168ee69d43e3-ex1', 'bbcf6d70-c36c-4db4-a01a-168ee69d43e3', 'CEO', 'The CEO spoke to all the employees.', '首席执行官向全体员工讲话。'),
  ('bbcf6d70-c36c-4db4-a01a-168ee69d43e3-ex2', 'bbcf6d70-c36c-4db4-a01a-168ee69d43e3', 'CEO', 'The CEO certified financial statements later shown to be materially false.', '这位首席执行官签署确认的财务报表后来被证明存在重大虚假。'),
  ('627c96a5-00fc-4deb-9d76-9684535aa75f-ex1', '627c96a5-00fc-4deb-9d76-9684535aa75f', 'secure', 'Make sure the windows are secure.', '确保窗户都关好了。'),
  ('627c96a5-00fc-4deb-9d76-9684535aa75f-ex2', '627c96a5-00fc-4deb-9d76-9684535aa75f', 'secure', 'The lenders required collateral sufficient to secure the entire facility.', '贷款方要求提供足以担保全部授信的抵押物。'),
  ('741b6dac-1fb9-4f74-9fa8-bb7f864d2774-ex1', '741b6dac-1fb9-4f74-9fa8-bb7f864d2774', 'pink', 'She painted her room pink.', '她把房间刷成了粉色。'),
  ('741b6dac-1fb9-4f74-9fa8-bb7f864d2774-ex2', '741b6dac-1fb9-4f74-9fa8-bb7f864d2774', 'pink', 'The pink slips arrived without the statutorily required notice period.', '解雇通知送达时未遵守法定的预告期。'),
  ('5bb0725b-6ceb-43ba-a8ae-e4e81b779670-ex1', '5bb0725b-6ceb-43ba-a8ae-e4e81b779670', 'buck', 'Can you lend me a few bucks?', '能借我几块钱吗？'),
  ('5bb0725b-6ceb-43ba-a8ae-e4e81b779670-ex2', '5bb0725b-6ceb-43ba-a8ae-e4e81b779670', 'buck', 'Each agency passed the buck until the ombudsman assigned responsibility.', '各机构相互推诿，直到监察专员认定了责任归属。'),
  ('d62ac36c-d0a6-4bc5-a876-61e74d2df316-ex1', 'd62ac36c-d0a6-4bc5-a876-61e74d2df316', 'historic', 'We visited the historic old town.', '我们参观了历史悠久的老城。'),
  ('d62ac36c-d0a6-4bc5-a876-61e74d2df316-ex2', 'd62ac36c-d0a6-4bc5-a876-61e74d2df316', 'historic', 'The historic ruling overturned doctrine that had stood for half a century.', '这一历史性裁决推翻了沿用半个世纪的法律原则。'),
  ('c1f1ad83-7fdd-462c-9f60-5426e9f54d28-ex1', 'c1f1ad83-7fdd-462c-9f60-5426e9f54d28', 'poem', 'She wrote a poem about spring.', '她写了一首关于春天的诗。'),
  ('c1f1ad83-7fdd-462c-9f60-5426e9f54d28-ex2', 'c1f1ad83-7fdd-462c-9f60-5426e9f54d28', 'poem', 'The poem entered the public domain upon expiry of the copyright term.', '版权期届满后，这首诗进入了公有领域。'),
  ('65ba39eb-3be4-421f-bf19-d180759df5cf-ex1', '65ba39eb-3be4-421f-bf19-d180759df5cf', 'grandmother', 'My grandmother tells wonderful stories.', '我祖母讲的故事很精彩。'),
  ('65ba39eb-3be4-421f-bf19-d180759df5cf-ex2', '65ba39eb-3be4-421f-bf19-d180759df5cf', 'grandmother', 'The court recognized the grandmother''s standing to seek custodial rights.', '法院承认祖母具有主张监护权的诉讼资格。'),
  ('acab7f7e-fcc9-4047-81fe-6e3906da1a0e-ex1', 'acab7f7e-fcc9-4047-81fe-6e3906da1a0e', 'bind', 'Use string to bind the papers together.', '用绳子把文件捆在一起。'),
  ('acab7f7e-fcc9-4047-81fe-6e3906da1a0e-ex2', 'acab7f7e-fcc9-4047-81fe-6e3906da1a0e', 'bind', 'The award binds the parties notwithstanding their continuing objections.', '尽管双方仍有异议，该裁决对其均有约束力。'),
  ('1f9dc1a9-41c8-4671-86b6-dc0e608f810f-ex1', '1f9dc1a9-41c8-4671-86b6-dc0e608f810f', 'fifth', 'Our office is on the fifth floor.', '我们的办公室在五楼。'),
  ('1f9dc1a9-41c8-4671-86b6-dc0e608f810f-ex2', '1f9dc1a9-41c8-4671-86b6-dc0e608f810f', 'fifth', 'The witness invoked the fifth amendment and declined to testify.', '证人援引宪法第五修正案，拒绝作证。'),
  ('e42901c9-a0e7-4b97-ae6e-da50ea3477a2-ex1', 'e42901c9-a0e7-4b97-ae6e-da50ea3477a2', 'constantly', 'The baby cries constantly at night.', '宝宝夜里不停地哭。'),
  ('e42901c9-a0e7-4b97-ae6e-da50ea3477a2-ex2', 'e42901c9-a0e7-4b97-ae6e-da50ea3477a2', 'constantly', 'Threat models must be constantly recalibrated as attack vectors evolve.', '随着攻击手段演变，威胁模型必须不断重新校准。'),
  ('fbffffed-1da2-4c92-a655-f1103bc583d3-ex1', 'fbffffed-1da2-4c92-a655-f1103bc583d3', 'enterprise', 'He started a small enterprise last year.', '他去年创办了一家小企业。'),
  ('fbffffed-1da2-4c92-a655-f1103bc583d3-ex2', 'fbffffed-1da2-4c92-a655-f1103bc583d3', 'enterprise', 'State-owned enterprises enjoy implicit guarantees that distort credit allocation.', '国有企业享有的隐性担保扭曲了信贷配置。'),
  ('9bf08ac8-016f-4176-bcaa-15129fd19e51-ex1', '9bf08ac8-016f-4176-bcaa-15129fd19e51', 'favor', 'Can you do me a favor?', '你能帮我个忙吗？'),
  ('9bf08ac8-016f-4176-bcaa-15129fd19e51-ex2', '9bf08ac8-016f-4176-bcaa-15129fd19e51', 'favor', 'The tribunal found in favor of the claimant on every substantive count.', '法庭在每项实体诉求上都作出了有利于申请人的裁定。'),
  ('1fe78bd8-63d6-40de-9146-b4a9b9a0e5d1-ex1', '1fe78bd8-63d6-40de-9146-b4a9b9a0e5d1', 'testing', 'The school does hearing testing every year.', '学校每年进行听力检测。'),
  ('1fe78bd8-63d6-40de-9146-b4a9b9a0e5d1-ex2', '1fe78bd8-63d6-40de-9146-b4a9b9a0e5d1', 'testing', 'Mandatory stress testing applies to all institutions above the threshold.', '强制压力测试适用于所有超过门槛的机构。'),
  ('eea4d11d-1962-4c07-b674-8b2c3393b039-ex1', 'eea4d11d-1962-4c07-b674-8b2c3393b039', 'stomach', 'My stomach hurts after lunch.', '午饭后我胃疼。'),
  ('eea4d11d-1962-4c07-b674-8b2c3393b039-ex2', 'eea4d11d-1962-4c07-b674-8b2c3393b039', 'stomach', 'Investors lacked the stomach for further exposure to the distressed debt.', '投资者已无胆量继续持有这些不良债务敞口。'),
  ('e3aacd5c-722d-4c2c-b9f2-327a35cca218-ex1', 'e3aacd5c-722d-4c2c-b9f2-327a35cca218', 'apparent', 'The reason for the delay was not apparent.', '延误的原因并不清楚。'),
  ('e3aacd5c-722d-4c2c-b9f2-327a35cca218-ex2', 'e3aacd5c-722d-4c2c-b9f2-327a35cca218', 'apparent', 'The agent acted within apparent authority, binding the undisclosed principal.', '代理人在表见授权范围内行事，约束了未披露的被代理人。'),
  ('c903d469-61c3-4f19-8551-4a287e282272-ex1', 'c903d469-61c3-4f19-8551-4a287e282272', 'weigh', 'Weigh the flour before adding it.', '加面粉前先称一下。'),
  ('c903d469-61c3-4f19-8551-4a287e282272-ex2', 'c903d469-61c3-4f19-8551-4a287e282272', 'weigh', 'The court must weigh probative value against the danger of unfair prejudice.', '法院必须在证明价值与不公正偏见的风险之间进行权衡。'),
  ('e750e280-5026-4034-b1af-87c0f56657e6-ex1', 'e750e280-5026-4034-b1af-87c0f56657e6', 'install', 'We installed a new air conditioner.', '我们安装了新空调。'),
  ('e750e280-5026-4034-b1af-87c0f56657e6-ex2', 'e750e280-5026-4034-b1af-87c0f56657e6', 'install', 'The decree requires the operator to install continuous emission monitors.', '该法令要求运营方安装连续排放监测装置。'),
  ('96bd325c-7e87-4410-8052-2a01be839df7-ex1', '96bd325c-7e87-4410-8052-2a01be839df7', 'sensitive', 'Her skin is sensitive to sunlight.', '她的皮肤对阳光敏感。'),
  ('96bd325c-7e87-4410-8052-2a01be839df7-ex2', '96bd325c-7e87-4410-8052-2a01be839df7', 'sensitive', 'Sensitive personal data attracts heightened processing safeguards.', '敏感个人数据适用更高的处理保障要求。'),
  ('d0e2cac0-387b-43ad-b050-ccac5061cac9-ex1', 'd0e2cac0-387b-43ad-b050-ccac5061cac9', 'suggestion', 'That is a great suggestion!', '这个建议太好了！'),
  ('d0e2cac0-387b-43ad-b050-ccac5061cac9-ex2', 'd0e2cac0-387b-43ad-b050-ccac5061cac9', 'suggestion', 'The consultation yielded suggestions subsequently embodied in the final rule.', '这次磋商收集的建议随后被纳入最终规则。'),
  ('8c83684a-d541-4dfa-9d36-7284e9d352b3-ex1', '8c83684a-d541-4dfa-9d36-7284e9d352b3', 'mail', 'Did you check the mail today?', '你今天查看邮件了吗？'),
  ('8c83684a-d541-4dfa-9d36-7284e9d352b3-ex2', '8c83684a-d541-4dfa-9d36-7284e9d352b3', 'mail', 'The statute criminalizes use of the mail in furtherance of fraudulent schemes.', '该法规将利用邮政实施欺诈计划的行为定为犯罪。'),
  ('6408e84b-9621-4af1-b6e7-f59c8fa4551e-ex1', '6408e84b-9621-4af1-b6e7-f59c8fa4551e', 'recipe', 'This is my grandmother''s soup recipe.', '这是我祖母的汤谱。'),
  ('6408e84b-9621-4af1-b6e7-f59c8fa4551e-ex2', '6408e84b-9621-4af1-b6e7-f59c8fa4551e', 'recipe', 'Opacity combined with leverage is a proven recipe for systemic crisis.', '不透明加上高杠杆是引发系统性危机的不二配方。'),
  ('17b6433d-e081-453f-afda-a281973c84b9-ex1', '17b6433d-e081-453f-afda-a281973c84b9', 'reasonable', 'The price seems reasonable to me.', '这个价格我觉得挺合理。'),
