  ('dc844470-1c86-4d20-9573-13e59b9d0465-ex1', 'dc844470-1c86-4d20-9573-13e59b9d0465', 'preparation', 'Good preparation is the key to success.', '充分的准备是成功的关键。'),
  ('dc844470-1c86-4d20-9573-13e59b9d0465-ex2', 'dc844470-1c86-4d20-9573-13e59b9d0465', 'preparation', 'The preparation of consolidated accounts must follow the prescribed standards.', '合并报表的编制必须遵循规定的准则。'),
  ('579b560c-2fa3-4caf-ad4b-f4ba7a8a90e4-ex1', '579b560c-2fa3-4caf-ad4b-f4ba7a8a90e4', 'wooden', 'We sat on a wooden bench.', '我们坐在木长椅上。'),
  ('579b560c-2fa3-4caf-ad4b-f4ba7a8a90e4-ex2', '579b560c-2fa3-4caf-ad4b-f4ba7a8a90e4', 'wooden', 'The wooden structures predate the fire code and enjoy grandfathered status.', '这些木结构建筑早于消防规范，享有既往不咎的豁免地位。'),
  ('e3de61b7-68d9-4b0e-be8a-57e92196e946-ex1', 'e3de61b7-68d9-4b0e-be8a-57e92196e946', 'elementary', 'My daughter is in elementary school.', '我女儿在上小学。'),
  ('e3de61b7-68d9-4b0e-be8a-57e92196e946-ex2', 'e3de61b7-68d9-4b0e-be8a-57e92196e946', 'elementary', 'The funding formula privileges elementary education in underserved districts.', '拨款公式向欠发达地区的初等教育倾斜。'),
  ('07e39a49-0db4-4457-bae0-9565f4277c10-ex1', '07e39a49-0db4-4457-bae0-9565f4277c10', 'concert', 'The concert starts at eight tonight.', '音乐会今晚八点开始。'),
  ('07e39a49-0db4-4457-bae0-9565f4277c10-ex2', '07e39a49-0db4-4457-bae0-9565f4277c10', 'concert', 'The defendants acted in concert to allocate markets and fix prices.', '被告们协同一致划分市场、操纵价格。'),
  ('68a51087-40a3-4a2b-a427-06fe09228c0e-ex1', '68a51087-40a3-4a2b-a427-06fe09228c0e', 'aggressive', 'The dog is not aggressive at all.', '这只狗一点也不凶。'),
  ('68a51087-40a3-4a2b-a427-06fe09228c0e-ex2', '68a51087-40a3-4a2b-a427-06fe09228c0e', 'aggressive', 'The aggressive tax structures attracted retrospective anti-avoidance legislation.', '这些激进的税务架构招致了具有追溯力的反避税立法。'),
  ('2fd162f4-5fd4-47c2-a403-ba22f45e8492-ex1', '2fd162f4-5fd4-47c2-a403-ba22f45e8492', 'false', 'The rumor turned out to be false.', '谣言被证明是假的。'),
  ('2fd162f4-5fd4-47c2-a403-ba22f45e8492-ex2', '2fd162f4-5fd4-47c2-a403-ba22f45e8492', 'false', 'Knowingly false statements to regulators constitute an independent offense.', '明知虚假仍向监管机构作出陈述，构成独立罪行。'),
  ('41e65cc3-2840-4ce4-9d76-85ccb7c9970b-ex1', '41e65cc3-2840-4ce4-9d76-85ccb7c9970b', 'intention', 'I have no intention of moving.', '我没有搬家的打算。'),
  ('41e65cc3-2840-4ce4-9d76-85ccb7c9970b-ex2', '41e65cc3-2840-4ce4-9d76-85ccb7c9970b', 'intention', 'The parties'' common intention prevails over the literal text where proven.', '在能够证明的情况下，双方的共同意图优先于字面文本。'),
  ('47d4c0cb-dfc1-4ed8-b99b-f5966de0b245-ex1', '47d4c0cb-dfc1-4ed8-b99b-f5966de0b245', 'channel', 'Change the channel; the news is on.', '换个台，新闻开始了。'),
  ('47d4c0cb-dfc1-4ed8-b99b-f5966de0b245-ex2', '47d4c0cb-dfc1-4ed8-b99b-f5966de0b245', 'channel', 'All communications must pass through the designated diplomatic channel.', '所有通信都必须经由指定的外交渠道。'),
  ('303f747e-7fae-4d2b-9abe-d715649c2d9e-ex1', '303f747e-7fae-4d2b-9abe-d715649c2d9e', 'extreme', 'The heat was extreme last summer.', '去年夏天酷热难耐。'),
  ('303f747e-7fae-4d2b-9abe-d715649c2d9e-ex2', '303f747e-7fae-4d2b-9abe-d715649c2d9e', 'extreme', 'Extreme weather attribution science increasingly informs liability claims.', '极端天气归因科学日益成为损害赔偿主张的依据。'),
  ('dfabbc67-eb6a-4b58-aea2-6133f535c2e3-ex1', 'dfabbc67-eb6a-4b58-aea2-6133f535c2e3', 'tube', 'The toothpaste tube is almost empty.', '牙膏快用完了。'),
  ('dfabbc67-eb6a-4b58-aea2-6133f535c2e3-ex2', 'dfabbc67-eb6a-4b58-aea2-6133f535c2e3', 'tube', 'The corroded tubes were replaced under the consent decree''s remediation schedule.', '根据和解令的整改时间表，受腐蚀的管道已被更换。'),
  ('564ae05e-49e5-4f24-ab8c-6136c2ce8027-ex1', '564ae05e-49e5-4f24-ab8c-6136c2ce8027', 'drawing', 'The child''s drawing won first prize.', '这个孩子的画获得了一等奖。'),
  ('564ae05e-49e5-4f24-ab8c-6136c2ce8027-ex2', '564ae05e-49e5-4f24-ab8c-6136c2ce8027', 'drawing', 'The engineering drawings diverged from the as-built condition in material respects.', '工程图纸与竣工实况在重大方面存在出入。'),
