  ('c6cb11b0-9dd4-470f-9136-07282dc645c9-ex1', 'c6cb11b0-9dd4-470f-9136-07282dc645c9', 'arise', 'Problems arise when we don''t communicate.', '缺乏沟通就会产生问题。'),
  ('c6cb11b0-9dd4-470f-9136-07282dc645c9-ex2', 'c6cb11b0-9dd4-470f-9136-07282dc645c9', 'arise', 'Disputes arising under the agreement shall be referred to arbitration.', '因本协议产生的争议应提交仲裁。'),
  ('cfe07e99-b4f0-45a6-ae0b-b726a03c1930-ex1', 'cfe07e99-b4f0-45a6-ae0b-b726a03c1930', 'armed', 'The guard is armed at night.', '警卫夜间携带武器。'),
  ('cfe07e99-b4f0-45a6-ae0b-b726a03c1930-ex2', 'cfe07e99-b4f0-45a6-ae0b-b726a03c1930', 'armed', 'The convention governs the conduct of parties to armed conflict.', '该公约规范武装冲突各方的行为。'),
  ('3703b51e-1dd5-446d-b315-c758a869fad1-ex1', '3703b51e-1dd5-446d-b315-c758a869fad1', 'nevertheless', 'It was raining; nevertheless, we went out.', '虽然下雨，我们还是出门了。'),
