  ('15804f84-fdd1-4182-9087-176ef558133a-ex2', '15804f84-fdd1-4182-9087-176ef558133a', 'stake', 'The acquirer disclosed a controlling stake exceeding the mandatory bid threshold.', '收购方披露了超过强制要约门槛的控股股权。'),
  ('c0e9c888-d0be-41e3-a46f-c265c447413c-ex1', 'c0e9c888-d0be-41e3-a46f-c265c447413c', 'Muslim', 'She has many Muslim friends.', '她有许多穆斯林朋友。'),
  ('c0e9c888-d0be-41e3-a46f-c265c447413c-ex2', 'c0e9c888-d0be-41e3-a46f-c265c447413c', 'Muslim', 'The charter guarantees Muslim communities equal protection of religious practice.', '宪章保障穆斯林群体宗教活动受平等保护。'),
