  ('c2044552-d079-4fd6-a9ac-c920c4850c21-ex1', 'c2044552-d079-4fd6-a9ac-c920c4850c21', 'activist', 'She is an environmental activist.', '她是一名环保活动家。'),
  ('c2044552-d079-4fd6-a9ac-c920c4850c21-ex2', 'c2044552-d079-4fd6-a9ac-c920c4850c21', 'activist', 'Activist shareholders pressed the board to divest its carbon-intensive holdings.', '维权股东敦促董事会剥离碳密集型资产。'),
