  ('3ca26bef-0570-43c7-bcb7-13b934f91c69-ex2', '3ca26bef-0570-43c7-bcb7-13b934f91c69', 'barrier', 'Non-tariff barriers proved more obstructive than the tariffs they replaced.', '非关税壁垒比它们所取代的关税更具阻碍性。'),
  ('d63af830-cc86-4d03-8d96-5ad903e851ac-ex1', 'd63af830-cc86-4d03-8d96-5ad903e851ac', 'minor', 'It was only a minor injury.', '只是轻微的伤。'),
