  ('6659b633-62fe-4290-b0a1-5da71c63b3fb-ex2', '6659b633-62fe-4290-b0a1-5da71c63b3fb', 'gang', 'The indictment charges the defendants with running an organized criminal gang.', '起诉书指控被告经营有组织犯罪团伙。'),
