  ('2f7b724f-9f8b-4809-858a-0a767f0375de-ex1', '2f7b724f-9f8b-4809-858a-0a767f0375de', 'chamber', 'The old castle has a hidden chamber.', '这座古堡有一间密室。'),
  ('2f7b724f-9f8b-4809-858a-0a767f0375de-ex2', '2f7b724f-9f8b-4809-858a-0a767f0375de', 'chamber', 'The upper chamber returned the bill with substantial amendments.', '上院将法案连同重大修正一并退回。'),
  ('1540c03a-8a1b-4263-99f2-f5c3ef8740d9-ex1', '1540c03a-8a1b-4263-99f2-f5c3ef8740d9', 'furniture', 'We bought new furniture for the living room.', '我们为客厅买了新家具。'),
  ('1540c03a-8a1b-4263-99f2-f5c3ef8740d9-ex2', '1540c03a-8a1b-4263-99f2-f5c3ef8740d9', 'furniture', 'The flammability standards apply to all upholstered furniture sold domestically.', '易燃性标准适用于国内销售的所有软垫家具。'),
  ('b0f82f73-3ffa-4751-92c2-6dbf11b66efc-ex1', 'b0f82f73-3ffa-4751-92c2-6dbf11b66efc', 'cooperation', 'Thank you for your cooperation.', '感谢你的配合。'),
  ('b0f82f73-3ffa-4751-92c2-6dbf11b66efc-ex2', 'b0f82f73-3ffa-4751-92c2-6dbf11b66efc', 'cooperation', 'The treaty institutionalizes cooperation on cross-border criminal investigation.', '该条约将跨境刑事侦查合作制度化。'),
  ('97537256-115e-4722-baf9-b75f984d0f8b-ex1', '97537256-115e-4722-baf9-b75f984d0f8b', 'string', 'Tie the box with a string.', '用绳子把箱子捆好。'),
  ('97537256-115e-4722-baf9-b75f984d0f8b-ex2', '97537256-115e-4722-baf9-b75f984d0f8b', 'string', 'The financing came with a string of covenants restricting further borrowing.', '这笔融资附带一系列限制进一步举债的契约条款。'),
  ('c53d67e7-6f7e-48e1-8ebb-fdf9a2f905cb-ex1', 'c53d67e7-6f7e-48e1-8ebb-fdf9a2f905cb', 'ceremony', 'The wedding ceremony was beautiful.', '婚礼仪式很美。'),
  ('c53d67e7-6f7e-48e1-8ebb-fdf9a2f905cb-ex2', 'c53d67e7-6f7e-48e1-8ebb-fdf9a2f905cb', 'ceremony', 'The signing ceremony marked the culmination of a decade of negotiation.', '签署仪式标志着十年谈判的圆满收官。'),
  ('4bc17b77-c76d-46a9-90da-b0c3196aea2f-ex1', '4bc17b77-c76d-46a9-90da-b0c3196aea2f', 'communicate', 'We communicate by email every day.', '我们每天通过邮件沟通。'),
  ('4bc17b77-c76d-46a9-90da-b0c3196aea2f-ex2', '4bc17b77-c76d-46a9-90da-b0c3196aea2f', 'communicate', 'The disclosure must communicate material risks comprehensibly to investors.', '披露必须以投资者能够理解的方式传达重大风险。'),
  ('ab045e7d-1d80-48a6-878d-fb44297e3854-ex1', 'ab045e7d-1d80-48a6-878d-fb44297e3854', 'cheek', 'The baby has rosy cheeks.', '宝宝脸蛋红扑扑的。'),
  ('ab045e7d-1d80-48a6-878d-fb44297e3854-ex2', 'ab045e7d-1d80-48a6-878d-fb44297e3854', 'cheek', 'It took considerable cheek to invoke an exemption the firm had itself opposed.', '援引一项公司自己曾反对过的豁免，着实厚颜。'),
  ('8d24bae7-51c3-4a2a-8a1d-8b98181a1d5c-ex1', '8d24bae7-51c3-4a2a-8a1d-8b98181a1d5c', 'lost', 'I got lost on the way here.', '我来的路上迷路了。'),
  ('8d24bae7-51c3-4a2a-8a1d-8b98181a1d5c-ex2', '8d24bae7-51c3-4a2a-8a1d-8b98181a1d5c', 'lost', 'The plaintiffs sued to recover profits lost through the unlawful exclusion.', '原告起诉追回因非法排挤而损失的利润。'),
  ('922fb5d0-4ff8-48f1-8b47-4171e465afa6-ex1', '922fb5d0-4ff8-48f1-8b47-4171e465afa6', 'profile', 'Please update your online profile.', '请更新你的网上个人资料。'),
  ('922fb5d0-4ff8-48f1-8b47-4171e465afa6-ex2', '922fb5d0-4ff8-48f1-8b47-4171e465afa6', 'profile', 'The institution''s risk profile shifted markedly after the leveraged acquisition.', '杠杆收购之后，该机构的风险状况发生了显著变化。'),
  ('c08eedc7-8d92-4b88-b3ce-0fe38f8c99df-ex1', 'c08eedc7-8d92-4b88-b3ce-0fe38f8c99df', 'mechanism', 'The clock''s mechanism is very old.', '这座钟的机械装置很古老。'),
  ('c08eedc7-8d92-4b88-b3ce-0fe38f8c99df-ex2', 'c08eedc7-8d92-4b88-b3ce-0fe38f8c99df', 'mechanism', 'The treaty establishes a dispute-resolution mechanism binding on all parties.', '该条约建立了对所有缔约方均有约束力的争端解决机制。'),
  ('eb7d3ff2-b13a-4886-b7ba-6f6b98c6e5ad-ex1', 'eb7d3ff2-b13a-4886-b7ba-6f6b98c6e5ad', 'disagree', 'I respectfully disagree with you.', '恕我不能同意你的看法。'),
  ('eb7d3ff2-b13a-4886-b7ba-6f6b98c6e5ad-ex2', 'eb7d3ff2-b13a-4886-b7ba-6f6b98c6e5ad', 'disagree', 'The dissenting justices disagree fundamentally with the majority''s premise.', '持异议的大法官从根本上不同意多数意见的前提。'),
  ('a24d4643-81a0-48e2-9e19-04d3a2d68221-ex1', 'a24d4643-81a0-48e2-9e19-04d3a2d68221', 'penalty', 'He got a penalty for parking illegally.', '他因违章停车被罚款。'),
  ('a24d4643-81a0-48e2-9e19-04d3a2d68221-ex2', 'a24d4643-81a0-48e2-9e19-04d3a2d68221', 'penalty', 'The penalty scales with the gravity and duration of the violation.', '处罚力度随违规的严重程度和持续时间而递增。'),
  ('fe74ae9f-b7aa-442c-ba4c-055ab6cf90b6-ex1', 'fe74ae9f-b7aa-442c-ba4c-055ab6cf90b6', 'resort', 'We stayed at a beach resort.', '我们住在一家海滨度假村。'),
  ('fe74ae9f-b7aa-442c-ba4c-055ab6cf90b6-ex2', 'fe74ae9f-b7aa-442c-ba4c-055ab6cf90b6', 'resort', 'Litigation should be a last resort after good-faith negotiation has failed.', '诉讼应是善意协商失败后的最后手段。'),
  ('5eac18a9-531d-4b94-8e6e-38bb63948fed-ex1', '5eac18a9-531d-4b94-8e6e-38bb63948fed', 'destruction', 'The fire caused total destruction.', '大火造成了彻底毁坏。'),
  ('5eac18a9-531d-4b94-8e6e-38bb63948fed-ex2', '5eac18a9-531d-4b94-8e6e-38bb63948fed', 'destruction', 'Deliberate destruction of evidence triggers adverse inferences against the offender.', '故意销毁证据将导致对销毁方作出不利推定。'),
  ('58c9f708-2fba-4383-b2fc-bd7d577ee94f-ex1', '58c9f708-2fba-4383-b2fc-bd7d577ee94f', 'unlikely', 'It is unlikely to snow today.', '今天不太可能下雪。'),
  ('58c9f708-2fba-4383-b2fc-bd7d577ee94f-ex2', '58c9f708-2fba-4383-b2fc-bd7d577ee94f', 'unlikely', 'A negotiated resolution appears unlikely absent a fundamental shift in positions.', '如果立场不发生根本转变，谈判解决似乎不太可能。'),
  ('7228b56c-c72e-4903-9653-95290e1f4ba2-ex1', '7228b56c-c72e-4903-9653-95290e1f4ba2', 'tissue', 'Pass me a tissue, please.', '请递给我一张纸巾。'),
  ('7228b56c-c72e-4903-9653-95290e1f4ba2-ex2', '7228b56c-c72e-4903-9653-95290e1f4ba2', 'tissue', 'The biopsy sampled tissue from several distinct anatomical sites.', '活检从几个不同的解剖部位取样组织。'),
  ('6a4c20c2-2f14-4733-a569-91d22879acee-ex1', '6a4c20c2-2f14-4733-a569-91d22879acee', 'constitutional', 'Free speech is a constitutional right.', '言论自由是一项宪法权利。'),
  ('6a4c20c2-2f14-4733-a569-91d22879acee-ex2', '6a4c20c2-2f14-4733-a569-91d22879acee', 'constitutional', 'The petitioners raised a constitutional challenge to the emergency decree.', '请愿人对紧急法令提起了违宪审查。'),
  ('d6b7cf5e-e564-4e28-9e03-d7e2ca4f1a44-ex1', 'd6b7cf5e-e564-4e28-9e03-d7e2ca4f1a44', 'pant', 'He wore black pants to the office.', '他穿着黑色裤子去上班。'),
  ('d6b7cf5e-e564-4e28-9e03-d7e2ca4f1a44-ex2', 'd6b7cf5e-e564-4e28-9e03-d7e2ca4f1a44', 'pant', 'The seized pants bore counterfeit marks of a protected designer label.', '查获的裤子带有受保护设计师品牌的假冒标识。'),
  ('88a008b9-2bc8-414f-bfe4-9444dd30befa-ex1', '88a008b9-2bc8-414f-bfe4-9444dd30befa', 'stranger', 'Don''t talk to strangers.', '不要和陌生人说话。'),
  ('88a008b9-2bc8-414f-bfe4-9444dd30befa-ex2', '88a008b9-2bc8-414f-bfe4-9444dd30befa', 'stranger', 'A stranger to the contract generally cannot enforce its provisions.', '合同的非缔约方通常无权执行其条款。'),
  ('ab80da94-8625-4e47-af97-64e3a36f562f-ex1', 'ab80da94-8625-4e47-af97-64e3a36f562f', 'infection', 'Wash the cut to prevent infection.', '清洗伤口以防感染。'),
  ('ab80da94-8625-4e47-af97-64e3a36f562f-ex2', 'ab80da94-8625-4e47-af97-64e3a36f562f', 'infection', 'The surveillance network enables early detection of infection clusters.', '该监测网络能够及早发现感染聚集性病例。'),
  ('706e66f3-3cba-41a5-8e24-5b7e6e8540ff-ex1', '706e66f3-3cba-41a5-8e24-5b7e6e8540ff', 'cabinet', 'The cups are in the kitchen cabinet.', '杯子在厨房橱柜里。'),
  ('706e66f3-3cba-41a5-8e24-5b7e6e8540ff-ex2', '706e66f3-3cba-41a5-8e24-5b7e6e8540ff', 'cabinet', 'The cabinet reshuffle followed the resignation of two senior ministers.', '内阁改组发生在两名资深部长辞职之后。'),
  ('ed3c8ac2-0037-4b61-92b1-6852c0f8452b-ex1', 'ed3c8ac2-0037-4b61-92b1-6852c0f8452b', 'broken', 'The window is broken.', '窗户破了。'),
  ('ed3c8ac2-0037-4b61-92b1-6852c0f8452b-ex2', 'ed3c8ac2-0037-4b61-92b1-6852c0f8452b', 'broken', 'The agreement collapsed amid mutual accusations of broken commitments.', '在相互指责对方违背承诺中，协议宣告破裂。'),
  ('749c9c67-05e5-4664-b16c-d131997cb365-ex1', '749c9c67-05e5-4664-b16c-d131997cb365', 'apple', 'An apple a day keeps the doctor away.', '一天一苹果，医生远离我。'),
  ('749c9c67-05e5-4664-b16c-d131997cb365-ex2', '749c9c67-05e5-4664-b16c-d131997cb365', 'apple', 'The orchard''s apple varieties enjoy protected geographical designation.', '这片果园的苹果品种享有地理标志保护。'),
  ('7927d2ed-5544-4cfb-8048-f575038557b3-ex1', '7927d2ed-5544-4cfb-8048-f575038557b3', 'electric', 'We bought an electric kettle.', '我们买了一个电热水壶。'),
  ('7927d2ed-5544-4cfb-8048-f575038557b3-ex2', '7927d2ed-5544-4cfb-8048-f575038557b3', 'electric', 'The transition to electric fleets requires unprecedented grid investment.', '向电动车队转型需要规模空前的电网投资。'),
  ('d44c4a42-cf44-41c8-b4ea-a26261255e34-ex1', 'd44c4a42-cf44-41c8-b4ea-a26261255e34', 'proceed', 'Please proceed to gate twelve.', '请前往十二号登机口。'),
  ('d44c4a42-cf44-41c8-b4ea-a26261255e34-ex2', 'd44c4a42-cf44-41c8-b4ea-a26261255e34', 'proceed', 'The court allowed the claims to proceed to full evidentiary hearing.', '法院准许这些诉求进入全面证据审理阶段。'),
  ('f19298bf-0245-4b2e-affb-1dc6859b2823-ex1', 'f19298bf-0245-4b2e-affb-1dc6859b2823', 'bet', 'I bet you can''t catch me!', '我打赌你抓不到我！'),
  ('f19298bf-0245-4b2e-affb-1dc6859b2823-ex2', 'f19298bf-0245-4b2e-affb-1dc6859b2823', 'bet', 'The leveraged bet on rising rates wiped out the fund''s reserves.', '押注利率上行的杠杆操作耗尽了该基金的储备金。'),
  ('c1363c6a-5435-44fc-ab11-1a557e148993-ex1', 'c1363c6a-5435-44fc-ab11-1a557e148993', 'literary', 'She has a literary talent.', '她有文学才华。'),
  ('c1363c6a-5435-44fc-ab11-1a557e148993-ex2', 'c1363c6a-5435-44fc-ab11-1a557e148993', 'literary', 'The literary estate retains exclusive rights for the statutory copyright term.', '该文学遗产在法定版权期内保留专有权利。'),
  ('b535942d-d8dd-4adc-ad16-1c7bac1bb906-ex1', 'b535942d-d8dd-4adc-ad16-1c7bac1bb906', 'virus', 'A virus made my computer crash.', '病毒导致我的电脑崩溃了。'),
  ('b535942d-d8dd-4adc-ad16-1c7bac1bb906-ex2', 'b535942d-d8dd-4adc-ad16-1c7bac1bb906', 'virus', 'The novel virus spread faster than containment protocols could be deployed.', '这种新型病毒的传播速度超过了防控方案的部署速度。'),
  ('bc111453-8c6b-4e3e-8f87-dbd813281243-ex1', 'bc111453-8c6b-4e3e-8f87-dbd813281243', 'stupid', 'That was a stupid mistake.', '那是个愚蠢的错误。'),
  ('bc111453-8c6b-4e3e-8f87-dbd813281243-ex2', 'bc111453-8c6b-4e3e-8f87-dbd813281243', 'stupid', 'Even ostensibly stupid clauses may carry consequences the parties overlooked.', '即使是表面上看似愚蠢的条款，也可能带来当事方忽视的后果。'),
  ('482df8ce-32b7-4f00-8876-e1e892dd0b4a-ex1', '482df8ce-32b7-4f00-8876-e1e892dd0b4a', 'dispute', 'They had a dispute over the bill.', '他们为账单起了争执。'),
  ('482df8ce-32b7-4f00-8876-e1e892dd0b4a-ex2', '482df8ce-32b7-4f00-8876-e1e892dd0b4a', 'dispute', 'The dispute was referred to arbitration under the contract''s governing clause.', '该争议依据合同的管辖条款被提交仲裁。'),
  ('e7dfb260-430d-47f5-a64b-140007ec777d-ex1', 'e7dfb260-430d-47f5-a64b-140007ec777d', 'fortune', 'He made a fortune in real estate.', '他靠房地产发了财。'),
  ('e7dfb260-430d-47f5-a64b-140007ec777d-ex2', 'e7dfb260-430d-47f5-a64b-140007ec777d', 'fortune', 'The family fortune was settled into a trust to shield it from creditors.', '这笔家族财富被设立为信托，以使其免受债权人追索。'),
  ('c2f148f5-75ad-4f31-b06e-74e796f968e9-ex1', 'c2f148f5-75ad-4f31-b06e-74e796f968e9', 'strategic', 'The company made a strategic decision.', '公司做出了一项战略决策。'),
  ('c2f148f5-75ad-4f31-b06e-74e796f968e9-ex2', 'c2f148f5-75ad-4f31-b06e-74e796f968e9', 'strategic', 'The screening regime targets foreign investment in strategic infrastructure.', '该审查制度针对进入战略性基础设施的外国投资。'),
  ('6334411f-a5eb-46f2-b206-7462dbf8aafa-ex1', '6334411f-a5eb-46f2-b206-7462dbf8aafa', 'assistant', 'My assistant will call you back.', '我的助理会给你回电。'),
  ('6334411f-a5eb-46f2-b206-7462dbf8aafa-ex2', '6334411f-a5eb-46f2-b206-7462dbf8aafa', 'assistant', 'The assistant acted within the scope of authority her principal had conferred.', '这名助理在被代理人授予的权限范围内行事。')
INSERT INTO vocab_examples (id, vocabulary_id, word, sentence_en, sentence_zh) VALUES
  ('287506fa-b922-4cc1-ae1a-3559b8126de4-ex1', '287506fa-b922-4cc1-ae1a-3559b8126de4', 'overcome', 'She overcame her fear of flying.', '她克服了对坐飞机的恐惧。'),
  ('287506fa-b922-4cc1-ae1a-3559b8126de4-ex2', '287506fa-b922-4cc1-ae1a-3559b8126de4', 'overcome', 'The reforms must overcome entrenched resistance from the beneficiaries of the status quo.', '这些改革必须克服现状受益者根深蒂固的阻力。'),
  ('14a31407-fb88-4cfa-8ad8-35486d152a6d-ex1', '14a31407-fb88-4cfa-8ad8-35486d152a6d', 'remarkable', 'She made remarkable progress in math.', '她在数学上取得了显著进步。'),
  ('14a31407-fb88-4cfa-8ad8-35486d152a6d-ex2', '14a31407-fb88-4cfa-8ad8-35486d152a6d', 'remarkable', 'The recovery proceeded at a remarkable pace that defied every forecast.', '复苏以惊人的速度推进，超出了所有预测。'),
  ('681c9b6b-d5bd-4014-9896-f08620bc49ce-ex1', '681c9b6b-d5bd-4014-9896-f08620bc49ce', 'occupy', 'The books occupy the entire shelf.', '这些书占满了整个书架。'),
  ('681c9b6b-d5bd-4014-9896-f08620bc49ce-ex2', '681c9b6b-d5bd-4014-9896-f08620bc49ce', 'occupy', 'The dispute over who may occupy the disputed premises remains unresolved.', '关于谁有权占用争议房屋的纠纷仍未解决。'),
  ('87ae6b3b-a765-4d51-829a-961078b380ce-ex1', '87ae6b3b-a765-4d51-829a-961078b380ce', 'statistics', 'The statistics show rising temperatures.', '统计数据显示气温在上升。'),
  ('87ae6b3b-a765-4d51-829a-961078b380ce-ex2', '87ae6b3b-a765-4d51-829a-961078b380ce', 'statistics', 'Official statistics understated unemployment by excluding discouraged workers.', '官方统计因剔除灰心丧气的求职者而低估了失业率。'),
  ('0be4d075-a060-4506-8684-e93037e18c12-ex1', '0be4d075-a060-4506-8684-e93037e18c12', 'shopping', 'We went shopping for groceries.', '我们去采购日用品了。'),
  ('0be4d075-a060-4506-8684-e93037e18c12-ex2', '0be4d075-a060-4506-8684-e93037e18c12', 'shopping', 'Forum shopping among lenient jurisdictions undermines uniform enforcement.', '在宽松司法管辖区之间挑选法院的做法破坏了统一执法。'),
  ('77461201-4d0f-4690-8049-874cb7cc30e9-ex1', '77461201-4d0f-4690-8049-874cb7cc30e9', 'cousin', 'My cousin lives in another city.', '我表弟住在另一座城市。'),
  ('77461201-4d0f-4690-8049-874cb7cc30e9-ex2', '77461201-4d0f-4690-8049-874cb7cc30e9', 'cousin', 'The court recognized the cousin''s standing as a beneficiary under the trust.', '法院承认该表亲作为信托受益人的资格。'),
  ('1be6dff9-0789-4ad1-a89a-8f3b6bfd4208-ex1', '1be6dff9-0789-4ad1-a89a-8f3b6bfd4208', 'encounter', 'We had a strange encounter on the trail.', '我们在小路上遇到了奇怪的事。'),
  ('1be6dff9-0789-4ad1-a89a-8f3b6bfd4208-ex2', '1be6dff9-0789-4ad1-a89a-8f3b6bfd4208', 'encounter', 'The negotiators encountered objections that no amount of redrafting could resolve.', '谈判代表遇到了无论怎样重新起草都无法化解的反对意见。'),
  ('6f52e6a7-3e7c-46d0-a744-54b5ab2bf1c8-ex1', '6f52e6a7-3e7c-46d0-a744-54b5ab2bf1c8', 'wipe', 'Wipe the table after dinner.', '饭后擦一下桌子。'),
  ('6f52e6a7-3e7c-46d0-a744-54b5ab2bf1c8-ex2', '6f52e6a7-3e7c-46d0-a744-54b5ab2bf1c8', 'wipe', 'The downturn wiped out gains accumulated over the preceding decade.', '这次衰退抹去了前十年累积的所有收益。'),
  ('4b67360b-d5e5-4dd2-b586-0e068c957319-ex1', '4b67360b-d5e5-4dd2-b586-0e068c957319', 'initially', 'I initially thought it was a joke.', '我起初以为是个玩笑。'),
  ('4b67360b-d5e5-4dd2-b586-0e068c957319-ex2', '4b67360b-d5e5-4dd2-b586-0e068c957319', 'initially', 'The provision, initially uncontroversial, became the litigation''s central battleground.', '这一最初毫无争议的条款，后来成了诉讼的主战场。'),
  ('af8bd676-4a97-4754-9698-672c40caea75-ex1', 'af8bd676-4a97-4754-9698-672c40caea75', 'blind', 'The guide dog helps the blind man.', '导盲犬帮助这位盲人。'),
  ('af8bd676-4a97-4754-9698-672c40caea75-ex2', 'af8bd676-4a97-4754-9698-672c40caea75', 'blind', 'The auditors were criticized for a blind reliance on management representations.', '审计师因盲目依赖管理层陈述而受到批评。'),
  ('67a3aec8-a11e-49bb-b03b-1adb04671914-ex1', '67a3aec8-a11e-49bb-b03b-1adb04671914', 'port', 'The ship arrived at the port.', '船抵达了港口。'),
  ('67a3aec8-a11e-49bb-b03b-1adb04671914-ex2', '67a3aec8-a11e-49bb-b03b-1adb04671914', 'port', 'Customs intercepted the consignment at the port of entry on documentary grounds.', '海关基于单据问题在入境口岸截留了这批货物。'),
  ('9569d523-6c49-4174-a981-c552928361fa-ex1', '9569d523-6c49-4174-a981-c552928361fa', 'electricity', 'The storm cut off our electricity.', '暴风雨切断了我们的电力。'),
  ('9569d523-6c49-4174-a981-c552928361fa-ex2', '9569d523-6c49-4174-a981-c552928361fa', 'electricity', 'Electricity tariffs are set through adversarial proceedings before the regulator.', '电价通过监管机构前的对审程序确定。'),
  ('424d3c36-f83d-4214-b9b5-9de6c0a9b6a8-ex1', '424d3c36-f83d-4214-b9b5-9de6c0a9b6a8', 'genetic', 'Eye color is a genetic trait.', '眼睛的颜色是遗传特征。'),
  ('424d3c36-f83d-4214-b9b5-9de6c0a9b6a8-ex2', '424d3c36-f83d-4214-b9b5-9de6c0a9b6a8', 'genetic', 'The statute prohibits discrimination based on genetic information in insurance.', '该法规禁止在保险中基于遗传信息的歧视。'),
  ('ad8b14aa-ac5f-4581-8551-d2072f7a2cb1-ex1', 'ad8b14aa-ac5f-4581-8551-d2072f7a2cb1', 'adviser', 'Her adviser helped her choose courses.', '她的导师帮她选课。'),
  ('ad8b14aa-ac5f-4581-8551-d2072f7a2cb1-ex2', 'ad8b14aa-ac5f-4581-8551-d2072f7a2cb1', 'adviser', 'The financial adviser''s undisclosed commissions tainted the recommendations.', '这名理财顾问未披露的佣金使其建议失去了公正性。'),
  ('00724932-c570-45b1-bbd3-50603d910e7d-ex1', '00724932-c570-45b1-bbd3-50603d910e7d', 'spokesman', 'The spokesman answered the reporters'' questions.', '发言人回答了记者的提问。'),
  ('00724932-c570-45b1-bbd3-50603d910e7d-ex2', '00724932-c570-45b1-bbd3-50603d910e7d', 'spokesman', 'The spokesman declined to comment on matters before the tribunal.', '发言人拒绝就法庭审理中的事项发表评论。'),
  ('164ecc96-58ee-47a2-bc9e-7e0c0029e7bd-ex1', '164ecc96-58ee-47a2-bc9e-7e0c0029e7bd', 'retain', 'Try to retain what you have learned.', '尽量保留学过的东西。'),
  ('164ecc96-58ee-47a2-bc9e-7e0c0029e7bd-ex2', '164ecc96-58ee-47a2-bc9e-7e0c0029e7bd', 'retain', 'The vendor retains title until the purchase price is paid in full.', '在购买款项全额支付之前，卖方保留所有权。'),
  ('b98b23ff-c39c-4d13-9208-45a84c58a1d4-ex1', 'b98b23ff-c39c-4d13-9208-45a84c58a1d4', 'latter', 'Of the two plans, I prefer the latter.', '两个方案中，我更喜欢后者。'),
  ('b98b23ff-c39c-4d13-9208-45a84c58a1d4-ex2', 'b98b23ff-c39c-4d13-9208-45a84c58a1d4', 'latter', 'The latter clause governs in the event of irreconcilable conflict.', '如发生无法调和的冲突，以后一条款为准。'),
  ('4d7bc8e9-9e27-4259-94e5-ffe3a91152cc-ex1', '4d7bc8e9-9e27-4259-94e5-ffe3a91152cc', 'incentive', 'The bonus is a good incentive to work hard.', '奖金是努力工作的好动力。'),
  ('4d7bc8e9-9e27-4259-94e5-ffe3a91152cc-ex2', '4d7bc8e9-9e27-4259-94e5-ffe3a91152cc', 'incentive', 'The compensation structure created perverse incentives for excessive risk-taking.', '这种薪酬结构产生了鼓励过度冒险的扭曲激励。'),
  ('e99cd4b8-6a3c-4a59-9023-a0b3c8e31db5-ex1', 'e99cd4b8-6a3c-4a59-9023-a0b3c8e31db5', 'slave', 'The museum tells the history of slaves.', '博物馆讲述了奴隶的历史。'),
  ('e99cd4b8-6a3c-4a59-9023-a0b3c8e31db5-ex2', 'e99cd4b8-6a3c-4a59-9023-a0b3c8e31db5', 'slave', 'The convention obliges states to criminalize all forms of modern slave labor.', '该公约要求各国将一切形式的现代奴役劳动定为犯罪。'),
  ('19f36216-cefb-44a0-900d-0b7ea1e65527-ex1', '19f36216-cefb-44a0-900d-0b7ea1e65527', 'translate', 'Can you translate this sentence?', '你能翻译这个句子吗？'),
  ('19f36216-cefb-44a0-900d-0b7ea1e65527-ex2', '19f36216-cefb-44a0-900d-0b7ea1e65527', 'translate', 'Pledges must translate into binding measures before they alter market behavior.', '承诺必须转化为约束性措施，才能改变市场行为。'),
  ('f82dde19-812f-4c46-a035-f30485b3a9c4-ex1', 'f82dde19-812f-4c46-a035-f30485b3a9c4', 'accurate', 'The map is very accurate.', '这张地图非常准确。'),
  ('f82dde19-812f-4c46-a035-f30485b3a9c4-ex2', 'f82dde19-812f-4c46-a035-f30485b3a9c4', 'accurate', 'The prospectus failed to provide an accurate picture of the issuer''s solvency.', '招股书未能准确呈现发行人的偿付能力状况。'),
  ('f16f83cb-bb68-42af-87c2-76c49631024b-ex1', 'f16f83cb-bb68-42af-87c2-76c49631024b', 'whereas', 'He likes tea, whereas I prefer coffee.', '他喜欢茶，而我更喜欢咖啡。'),
  ('f16f83cb-bb68-42af-87c2-76c49631024b-ex2', 'f16f83cb-bb68-42af-87c2-76c49631024b', 'whereas', 'Whereas the parties wish to settle their dispute, they agree as follows.', '鉴于双方希望解决争端，特此达成如下约定。'),
  ('dff8398b-9c28-4a21-b5bb-e7c365c4aa81-ex1', 'dff8398b-9c28-4a21-b5bb-e7c365c4aa81', 'terror', 'The child screamed in terror.', '孩子吓得尖叫起来。'),
  ('dff8398b-9c28-4a21-b5bb-e7c365c4aa81-ex2', 'dff8398b-9c28-4a21-b5bb-e7c365c4aa81', 'terror', 'The financing of terror is criminalized under the international convention.', '资助恐怖活动的行为在国际公约下被定为犯罪。'),
  ('5cf5c097-6063-4cf6-8dbf-7dcfec1d4c60-ex1', '5cf5c097-6063-4cf6-8dbf-7dcfec1d4c60', 'expansion', 'The company announced a major expansion.', '公司宣布了一项重大扩张。'),
  ('5cf5c097-6063-4cf6-8dbf-7dcfec1d4c60-ex2', '5cf5c097-6063-4cf6-8dbf-7dcfec1d4c60', 'expansion', 'The credit expansion fueled an asset bubble that supervisors failed to restrain.', '信贷扩张助长了监管者未能遏制的资产泡沫。'),
  ('b84d4d7e-84ba-4c1c-a5de-1f969eb2d75f-ex1', 'b84d4d7e-84ba-4c1c-a5de-1f969eb2d75f', 'elite', 'He trained with elite athletes.', '他和顶尖运动员一起训练。'),
  ('b84d4d7e-84ba-4c1c-a5de-1f969eb2d75f-ex2', 'b84d4d7e-84ba-4c1c-a5de-1f969eb2d75f', 'elite', 'The reforms threatened entrenched interests of the political and economic elite.', '这些改革触及了政治和经济精英根深蒂固的利益。'),
  ('57672a83-cf4f-415e-8659-e9cbcab0b087-ex1', '57672a83-cf4f-415e-8659-e9cbcab0b087', 'Olympic', 'She dreams of competing in the Olympic Games.', '她梦想参加奥运会。'),
  ('57672a83-cf4f-415e-8659-e9cbcab0b087-ex2', '57672a83-cf4f-415e-8659-e9cbcab0b087', 'Olympic', 'The Olympic host city committed to binding sustainability undertakings.', '奥运主办城市承诺履行有约束力的可持续发展义务。'),
  ('e34aba49-4b46-4f44-9959-b3de3a19281e-ex1', 'e34aba49-4b46-4f44-9959-b3de3a19281e', 'dirt', 'Wash the dirt off your hands.', '把手上的泥洗掉。'),
  ('e34aba49-4b46-4f44-9959-b3de3a19281e-ex2', 'e34aba49-4b46-4f44-9959-b3de3a19281e', 'dirt', 'The exposé unearthed dirt that ended several distinguished careers.', '这篇揭露报道挖出的丑闻终结了数位名人的职业生涯。'),
  ('bb5fbaf5-84d4-4234-8699-35f81b6e1587-ex1', 'bb5fbaf5-84d4-4234-8699-35f81b6e1587', 'odd', 'That is an odd-looking hat.', '那顶帽子样子很怪。'),
  ('bb5fbaf5-84d4-4234-8699-35f81b6e1587-ex2', 'bb5fbaf5-84d4-4234-8699-35f81b6e1587', 'odd', 'It struck investigators as odd that the records ended abruptly that month.', '记录在那个月戛然而止，这让调查人员觉得很蹊跷。'),
  ('992fe705-2450-4fa6-8233-c002a7941faf-ex1', '992fe705-2450-4fa6-8233-c002a7941faf', 'rice', 'We had rice with dinner.', '我们晚饭吃了米饭。'),
  ('992fe705-2450-4fa6-8233-c002a7941faf-ex2', '992fe705-2450-4fa6-8233-c002a7941faf', 'rice', 'Rice export restrictions destabilized prices across import-dependent economies.', '大米出口限制扰乱了依赖进口经济体的价格稳定。'),
  ('f9e5de26-53a3-47dc-857f-ebc2c817ae1f-ex1', 'f9e5de26-53a3-47dc-857f-ebc2c817ae1f', 'bullet', 'The police found a bullet at the scene.', '警方在现场发现了一颗子弹。'),
  ('f9e5de26-53a3-47dc-857f-ebc2c817ae1f-ex2', 'f9e5de26-53a3-47dc-857f-ebc2c817ae1f', 'bullet', 'There is no silver bullet for a crisis rooted in structural imbalance.', '对于根源在于结构性失衡的危机，并不存在一劳永逸的灵丹妙药。'),
  ('938a8364-5cc9-4f28-bdf9-8c8b55940497-ex1', '938a8364-5cc9-4f28-bdf9-8c8b55940497', 'tight', 'These shoes are too tight.', '这双鞋太紧了。'),
  ('938a8364-5cc9-4f28-bdf9-8c8b55940497-ex2', '938a8364-5cc9-4f28-bdf9-8c8b55940497', 'tight', 'Tight credit conditions choked off financing for viable small enterprises.', '信贷紧缩切断了对有生存能力的小企业的融资。'),
  ('4abc6e22-2ff9-4b4a-af49-3c63e82358af-ex1', '4abc6e22-2ff9-4b4a-af49-3c63e82358af', 'Bible', 'The hotel room had a Bible in the drawer.', '酒店房间的抽屉里有一本《圣经》。'),
  ('4abc6e22-2ff9-4b4a-af49-3c63e82358af-ex2', '4abc6e22-2ff9-4b4a-af49-3c63e82358af', 'Bible', 'The manual became the regulatory bible governing every certification decision.', '这本手册成了规范每一项认证决定的监管圣经。'),
  ('0b33ca73-ca20-4643-8868-7375d7593591-ex1', '0b33ca73-ca20-4643-8868-7375d7593591', 'chart', 'The chart shows our monthly sales.', '这张图表显示了我们的月销售额。'),
  ('0b33ca73-ca20-4643-8868-7375d7593591-ex2', '0b33ca73-ca20-4643-8868-7375d7593591', 'chart', 'The agreement charts a credible path toward full normalization.', '该协议为全面正常化规划了一条可信的路径。'),
  ('31c02cf9-e8f0-4367-8bda-c1a0664ff2ae-ex1', '31c02cf9-e8f0-4367-8bda-c1a0664ff2ae', 'solar', 'They installed solar panels on the roof.', '他们在屋顶安装了太阳能板。'),
  ('31c02cf9-e8f0-4367-8bda-c1a0664ff2ae-ex2', '31c02cf9-e8f0-4367-8bda-c1a0664ff2ae', 'solar', 'Utility-scale solar now undercuts fossil generation on a levelized basis.', '大型太阳能发电按平准化成本计算如今已低于化石能源发电。'),
  ('c1e6f98d-1864-48a1-8ea5-0f8823bd5427-ex1', 'c1e6f98d-1864-48a1-8ea5-0f8823bd5427', 'square', 'We met in the town square.', '我们在镇广场见面。'),
  ('c1e6f98d-1864-48a1-8ea5-0f8823bd5427-ex2', 'c1e6f98d-1864-48a1-8ea5-0f8823bd5427', 'square', 'The figures simply do not square with the audited financial statements.', '这些数字与经审计的财务报表根本对不上。'),
  ('9b67e0c7-8648-437b-a90e-da7ab128454a-ex1', '9b67e0c7-8648-437b-a90e-da7ab128454a', 'concentration', 'Reading requires concentration.', '阅读需要专注。'),
  ('9b67e0c7-8648-437b-a90e-da7ab128454a-ex2', '9b67e0c7-8648-437b-a90e-da7ab128454a', 'concentration', 'Market concentration reached levels that effectively foreclosed new entry.', '市场集中度达到了实际上阻断新进入的水平。'),
  ('5fc0537a-0ff7-4d26-81f2-af6b156d3167-ex1', '5fc0537a-0ff7-4d26-81f2-af6b156d3167', 'complicated', 'The instructions are too complicated.', '这些说明太复杂了。'),
  ('5fc0537a-0ff7-4d26-81f2-af6b156d3167-ex2', '5fc0537a-0ff7-4d26-81f2-af6b156d3167', 'complicated', 'The ownership structure was deliberately complicated to obscure control.', '这一所有权结构被刻意设计得复杂，以掩盖控制权。'),
  ('5c68db09-eb2a-412f-9981-89e8531e3ca1-ex1', '5c68db09-eb2a-412f-9981-89e8531e3ca1', 'gently', 'Hold the baby gently.', '轻轻地抱着宝宝。'),
  ('5c68db09-eb2a-412f-9981-89e8531e3ca1-ex2', '5c68db09-eb2a-412f-9981-89e8531e3ca1', 'gently', 'The court gently but firmly reminded counsel of the evidentiary rules.', '法院温和而坚定地提醒律师注意证据规则。'),
  ('f5cb5ffd-fc32-4d2f-ba78-37bd9c0efb9d-ex1', 'f5cb5ffd-fc32-4d2f-ba78-37bd9c0efb9d', 'champion', 'She is the chess champion of our school.', '她是我们学校的国际象棋冠军。'),
  ('f5cb5ffd-fc32-4d2f-ba78-37bd9c0efb9d-ex2', 'f5cb5ffd-fc32-4d2f-ba78-37bd9c0efb9d', 'champion', 'The senator championed reforms that her own party initially opposed.', '这位参议员力推的改革起初连她自己的政党都反对。'),
  ('2341a34d-461f-4f71-809f-aaa9772bb255-ex1', '2341a34d-461f-4f71-809f-aaa9772bb255', 'scenario', 'Imagine a scenario where you win the prize.', '想象一下你获奖的情景。'),
  ('2341a34d-461f-4f71-809f-aaa9772bb255-ex2', '2341a34d-461f-4f71-809f-aaa9772bb255', 'scenario', 'The stress tests model each institution under a severe adverse scenario.', '压力测试模拟每家机构在严峻不利情景下的状况。'),
  ('5ba9ad70-6783-4d21-b509-2a98697e036a-ex1', '5ba9ad70-6783-4d21-b509-2a98697e036a', 'telescope', 'We watched the stars through a telescope.', '我们用望远镜观看星星。'),
  ('5ba9ad70-6783-4d21-b509-2a98697e036a-ex2', '5ba9ad70-6783-4d21-b509-2a98697e036a', 'telescope', 'The orbiting telescope captured radiation from the universe''s earliest epochs.', '这台轨道望远镜捕捉到了来自宇宙最早期的辐射。'),
  ('20c40a80-c883-4c54-95c8-91cd2155f999-ex1', '20c40a80-c883-4c54-95c8-91cd2155f999', 'reflection', 'She saw her reflection in the water.', '她在水中看到了自己的倒影。'),
  ('20c40a80-c883-4c54-95c8-91cd2155f999-ex2', '20c40a80-c883-4c54-95c8-91cd2155f999', 'reflection', 'On reflection, the committee revised conclusions reached too hastily.', '经过反思，委员会修正了过于仓促得出的结论。'),
  ('b5e4e977-4cec-4b18-b551-e6c1674fc1c2-ex1', 'b5e4e977-4cec-4b18-b551-e6c1674fc1c2', 'revolution', 'The revolution changed the country forever.', '这场革命永远改变了这个国家。'),
  ('b5e4e977-4cec-4b18-b551-e6c1674fc1c2-ex2', 'b5e4e977-4cec-4b18-b551-e6c1674fc1c2', 'revolution', 'The digital revolution outpaced the legal frameworks meant to govern it.', '数字革命的发展速度超过了本应规范它的法律框架。'),
  ('45320bbc-5c18-41df-b9ed-d8b6beeb5d1e-ex1', '45320bbc-5c18-41df-b9ed-d8b6beeb5d1e', 'strip', 'Strip the old paint off the wall.', '把墙上的旧漆刮掉。'),
  ('45320bbc-5c18-41df-b9ed-d8b6beeb5d1e-ex2', '45320bbc-5c18-41df-b9ed-d8b6beeb5d1e', 'strip', 'The ruling strips the contested clause of any enforceable effect.', '该裁决剥夺了争议条款的一切可执行效力。'),
  ('65bbbc2d-ec5c-4ce3-b1f0-e2037bb11806-ex1', '65bbbc2d-ec5c-4ce3-b1f0-e2037bb11806', 'interpret', 'How do you interpret this poem?', '你如何理解这首诗？'),
  ('65bbbc2d-ec5c-4ce3-b1f0-e2037bb11806-ex2', '65bbbc2d-ec5c-4ce3-b1f0-e2037bb11806', 'interpret', 'Courts interpret penal statutes strictly in favor of the accused.', '法院对刑事法规作严格解释，作有利于被告的处理。'),
  ('1d97bd21-84ce-4ba6-aab9-849b3c60ab29-ex1', '1d97bd21-84ce-4ba6-aab9-849b3c60ab29', 'friendly', 'The staff here are very friendly.', '这里的员工非常友好。'),
  ('1d97bd21-84ce-4ba6-aab9-849b3c60ab29-ex2', '1d97bd21-84ce-4ba6-aab9-849b3c60ab29', 'friendly', 'The seemingly friendly merger masked a contest for outright control.', '这桩看似友好的合并掩盖着一场彻底夺权的较量。'),
  ('369aad9d-7378-43ce-9a1c-ca9f8bd350cd-ex1', '369aad9d-7378-43ce-9a1c-ca9f8bd350cd', 'tournament', 'He won the tennis tournament.', '他赢得了网球锦标赛。'),
  ('369aad9d-7378-43ce-9a1c-ca9f8bd350cd-ex2', '369aad9d-7378-43ce-9a1c-ca9f8bd350cd', 'tournament', 'The tournament''s broadcasting rights were awarded through competitive tender.', '该锦标赛的转播权通过竞争性招标授予。'),
  ('b786c5c2-6442-46c4-989c-bf315c63e85c-ex1', 'b786c5c2-6442-46c4-989c-bf315c63e85c', 'fiction', 'I enjoy reading science fiction.', '我喜欢读科幻小说。'),
  ('b786c5c2-6442-46c4-989c-bf315c63e85c-ex2', 'b786c5c2-6442-46c4-989c-bf315c63e85c', 'fiction', 'The defense maintained that the allegations were fiction unsupported by evidence.', '辩方坚称这些指控纯属虚构，没有证据支持。'),
  ('f820426a-8ef1-4ea6-8a7f-585b6f352b9b-ex1', 'f820426a-8ef1-4ea6-8a7f-585b6f352b9b', 'detect', 'The alarm can detect smoke.', '警报器能探测到烟雾。'),
