  ('22877a9f-165a-4463-ab0a-40bf494156f3-ex1', '22877a9f-165a-4463-ab0a-40bf494156f3', 'senator', 'The senator gave a speech today.', '这位参议员今天发表了讲话。'),
  ('22877a9f-165a-4463-ab0a-40bf494156f3-ex2', '22877a9f-165a-4463-ab0a-40bf494156f3', 'senator', 'The senator''s bill stalled in committee amid bipartisan reservations.', '这位参议员的法案因两党的保留意见而在委员会搁浅。'),
  ('756a9cef-7ca5-4b33-a3a2-a153de410db1-ex1', '756a9cef-7ca5-4b33-a3a2-a153de410db1', 'hunting', 'They went hunting in the forest.', '他们去森林里打猎了。'),
  ('756a9cef-7ca5-4b33-a3a2-a153de410db1-ex2', '756a9cef-7ca5-4b33-a3a2-a153de410db1', 'hunting', 'The treaty restricts hunting of species listed in its protected annex.', '该条约限制猎捕其保护附件所列物种。'),
  ('52bc923f-081e-454d-ae49-389ad13e235f-ex1', '52bc923f-081e-454d-ae49-389ad13e235f', 'salad', 'I made a green salad for lunch.', '我午餐做了一份蔬菜沙拉。'),
  ('52bc923f-081e-454d-ae49-389ad13e235f-ex2', '52bc923f-081e-454d-ae49-389ad13e235f', 'salad', 'The import standards apply to every salad green entering the common market.', '进口标准适用于进入共同市场的每一种沙拉蔬菜。'),
  ('c955dc56-cd9e-4917-b560-683d249e3f4d-ex1', 'c955dc56-cd9e-4917-b560-683d249e3f4d', 'guarantee', 'The phone comes with a one-year guarantee.', '这部手机有一年保修。'),
  ('c955dc56-cd9e-4917-b560-683d249e3f4d-ex2', 'c955dc56-cd9e-4917-b560-683d249e3f4d', 'guarantee', 'The state guarantee distorted risk pricing throughout the sector.', '国家担保扭曲了整个行业的风险定价。'),
  ('b135fb4d-2d6d-48ed-9866-79cc89af4677-ex1', 'b135fb4d-2d6d-48ed-9866-79cc89af4677', 'innocent', 'The court found him innocent.', '法院判他无罪。'),
  ('b135fb4d-2d6d-48ed-9866-79cc89af4677-ex2', 'b135fb4d-2d6d-48ed-9866-79cc89af4677', 'innocent', 'The presumption of innocence persists until guilt is proven beyond doubt.', '在排除合理怀疑地证明有罪之前，无罪推定始终成立。'),
