  ('61597ce4-3fcf-4a54-87b3-48ac53ee187f-ex1', '61597ce4-3fcf-4a54-87b3-48ac53ee187f', 'remote', 'They live in a remote village.', '他们住在一个偏远的村庄。'),
  ('61597ce4-3fcf-4a54-87b3-48ac53ee187f-ex2', '61597ce4-3fcf-4a54-87b3-48ac53ee187f', 'remote', 'The prospect of recovery in such cases is remote and heavily contingent.', '此类案件追偿的可能性很小，且高度取决于具体情况。'),
