  ('f7cb1cef-528b-4460-b11e-cf9e8d56f45d-ex2', 'f7cb1cef-528b-4460-b11e-cf9e8d56f45d', 'bench', 'The matter was referred to a full bench given its constitutional significance.', '鉴于其宪法意义，此案被提交全席法庭审理。'),
  ('76b34377-c693-48d7-98b5-2977c571fad7-ex1', '76b34377-c693-48d7-98b5-2977c571fad7', 'lover', 'She is a great lover of music.', '她非常热爱音乐。'),
  ('76b34377-c693-48d7-98b5-2977c571fad7-ex2', '76b34377-c693-48d7-98b5-2977c571fad7', 'lover', 'The estate dispute pitted the heirs against the deceased''s former lover.', '这场遗产纠纷使继承人与死者的旧情人对簿公堂。'),
  ('05c7e85f-d58b-4b0b-88da-29e09f027aad-ex1', '05c7e85f-d58b-4b0b-88da-29e09f027aad', 'raw', 'Don''t eat raw chicken.', '不要吃生鸡肉。'),
  ('05c7e85f-d58b-4b0b-88da-29e09f027aad-ex2', '05c7e85f-d58b-4b0b-88da-29e09f027aad', 'raw', 'Export controls on raw materials reconfigured global processing chains.', '原材料出口管制重构了全球加工链。'),
  ('bde0e45c-1a37-4295-8c61-f58fdd2833fa-ex1', 'bde0e45c-1a37-4295-8c61-f58fdd2833fa', 'awareness', 'The campaign raises health awareness.', '这场活动提高了健康意识。'),
  ('bde0e45c-1a37-4295-8c61-f58fdd2833fa-ex2', 'bde0e45c-1a37-4295-8c61-f58fdd2833fa', 'awareness', 'The directors'' awareness of the risks was established through internal memoranda.', '内部备忘录证明董事们对这些风险是知情的。'),
