  ('c0fd730f-50ea-45b1-a0c0-12630d3379fb-ex2', 'c0fd730f-50ea-45b1-a0c0-12630d3379fb', 'surprising', 'It is hardly surprising that the safeguards failed under correlated stress.', '这些保障措施在关联性压力下失灵，并不令人意外。'),
  ('4594157d-a486-4929-a79b-ebc769756a74-ex1', '4594157d-a486-4929-a79b-ebc769756a74', 'withdraw', 'I need to withdraw some cash.', '我需要取一些现金。'),
