  ('8ee51a7f-976f-4777-a60d-9fb320fb1d89-ex1', '8ee51a7f-976f-4777-a60d-9fb320fb1d89', 'pole', 'The flag hangs from a tall pole.', '旗帜挂在高高的旗杆上。'),
  ('8ee51a7f-976f-4777-a60d-9fb320fb1d89-ex2', '8ee51a7f-976f-4777-a60d-9fb320fb1d89', 'pole', 'The two positions sit at opposite poles of an irreconcilable debate.', '这两种立场处于一场无法调和辩论的两极。'),
