  ('b35c09ba-0a12-4a1c-aa15-637a472f47f8-ex2', 'b35c09ba-0a12-4a1c-aa15-637a472f47f8', 'founder', 'The founder retained voting control through a dual-class share structure.', '创始人通过双重股权结构保留了投票控制权。'),
  ('7a40f9dc-577f-40c0-8de2-816fd5da13dd-ex1', '7a40f9dc-577f-40c0-8de2-816fd5da13dd', 'advanced', 'She is taking an advanced math class.', '她在上高级数学课。'),
  ('7a40f9dc-577f-40c0-8de2-816fd5da13dd-ex2', '7a40f9dc-577f-40c0-8de2-816fd5da13dd', 'advanced', 'Export of advanced semiconductors is subject to stringent licensing controls.', '先进半导体的出口受到严格的许可管制。'),
  ('c920d7d6-70fe-4f70-91b6-5c017acfd252-ex1', 'c920d7d6-70fe-4f70-91b6-5c017acfd252', 'pride', 'She takes pride in her work.', '她为自己的工作感到自豪。'),
  ('c920d7d6-70fe-4f70-91b6-5c017acfd252-ex2', 'c920d7d6-70fe-4f70-91b6-5c017acfd252', 'pride', 'Institutional pride blinded management to warnings that proved well founded.', '机构的自负使管理层无视了后来被证明确有根据的警告。'),
