  ('6b748f2b-a9f2-4080-aa54-0dc2d7143326-ex2', '6b748f2b-a9f2-4080-aa54-0dc2d7143326', 'platform', 'The directive subjects dominant platforms to heightened transparency duties.', '该指令对占主导地位的平台施加了更高的透明度义务。'),
  ('039de641-7844-4b27-b663-01dbf75b3881-ex1', '039de641-7844-4b27-b663-01dbf75b3881', 'finance', 'He studies finance at university.', '他在大学学习金融。'),
  ('039de641-7844-4b27-b663-01dbf75b3881-ex2', '039de641-7844-4b27-b663-01dbf75b3881', 'finance', 'Public finance constraints foreclosed the countercyclical response economists urged.', '公共财政的约束使经济学家所倡导的逆周期应对无从实施。'),
