  ('fec5359f-aefc-408e-a878-c231787dd8e9-ex1', 'fec5359f-aefc-408e-a878-c231787dd8e9', 'adventure', 'Our trip was a great adventure.', '我们的旅行是一次精彩的冒险。'),
  ('fec5359f-aefc-408e-a878-c231787dd8e9-ex2', 'fec5359f-aefc-408e-a878-c231787dd8e9', 'adventure', 'The overseas expansion proved a costly adventure the board later regretted.', '海外扩张被证明是一次代价高昂、董事会后来追悔的冒险。'),
  ('341def87-7220-463f-93a8-df40d8531af5-ex1', '341def87-7220-463f-93a8-df40d8531af5', 'external', 'The hard drive is an external device.', '硬盘是一个外置设备。'),
  ('341def87-7220-463f-93a8-df40d8531af5-ex2', '341def87-7220-463f-93a8-df40d8531af5', 'external', 'External shocks exposed the fragility of the country''s debt position.', '外部冲击暴露了该国债务状况的脆弱性。'),
  ('61e2c21c-a2b7-44fa-b137-882c8310feb4-ex1', '61e2c21c-a2b7-44fa-b137-882c8310feb4', 'proof', 'Do you have proof of purchase?', '你有购买凭证吗？'),
  ('61e2c21c-a2b7-44fa-b137-882c8310feb4-ex2', '61e2c21c-a2b7-44fa-b137-882c8310feb4', 'proof', 'The burden of proof rests with the party alleging the misconduct.', '举证责任在于指控不当行为的一方。'),
  ('2fb9858a-0c11-473e-98d0-d0fafbf850d1-ex1', '2fb9858a-0c11-473e-98d0-d0fafbf850d1', 'confident', 'I am confident we will win.', '我有信心我们会赢。'),
  ('2fb9858a-0c11-473e-98d0-d0fafbf850d1-ex2', '2fb9858a-0c11-473e-98d0-d0fafbf850d1', 'confident', 'Management remained publicly confident even as reserves quietly evaporated.', '即便储备在悄然蒸发，管理层对外仍表现得信心十足。'),
  ('332dc6fd-759f-49bd-82ea-1c32114fa07b-ex1', '332dc6fd-759f-49bd-82ea-1c32114fa07b', 'headquarters', 'The company''s headquarters is in Tokyo.', '公司总部在东京。'),
  ('332dc6fd-759f-49bd-82ea-1c32114fa07b-ex2', '332dc6fd-759f-49bd-82ea-1c32114fa07b', 'headquarters', 'The relocation of headquarters offshore triggered scrutiny of the tax motivation.', '将总部迁往离岸地引发了对其税务动机的审查。'),
  ('c99fb776-5d93-481d-ab65-c2090da14420-ex1', 'c99fb776-5d93-481d-ab65-c2090da14420', 'sudden', 'There was a sudden change in the weather.', '天气突然变了。'),
  ('c99fb776-5d93-481d-ab65-c2090da14420-ex2', 'c99fb776-5d93-481d-ab65-c2090da14420', 'sudden', 'The sudden withdrawal of liquidity precipitated the institution''s collapse.', '流动性的骤然抽离加速了该机构的崩溃。'),
  ('dd83ca3d-3920-46bb-96e2-1eebbe9b41f8-ex1', 'dd83ca3d-3920-46bb-96e2-1eebbe9b41f8', 'dirty', 'My shoes are dirty.', '我的鞋脏了。'),
