  ('15b15fc3-536e-41e8-ad9a-6b76683ab107-ex1', '15b15fc3-536e-41e8-ad9a-6b76683ab107', 'license', 'You need a license to drive.', '开车需要驾照。'),
  ('15b15fc3-536e-41e8-ad9a-6b76683ab107-ex2', '15b15fc3-536e-41e8-ad9a-6b76683ab107', 'license', 'The operating license was revoked for repeated breaches of its conditions.', '运营许可因屡次违反条件而被吊销。'),
  ('99dc4ee3-26b8-42c3-9725-b7b003ea544e-ex1', '99dc4ee3-26b8-42c3-9725-b7b003ea544e', 'shelter', 'We found shelter from the rain.', '我们找到了躲雨的地方。'),
  ('99dc4ee3-26b8-42c3-9725-b7b003ea544e-ex2', '99dc4ee3-26b8-42c3-9725-b7b003ea544e', 'shelter', 'The structure functioned as a tax shelter the legislation subsequently dismantled.', '这一架构曾充当避税工具，后被立法所拆除。'),
