  ('65fffc56-aed4-43e4-847c-1fbecea99ec1-ex1', '65fffc56-aed4-43e4-847c-1fbecea99ec1', 'controversy', 'The decision caused a lot of controversy.', '这个决定引起了很大争议。'),
  ('65fffc56-aed4-43e4-847c-1fbecea99ec1-ex2', '65fffc56-aed4-43e4-847c-1fbecea99ec1', 'controversy', 'The appointment ignited controversy over the independence of the tribunal.', '这项任命引发了关于法庭独立性的争议。'),
  ('b1cf6260-3c15-4665-9ff2-b0d3b02756ac-ex1', 'b1cf6260-3c15-4665-9ff2-b0d3b02756ac', 'entrance', 'The entrance is on the left.', '入口在左边。'),
  ('b1cf6260-3c15-4665-9ff2-b0d3b02756ac-ex2', 'b1cf6260-3c15-4665-9ff2-b0d3b02756ac', 'entrance', 'The licensing regime erects entrance barriers favoring established operators.', '许可制度竖起的准入壁垒偏向于既有经营者。'),
  ('e15c373c-8701-4d1e-9dc3-b7e6ec385dd0-ex1', 'e15c373c-8701-4d1e-9dc3-b7e6ec385dd0', 'properly', 'Did you close the door properly?', '你把门关好了吗？'),
  ('e15c373c-8701-4d1e-9dc3-b7e6ec385dd0-ex2', 'e15c373c-8701-4d1e-9dc3-b7e6ec385dd0', 'properly', 'The notice, not properly served, failed to terminate the tenancy.', '该通知因未妥善送达，未能产生终止租约的效力。'),
  ('4e59465e-20be-4909-a398-68fe1548a9b1-ex1', '4e59465e-20be-4909-a398-68fe1548a9b1', 'fade', 'The colors fade in the sun.', '颜色在阳光下会褪色。'),
