  ('2106a335-3914-49e4-a477-37c89fcdf7d4-ex2', '2106a335-3914-49e4-a477-37c89fcdf7d4', 'tragedy', 'The inquiry concluded that the tragedy was eminently preventable.', '调查认定这场悲剧本来完全可以避免。'),
  ('1707e815-b69f-490c-b05c-a1cbc8d83442-ex1', '1707e815-b69f-490c-b05c-a1cbc8d83442', 'net', 'The fish escaped through the net.', '鱼从网里逃走了。'),
  ('1707e815-b69f-490c-b05c-a1cbc8d83442-ex2', '1707e815-b69f-490c-b05c-a1cbc8d83442', 'net', 'Net liabilities exceeded reported assets by a startling margin.', '净负债超出账面资产的幅度令人吃惊。'),
  ('094e652a-456f-4c05-9818-99d53a4a00ca-ex1', '094e652a-456f-4c05-9818-99d53a4a00ca', 'characterize', 'How would you characterize the book?', '你会怎么评价这本书？'),
