  ('5166c87c-8451-4689-bb6e-954e85cdbf4e-ex2', '5166c87c-8451-4689-bb6e-954e85cdbf4e', 'profession', 'The disciplinary board may bar offenders from the profession entirely.', '惩戒委员会可将违规者彻底逐出该行业。'),
