  ('abc00576-e338-4224-bb93-01276f210d27-ex1', 'abc00576-e338-4224-bb93-01276f210d27', 'imagination', 'The story sparks children''s imagination.', '这个故事激发了孩子们的想象力。'),
  ('abc00576-e338-4224-bb93-01276f210d27-ex2', 'abc00576-e338-4224-bb93-01276f210d27', 'imagination', 'The scale of the fraud strained even the investigators'' imagination.', '这起欺诈的规模之大连调查人员都难以想象。'),
  ('7edd79de-dfc4-493d-a6a4-694f48633a83-ex1', '7edd79de-dfc4-493d-a6a4-694f48633a83', 'mask', 'He wore a mask to the party.', '他戴着面具去参加聚会。'),
