  ('dd6f98eb-db6f-4d37-928c-88ef6eceacbc-ex2', 'dd6f98eb-db6f-4d37-928c-88ef6eceacbc', 'load', 'The case load overwhelmed a tribunal designed for a fraction of the volume.', '案件量压垮了一个仅按少量案件设计的法庭。'),
  ('178d4ae4-d326-449a-8763-5547380d7be2-ex1', '178d4ae4-d326-449a-8763-5547380d7be2', 'stable', 'The ladder is stable now.', '梯子现在稳了。'),
  ('178d4ae4-d326-449a-8763-5547380d7be2-ex2', '178d4ae4-d326-449a-8763-5547380d7be2', 'stable', 'A stable currency is the bedrock of credible long-term contracting.', '稳定的货币是可信的长期缔约的基石。'),
  ('0f23f453-aa4b-4179-a0e8-52f7a896b1a6-ex1', '0f23f453-aa4b-4179-a0e8-52f7a896b1a6', 'introduction', 'The introduction explains the main idea.', '引言阐明了主旨。'),
