  ('c64cf0c3-6e0e-46c7-b525-1c0083fc996d-ex1', 'c64cf0c3-6e0e-46c7-b525-1c0083fc996d', 'pretend', 'The kids pretend to be pirates.', '孩子们假扮海盗。'),
  ('c64cf0c3-6e0e-46c7-b525-1c0083fc996d-ex2', 'c64cf0c3-6e0e-46c7-b525-1c0083fc996d', 'pretend', 'Management could no longer pretend that the losses were merely cyclical.', '管理层再也无法佯称这些亏损只是周期性的。'),
  ('a81c9910-d799-42b3-bdfe-441768c1bee3-ex1', 'a81c9910-d799-42b3-bdfe-441768c1bee3', 'elderly', 'The elderly woman needs help crossing.', '那位老妇人过马路需要帮助。'),
  ('a81c9910-d799-42b3-bdfe-441768c1bee3-ex2', 'a81c9910-d799-42b3-bdfe-441768c1bee3', 'elderly', 'The reforms extend home-based care entitlements to the frail elderly.', '这些改革将居家照护权利扩展至体弱的老年人。'),
  ('465bfb37-6dd5-460d-b623-c984337c6a76-ex1', '465bfb37-6dd5-460d-b623-c984337c6a76', 'representation', 'The lawyer offered free representation.', '律师提供了免费代理。'),
  ('465bfb37-6dd5-460d-b623-c984337c6a76-ex2', '465bfb37-6dd5-460d-b623-c984337c6a76', 'representation', 'The claim rests on representations the issuer expressly disclaimed.', '该索赔依据的是发行人已明确否认的陈述。'),
  ('c03482b0-b671-4b9d-b993-e282be34f7db-ex1', 'c03482b0-b671-4b9d-b993-e282be34f7db', 'deer', 'A deer ran across the road.', '一只鹿跑过了马路。'),
