  ('6ade7c60-4c24-49ef-9123-e8ad7d49b818-ex2', '6ade7c60-4c24-49ef-9123-e8ad7d49b818', 'satisfy', 'The applicant must satisfy every statutory criterion before approval issues.', '申请人必须满足每一项法定标准，方可获得批准。'),
