  ('9973d938-251f-4424-8652-7707f6d4f444-ex2', '9973d938-251f-4424-8652-7707f6d4f444', 'pile', 'Unprocessed claims piled up faster than the tribunal could adjudicate them.', '未处理的索赔积压的速度超过了法庭审结的速度。'),
  ('c26eb8a7-1b4f-4a53-9361-07b53bdb86b3-ex1', 'c26eb8a7-1b4f-4a53-9361-07b53bdb86b3', 'briefly', 'Let me explain briefly.', '让我简单解释一下。'),
  ('c26eb8a7-1b4f-4a53-9361-07b53bdb86b3-ex2', 'c26eb8a7-1b4f-4a53-9361-07b53bdb86b3', 'briefly', 'The court addressed the constitutional question only briefly before deciding otherwise.', '法院仅简短地触及宪法问题，便以其他理由作出裁决。'),
  ('f62c1c20-54ff-41ff-aa1a-23d953f1c9be-ex1', 'f62c1c20-54ff-41ff-aa1a-23d953f1c9be', 'carbon', 'Trees absorb carbon from the air.', '树木从空气中吸收碳。'),
  ('f62c1c20-54ff-41ff-aa1a-23d953f1c9be-ex2', 'f62c1c20-54ff-41ff-aa1a-23d953f1c9be', 'carbon', 'The carbon levy is calibrated to verified emission volumes.', '碳税按经核实的排放量进行核算。'),
  ('879cc233-cab7-4d18-8919-6f1e8b6cac54-ex1', '879cc233-cab7-4d18-8919-6f1e8b6cac54', 'closer', 'Move closer so I can hear you.', '靠近一点，我才能听见你说话。'),
  ('879cc233-cab7-4d18-8919-6f1e8b6cac54-ex2', '879cc233-cab7-4d18-8919-6f1e8b6cac54', 'closer', 'Closer scrutiny revealed transactions structured to evade the threshold.', '更仔细的审查发现了为规避门槛而设计的交易。'),
  ('89418a60-7479-4226-b724-b8ede4548378-ex1', '89418a60-7479-4226-b724-b8ede4548378', 'consume', 'We consume too much sugar.', '我们摄入了太多糖。'),
  ('89418a60-7479-4226-b724-b8ede4548378-ex2', '89418a60-7479-4226-b724-b8ede4548378', 'consume', 'Rising input costs consume the margins of even efficient producers.', '投入成本上升侵蚀了即使是高效生产商的利润。'),
  ('40538c66-a3ff-4ed9-ba40-03bbe51fc54b-ex1', '40538c66-a3ff-4ed9-ba40-03bbe51fc54b', 'scheme', 'They came up with a clever scheme.', '他们想出了一个巧妙的方案。'),
  ('40538c66-a3ff-4ed9-ba40-03bbe51fc54b-ex2', '40538c66-a3ff-4ed9-ba40-03bbe51fc54b', 'scheme', 'The indictment alleges a scheme to defraud investors over several years.', '起诉书指控存在一项历时数年欺诈投资者的计划。'),
  ('38c3616c-6d35-4b80-8c35-15fb26006e4f-ex1', '38c3616c-6d35-4b80-8c35-15fb26006e4f', 'crack', 'There is a crack in the wall.', '墙上有一道裂缝。'),
  ('38c3616c-6d35-4b80-8c35-15fb26006e4f-ex2', '38c3616c-6d35-4b80-8c35-15fb26006e4f', 'crack', 'The crisis exposed cracks in oversight that prosperity had long concealed.', '这场危机暴露了长期被繁荣掩盖的监管裂痕。'),
  ('095b1778-0078-4d71-83c9-a58da861a9e2-ex1', '095b1778-0078-4d71-83c9-a58da861a9e2', 'frequency', 'The buses run with high frequency.', '公交车班次很密。'),
  ('095b1778-0078-4d71-83c9-a58da861a9e2-ex2', '095b1778-0078-4d71-83c9-a58da861a9e2', 'frequency', 'The frequency of violations triggered escalation to formal enforcement.', '违规的频繁程度触发了升级为正式执法。'),
  ('3a975bd5-ab7d-44d4-ab5e-9966925052d7-ex1', '3a975bd5-ab7d-44d4-ab5e-9966925052d7', 'tobacco', 'Tobacco is harmful to health.', '烟草有害健康。'),
  ('3a975bd5-ab7d-44d4-ab5e-9966925052d7-ex2', '3a975bd5-ab7d-44d4-ab5e-9966925052d7', 'tobacco', 'Plain packaging rules apply to every tobacco product sold domestically.', '平装规定适用于国内销售的每一种烟草产品。'),
  ('79a2aeb3-7dc8-46bf-b48e-160b912f1770-ex1', '79a2aeb3-7dc8-46bf-b48e-160b912f1770', 'survivor', 'The survivor was rescued after two days.', '幸存者在两天后获救。'),
  ('79a2aeb3-7dc8-46bf-b48e-160b912f1770-ex2', '79a2aeb3-7dc8-46bf-b48e-160b912f1770', 'survivor', 'The compensation scheme prioritizes survivors of the most severe harm.', '赔偿方案优先照顾遭受最严重伤害的幸存者。'),
  ('fef21e19-38bd-4eb2-8a21-7a41746a09ea-ex1', 'fef21e19-38bd-4eb2-8a21-7a41746a09ea', 'besides', 'Besides tea, we have coffee.', '除了茶，我们还有咖啡。'),
  ('fef21e19-38bd-4eb2-8a21-7a41746a09ea-ex2', 'fef21e19-38bd-4eb2-8a21-7a41746a09ea', 'besides', 'Besides the procedural defects, the award conflicts with mandatory public policy.', '除程序瑕疵外，该裁决还与强制性公共政策相抵触。'),
  ('a1dd81fb-c372-49cc-8763-c87e02dafb08-ex1', 'a1dd81fb-c372-49cc-8763-c87e02dafb08', 'psychologist', 'The psychologist listened carefully.', '心理学家认真倾听。'),
  ('a1dd81fb-c372-49cc-8763-c87e02dafb08-ex2', 'a1dd81fb-c372-49cc-8763-c87e02dafb08', 'psychologist', 'The psychologist''s evaluation was admitted subject to rigorous cross-examination.', '心理学家的评估意见经过严格交叉询问后被采纳。'),
  ('867c9543-6099-4577-a62d-255e1b1a161e-ex1', '867c9543-6099-4577-a62d-255e1b1a161e', 'wealthy', 'They live in a wealthy neighborhood.', '他们住在富裕的社区。'),
  ('867c9543-6099-4577-a62d-255e1b1a161e-ex2', '867c9543-6099-4577-a62d-255e1b1a161e', 'wealthy', 'The levy targets the wealthiest households holding assets above the threshold.', '该税项针对持有超过门槛资产的最富裕家庭。'),
  ('7d036f3a-b7d9-4198-a3ac-fd689208745b-ex1', '7d036f3a-b7d9-4198-a3ac-fd689208745b', 'galaxy', 'Our galaxy contains billions of stars.', '我们的星系包含数十亿颗恒星。'),
  ('7d036f3a-b7d9-4198-a3ac-fd689208745b-ex2', '7d036f3a-b7d9-4198-a3ac-fd689208745b', 'galaxy', 'The telescope mapped galaxies dating to the universe''s earliest epochs.', '这台望远镜描绘了可追溯至宇宙最早期的星系。'),
  ('c4817c39-3342-4ad7-a5e7-733412a1f39e-ex1', 'c4817c39-3342-4ad7-a5e7-733412a1f39e', 'given', 'Given the time, let''s start now.', '考虑到时间，我们现在开始吧。'),
  ('c4817c39-3342-4ad7-a5e7-733412a1f39e-ex2', 'c4817c39-3342-4ad7-a5e7-733412a1f39e', 'given', 'Given the magnitude of the exposure, intervention became unavoidable.', '鉴于风险敞口之大，干预已不可避免。'),
  ('c4dde85e-45eb-4ddb-9ef4-a3a8df5cb604-ex1', 'c4dde85e-45eb-4ddb-9ef4-a3a8df5cb604', 'ski', 'We learned to ski last winter.', '去年冬天我们学会了滑雪。'),
  ('c4dde85e-45eb-4ddb-9ef4-a3a8df5cb604-ex2', 'c4dde85e-45eb-4ddb-9ef4-a3a8df5cb604', 'ski', 'The ski resort''s water permits were revoked amid the prolonged drought.', '在持续干旱期间，这家滑雪场的用水许可被吊销。'),
  ('d6efe1f8-c08c-48dc-9f97-343eba6fe2d1-ex1', 'd6efe1f8-c08c-48dc-9f97-343eba6fe2d1', 'limitation', 'Everyone has their limitations.', '每个人都有自己的局限。'),
  ('d6efe1f8-c08c-48dc-9f97-343eba6fe2d1-ex2', 'd6efe1f8-c08c-48dc-9f97-343eba6fe2d1', 'limitation', 'The claim was time-barred under the applicable statute of limitation.', '根据适用的时效法规，该索赔已超过诉讼时效。'),
  ('2d0da93e-b3be-4f84-a254-808ff89a4b90-ex1', '2d0da93e-b3be-4f84-a254-808ff89a4b90', 'trace', 'There was no trace of the missing cat.', '失踪的猫毫无踪迹。'),
  ('2d0da93e-b3be-4f84-a254-808ff89a4b90-ex2', '2d0da93e-b3be-4f84-a254-808ff89a4b90', 'trace', 'Investigators traced the funds through successive offshore intermediaries.', '调查人员通过一连串离岸中介追踪了这些资金。'),
  ('30ddb8db-76e9-4175-beb8-e6c3dd6bee78-ex1', '30ddb8db-76e9-4175-beb8-e6c3dd6bee78', 'appointment', 'I have a doctor''s appointment at three.', '我三点有个看医生的预约。'),
  ('30ddb8db-76e9-4175-beb8-e6c3dd6bee78-ex2', '30ddb8db-76e9-4175-beb8-e6c3dd6bee78', 'appointment', 'The appointment was challenged for failure to observe the consultation requirement.', '这项任命因未履行咨询要求而受到质疑。'),
  ('79894594-3e51-4a46-8156-ad30711e002c-ex1', '79894594-3e51-4a46-8156-ad30711e002c', 'preference', 'Do you have a color preference?', '你对颜色有偏好吗？'),
  ('79894594-3e51-4a46-8156-ad30711e002c-ex2', '79894594-3e51-4a46-8156-ad30711e002c', 'preference', 'The transfer conferred an unlawful preference voidable in the insolvency.', '这笔转账构成在破产中可撤销的非法优先清偿。'),
  ('902817d6-73f3-4718-840a-067766ff3504-ex1', '902817d6-73f3-4718-840a-067766ff3504', 'meter', 'The pool is two meters deep.', '泳池有两米深。'),
  ('902817d6-73f3-4718-840a-067766ff3504-ex2', '902817d6-73f3-4718-840a-067766ff3504', 'meter', 'Smart meters enable consumption-based tariffs across the distribution grid.', '智能电表使配电网络能够实行基于用量的电价。'),
  ('07eea547-66f9-4833-8502-3605cddd6756-ex1', '07eea547-66f9-4833-8502-3605cddd6756', 'explosion', 'The explosion was heard miles away.', '爆炸声在数英里外都能听到。'),
  ('07eea547-66f9-4833-8502-3605cddd6756-ex2', '07eea547-66f9-4833-8502-3605cddd6756', 'explosion', 'The inquiry attributed the explosion to a sustained erosion of safety standards.', '调查将这次爆炸归因于安全标准的持续滑坡。'),
  ('e6741b07-be0c-430f-9d12-fe8060b82018-ex1', 'e6741b07-be0c-430f-9d12-fe8060b82018', 'publicly', 'She publicly thanked her team.', '她公开感谢了她的团队。'),
  ('e6741b07-be0c-430f-9d12-fe8060b82018-ex2', 'e6741b07-be0c-430f-9d12-fe8060b82018', 'publicly', 'The settlement terms were sealed and never disclosed publicly.', '和解条款被封存，从未公开披露。'),
  ('758b6fbc-3632-4811-a5f0-1eec7091296e-ex1', '758b6fbc-3632-4811-a5f0-1eec7091296e', 'incredible', 'The view was absolutely incredible.', '景色实在令人惊叹。'),
  ('758b6fbc-3632-4811-a5f0-1eec7091296e-ex2', '758b6fbc-3632-4811-a5f0-1eec7091296e', 'incredible', 'The scale of the concealment was incredible even to seasoned investigators.', '隐瞒的规模之大连资深调查人员都难以置信。'),
  ('9c20b55d-330d-4e9d-8289-d7f7eb01f830-ex1', '9c20b55d-330d-4e9d-8289-d7f7eb01f830', 'fighter', 'The fighter trained for months.', '这名拳手训练了几个月。'),
  ('9c20b55d-330d-4e9d-8289-d7f7eb01f830-ex2', '9c20b55d-330d-4e9d-8289-d7f7eb01f830', 'fighter', 'She earned a reputation as a determined fighter for consumer rights.', '她以坚定的消费者权益斗士而闻名。'),
  ('fc393d31-3359-4d17-951a-d0c623608b09-ex1', 'fc393d31-3359-4d17-951a-d0c623608b09', 'rapid', 'The river has rapid currents.', '这条河水流湍急。'),
  ('fc393d31-3359-4d17-951a-d0c623608b09-ex2', 'fc393d31-3359-4d17-951a-d0c623608b09', 'rapid', 'Rapid financial innovation continually outpaces the rules meant to govern it.', '快速的金融创新不断超越本应规范它的规则。'),
  ('6cc32168-98ff-4a35-9244-216688f20222-ex1', '6cc32168-98ff-4a35-9244-216688f20222', 'admission', 'Admission to the museum is free.', '博物馆免费入场。'),
  ('6cc32168-98ff-4a35-9244-216688f20222-ex2', '6cc32168-98ff-4a35-9244-216688f20222', 'admission', 'The admission of liability was carefully qualified to limit its scope.', '对责任的承认经过审慎限定，以控制其范围。'),
  ('3c73e3f4-4381-4666-9bc3-3b00784b00e6-ex1', '3c73e3f4-4381-4666-9bc3-3b00784b00e6', 'hunter', 'The hunter tracked the deer for hours.', '猎人追踪那只鹿好几个小时。'),
  ('3c73e3f4-4381-4666-9bc3-3b00784b00e6-ex2', '3c73e3f4-4381-4666-9bc3-3b00784b00e6', 'hunter', 'Licensed hunters must report every kill under the conservation regime.', '根据保护制度，持证猎人必须报告每一次捕猎。'),
  ('8d43f500-2083-44a2-8e90-e1c5c6f8ebfc-ex1', '8d43f500-2083-44a2-8e90-e1c5c6f8ebfc', 'educate', 'We must educate children about safety.', '我们必须教育孩子注意安全。'),
  ('8d43f500-2083-44a2-8e90-e1c5c6f8ebfc-ex2', '8d43f500-2083-44a2-8e90-e1c5c6f8ebfc', 'educate', 'The campaign sought to educate consumers about their statutory rights.', '该活动旨在向消费者普及其法定权利。'),
  ('19b615b1-8992-4a97-aad2-ffaadd56a79d-ex1', '19b615b1-8992-4a97-aad2-ffaadd56a79d', 'painful', 'The injury was very painful.', '这处伤很疼。'),
  ('19b615b1-8992-4a97-aad2-ffaadd56a79d-ex2', '19b615b1-8992-4a97-aad2-ffaadd56a79d', 'painful', 'The restructuring imposed painful losses on the most junior creditors.', '重组使最次级的债权人承受了痛苦的损失。'),
  ('7619b143-b219-4fa8-8b28-96b381ee5148-ex1', '7619b143-b219-4fa8-8b28-96b381ee5148', 'friendship', 'Their friendship lasted a lifetime.', '他们的友谊持续了一生。'),
  ('7619b143-b219-4fa8-8b28-96b381ee5148-ex2', '7619b143-b219-4fa8-8b28-96b381ee5148', 'friendship', 'The treaty of friendship masked deepening commercial rivalry between the states.', '这份友好条约掩盖了两国之间日益加深的商业竞争。'),
  ('f792d400-7c89-49ce-807e-afb6e147b8c6-ex1', 'f792d400-7c89-49ce-807e-afb6e147b8c6', 'aide', 'The senator''s aide answered the call.', '参议员的助手接了电话。'),
  ('f792d400-7c89-49ce-807e-afb6e147b8c6-ex2', 'f792d400-7c89-49ce-807e-afb6e147b8c6', 'aide', 'A senior aide testified about the deliberations preceding the decision.', '一名高级助手就决定作出前的讨论出庭作证。'),
  ('23fcc84f-7fdc-4c07-a568-98a799407b5f-ex1', '23fcc84f-7fdc-4c07-a568-98a799407b5f', 'infant', 'The infant slept through the night.', '婴儿一夜睡到天亮。'),
  ('23fcc84f-7fdc-4c07-a568-98a799407b5f-ex2', '23fcc84f-7fdc-4c07-a568-98a799407b5f', 'infant', 'The trial excluded infants for whom the dosage had not been validated.', '该试验排除了尚未验证用药剂量的婴儿。'),
  ('586c08a8-f349-4a0d-bafc-d4aec1885df3-ex1', '586c08a8-f349-4a0d-bafc-d4aec1885df3', 'calculate', 'Calculate the total cost first.', '先算出总成本。'),
  ('586c08a8-f349-4a0d-bafc-d4aec1885df3-ex2', '586c08a8-f349-4a0d-bafc-d4aec1885df3', 'calculate', 'Damages are calculated by reference to the loss actually sustained.', '损害赔偿以实际遭受的损失为依据计算。'),
  ('df14e723-8a9b-4489-86dc-6a39c0c63fe1-ex1', 'df14e723-8a9b-4489-86dc-6a39c0c63fe1', 'fifty', 'The book has fifty pages.', '这本书有五十页。'),
  ('df14e723-8a9b-4489-86dc-6a39c0c63fe1-ex2', 'df14e723-8a9b-4489-86dc-6a39c0c63fe1', 'fifty', 'The fund''s losses approached fifty percent before redemptions were suspended.', '在暂停赎回之前，该基金的亏损接近百分之五十。'),
  ('4b2cab01-14c7-41c4-b467-f06dcbd2b3cd-ex1', '4b2cab01-14c7-41c4-b467-f06dcbd2b3cd', 'rid', 'I want to get rid of these old shoes.', '我想扔掉这些旧鞋。'),
  ('4b2cab01-14c7-41c4-b467-f06dcbd2b3cd-ex2', '4b2cab01-14c7-41c4-b467-f06dcbd2b3cd', 'rid', 'The reforms aim to rid the framework of exemptions ripe for abuse.', '这些改革旨在清除框架中易被滥用的豁免条款。'),
  ('6db336ba-b45a-4916-97ee-a8cc11a2ed65-ex1', '6db336ba-b45a-4916-97ee-a8cc11a2ed65', 'porch', 'We sat on the porch in the evening.', '傍晚我们坐在门廊上。'),
  ('6db336ba-b45a-4916-97ee-a8cc11a2ed65-ex2', '6db336ba-b45a-4916-97ee-a8cc11a2ed65', 'porch', 'The package was left on the porch without the required signature.', '包裹在未取得所需签收的情况下被放在门廊上。'),
  ('191b6b2f-d462-4a45-a164-b65d3a6dab9f-ex1', '191b6b2f-d462-4a45-a164-b65d3a6dab9f', 'tendency', 'He has a tendency to arrive late.', '他有迟到的习惯。'),
  ('191b6b2f-d462-4a45-a164-b65d3a6dab9f-ex2', '191b6b2f-d462-4a45-a164-b65d3a6dab9f', 'tendency', 'Concentrated markets exhibit a tendency toward consumer-adverse pricing.', '高度集中的市场倾向于出现损害消费者利益的定价。'),
  ('50f6ccb5-36c5-440d-a8fe-ad0e259d1792-ex1', '50f6ccb5-36c5-440d-a8fe-ad0e259d1792', 'uniform', 'Students wear a uniform to school.', '学生穿校服上学。'),
  ('50f6ccb5-36c5-440d-a8fe-ad0e259d1792-ex2', '50f6ccb5-36c5-440d-a8fe-ad0e259d1792', 'uniform', 'The directive aims at uniform application of standards across all jurisdictions.', '该指令旨在使标准在所有司法管辖区统一适用。'),
  ('00eb2fad-8120-49fa-882e-8ab622ab169e-ex1', '00eb2fad-8120-49fa-882e-8ab622ab169e', 'formation', 'The birds flew in a V formation.', '鸟儿排成V字形飞翔。'),
  ('00eb2fad-8120-49fa-882e-8ab622ab169e-ex2', '00eb2fad-8120-49fa-882e-8ab622ab169e', 'formation', 'Consideration must be present at the formation of an enforceable contract.', '在订立可执行合同时必须存在对价。'),
  ('bfb98bd8-0ed7-4206-bddb-bafb361a1f49-ex1', 'bfb98bd8-0ed7-4206-bddb-bafb361a1f49', 'scholarship', 'She won a scholarship to university.', '她获得了大学奖学金。'),
