  ('f12bcae9-db77-440c-a50a-c002ffeaa89d-ex1', 'f12bcae9-db77-440c-a50a-c002ffeaa89d', 'loud', 'The music is too loud.', '音乐太吵了。'),
  ('f12bcae9-db77-440c-a50a-c002ffeaa89d-ex2', 'f12bcae9-db77-440c-a50a-c002ffeaa89d', 'loud', 'The dissent constitutes a loud warning against unchecked delegation.', '这份异议意见是对不受约束的授权发出的响亮警告。'),
  ('e2c0350d-7182-4e5a-b57d-3f682b5f7e36-ex1', 'e2c0350d-7182-4e5a-b57d-3f682b5f7e36', 'glove', 'Wear gloves when it is cold.', '天冷时戴上手套。'),
