  ('9f294ca5-86d0-49b0-94eb-56a4e2da74a3-ex1', '9f294ca5-86d0-49b0-94eb-56a4e2da74a3', 'sufficient', 'Is one bottle sufficient for everyone?', '一瓶够大家喝吗？'),
