  ('29653c76-f1dc-418e-ad14-dd6c8998ea80-ex1', '29653c76-f1dc-418e-ad14-dd6c8998ea80', 'helicopter', 'A helicopter flew over the city.', '一架直升机飞过城市上空。'),
  ('29653c76-f1dc-418e-ad14-dd6c8998ea80-ex2', '29653c76-f1dc-418e-ad14-dd6c8998ea80', 'helicopter', 'Rescue helicopters reached the stranded communities within the critical window.', '救援直升机在关键时间窗内抵达了被困社区。'),
  ('2911a696-fbb3-480e-90b4-2c2f8c520778-ex1', '2911a696-fbb3-480e-90b4-2c2f8c520778', 'modest', 'She is modest about her success.', '她对自己的成就很谦虚。'),
  ('2911a696-fbb3-480e-90b4-2c2f8c520778-ex2', '2911a696-fbb3-480e-90b4-2c2f8c520778', 'modest', 'The reforms produced modest gains far short of their stated objectives.', '这些改革成效有限，远未达到既定目标。'),
  ('e7951154-327d-4f00-aa91-050f2210336c-ex1', 'e7951154-327d-4f00-aa91-050f2210336c', 'provider', 'Our internet provider raised its prices.', '我们的网络供应商涨价了。'),
  ('e7951154-327d-4f00-aa91-050f2210336c-ex2', 'e7951154-327d-4f00-aa91-050f2210336c', 'provider', 'Service providers bear graduated obligations proportionate to the risks they create.', '服务提供者根据其制造的风险承担相应递进的义务。'),
  ('7011ef00-bbab-4bfc-b4f0-d2d264498a7b-ex1', '7011ef00-bbab-4bfc-b4f0-d2d264498a7b', 'delay', 'The flight had a two-hour delay.', '航班延误了两个小时。'),
  ('7011ef00-bbab-4bfc-b4f0-d2d264498a7b-ex2', '7011ef00-bbab-4bfc-b4f0-d2d264498a7b', 'delay', 'The delay in remediation compounded the harm and inflated the eventual cost.', '整改的拖延加重了损害，并推高了最终成本。'),
  ('20499249-1392-42b0-91d1-972725e4f2aa-ex1', '20499249-1392-42b0-91d1-972725e4f2aa', 'agricultural', 'This is rich agricultural land.', '这是肥沃的农业用地。'),
  ('20499249-1392-42b0-91d1-972725e4f2aa-ex2', '20499249-1392-42b0-91d1-972725e4f2aa', 'agricultural', 'The accord secured safeguards for agricultural exports from developing economies.', '该协定为发展中经济体的农产品出口争取到了保障条款。'),
  ('c25709d7-55a9-4f8f-8c5f-905293569f08-ex1', 'c25709d7-55a9-4f8f-8c5f-905293569f08', 'explode', 'The firework exploded in the sky.', '烟花在空中绽放。'),
  ('c25709d7-55a9-4f8f-8c5f-905293569f08-ex2', 'c25709d7-55a9-4f8f-8c5f-905293569f08', 'explode', 'Demand exploded once the subsidy was announced, overwhelming the program.', '补贴一经宣布，需求骤增，使该项目应接不暇。'),
  ('3d3fa90f-55bf-4a95-9912-0642046fb561-ex1', '3d3fa90f-55bf-4a95-9912-0642046fb561', 'stroke', 'He had a stroke last year.', '他去年中风了。'),
  ('3d3fa90f-55bf-4a95-9912-0642046fb561-ex2', '3d3fa90f-55bf-4a95-9912-0642046fb561', 'stroke', 'With a stroke of the pen, the decree nullified decades of regulatory practice.', '一纸法令大笔一挥，便否定了数十年的监管实践。'),
  ('caeadf05-12d2-4bd7-960a-2029407d6242-ex1', 'caeadf05-12d2-4bd7-960a-2029407d6242', 'scope', 'The project''s scope is quite large.', '项目的范围相当大。'),
  ('caeadf05-12d2-4bd7-960a-2029407d6242-ex2', 'caeadf05-12d2-4bd7-960a-2029407d6242', 'scope', 'The court construed the exemption narrowly to confine its scope.', '法院对该豁免作狭义解释，以限定其适用范围。'),
  ('9ba889d3-1978-42ec-bbd6-152a1bd8cb96-ex1', '9ba889d3-1978-42ec-bbd6-152a1bd8cb96', 'punishment', 'The punishment seemed too harsh.', '这个惩罚似乎太严厉了。'),
  ('9ba889d3-1978-42ec-bbd6-152a1bd8cb96-ex2', '9ba889d3-1978-42ec-bbd6-152a1bd8cb96', 'punishment', 'The punishment must be proportionate to the gravity of the offense.', '惩罚必须与罪行的严重程度相称。'),
  ('6550863e-3738-4126-8531-9ed5e7c2ea74-ex1', '6550863e-3738-4126-8531-9ed5e7c2ea74', 'handful', 'He grabbed a handful of nuts.', '他抓了一把坚果。'),
