  ('1ee61406-d1c4-4df3-b024-e5a30c12863f-ex1', '1ee61406-d1c4-4df3-b024-e5a30c12863f', 'badly', 'The team played badly today.', '球队今天表现很差。'),
  ('1ee61406-d1c4-4df3-b024-e5a30c12863f-ex2', '1ee61406-d1c4-4df3-b024-e5a30c12863f', 'badly', 'The contracts were drafted so badly that litigation became inevitable.', '这些合同起草得如此拙劣，以致诉讼在所难免。'),
