  ('3a38e0c8-1b0f-4d11-8981-8513c4f7bbef-ex2', '3a38e0c8-1b0f-4d11-8981-8513c4f7bbef', 'horizon', 'Long electoral horizons systematically disadvantage long-term infrastructure planning.', '漫长的选举视野系统性地不利于长期基础设施规划。'),
