  ('ef93aba0-9a23-4567-9dbf-a3973c5b199e-ex1', 'ef93aba0-9a23-4567-9dbf-a3973c5b199e', 'downtown', 'We work downtown.', '我们在市中心上班。'),
  ('ef93aba0-9a23-4567-9dbf-a3973c5b199e-ex2', 'ef93aba0-9a23-4567-9dbf-a3973c5b199e', 'downtown', 'The downtown revitalization displaced long-standing low-income residents.', '市中心的复兴改造使长期居住的低收入居民被迫迁离。'),
  ('82709415-8c32-4063-be98-37933547876f-ex1', '82709415-8c32-4063-be98-37933547876f', 'girlfriend', 'He introduced his girlfriend to us.', '他向我们介绍了他的女朋友。'),
