  ('f16481f2-d1a5-4686-b9e7-b3d5c8de18ac-ex1', 'f16481f2-d1a5-4686-b9e7-b3d5c8de18ac', 'taxpayer', 'The road was paid for by taxpayers.', '这条路是纳税人出钱修的。'),
  ('f16481f2-d1a5-4686-b9e7-b3d5c8de18ac-ex2', 'f16481f2-d1a5-4686-b9e7-b3d5c8de18ac', 'taxpayer', 'The bailout transferred private losses squarely onto the taxpayer.', '这次救助把私人亏损直接转嫁给了纳税人。'),
  ('b90ae8c2-bd3f-44f6-a456-993d95497ee6-ex1', 'b90ae8c2-bd3f-44f6-a456-993d95497ee6', 'eager', 'The students are eager to learn.', '学生们渴望学习。'),
  ('b90ae8c2-bd3f-44f6-a456-993d95497ee6-ex2', 'b90ae8c2-bd3f-44f6-a456-993d95497ee6', 'eager', 'Investors eager for yield overlooked the credit risk embedded in the structure.', '急于追逐收益的投资者忽视了这一结构中蕴含的信用风险。'),
