  ('204f388e-6714-43ab-bda6-bfc5a529835f-ex2', '204f388e-6714-43ab-bda6-bfc5a529835f', 'assignment', 'The assignment of receivables was perfected by registration under the statute.', '应收账款的转让通过依法登记而得到完善。'),
