  ('789a1954-9eee-4713-97e0-fc2ec33e8a71-ex2', '789a1954-9eee-4713-97e0-fc2ec33e8a71', 'workshop', 'The workshop convened experts to draft model rules for cross-border enforcement.', '该研讨会召集专家起草跨境执法的示范规则。'),
  ('60199e1d-4b58-46e4-be53-3374014da7b6-ex1', '60199e1d-4b58-46e4-be53-3374014da7b6', 'differently', 'She sees the problem differently.', '她对这个问题有不同的看法。'),
  ('60199e1d-4b58-46e4-be53-3374014da7b6-ex2', '60199e1d-4b58-46e4-be53-3374014da7b6', 'differently', 'Comparable claimants must not be treated differently absent objective justification.', '在没有客观理由的情况下，处境相同的索赔人不得受到差别对待。'),
  ('d22ab1ac-2c8b-4e97-97d3-c4cce457c116-ex1', 'd22ab1ac-2c8b-4e97-97d3-c4cce457c116', 'auto', 'He works in the auto industry.', '他在汽车行业工作。'),
  ('d22ab1ac-2c8b-4e97-97d3-c4cce457c116-ex2', 'd22ab1ac-2c8b-4e97-97d3-c4cce457c116', 'auto', 'Stricter emission standards compelled auto manufacturers to accelerate electrification.', '更严格的排放标准迫使汽车制造商加快电动化。'),
  ('c95fdebb-5394-4c1d-ab9d-ce8a122e39e3-ex1', 'c95fdebb-5394-4c1d-ab9d-ce8a122e39e3', 'romantic', 'They had a romantic dinner.', '他们共进了一顿浪漫的晚餐。'),
  ('c95fdebb-5394-4c1d-ab9d-ce8a122e39e3-ex2', 'c95fdebb-5394-4c1d-ab9d-ce8a122e39e3', 'romantic', 'The romantic notion of self-correcting markets has been repeatedly disproved.', '市场能自我纠正的浪漫想法已被一再证伪。'),
  ('53d958e7-2dc3-4fbe-879a-18379cb3e977-ex1', '53d958e7-2dc3-4fbe-879a-18379cb3e977', 'cotton', 'The shirt is made of cotton.', '这件衬衫是棉的。'),
  ('53d958e7-2dc3-4fbe-879a-18379cb3e977-ex2', '53d958e7-2dc3-4fbe-879a-18379cb3e977', 'cotton', 'The cotton tariffs reshaped sourcing decisions across the textile supply chain.', '棉花关税重塑了整条纺织供应链的采购决策。'),
  ('f14342bc-36be-4720-b7f9-76ac7c818542-ex1', 'f14342bc-36be-4720-b7f9-76ac7c818542', 'motor', 'The toy car has a small motor.', '这辆玩具车有一个小马达。'),
  ('f14342bc-36be-4720-b7f9-76ac7c818542-ex2', 'f14342bc-36be-4720-b7f9-76ac7c818542', 'motor', 'The motor industry faces structural transformation as electrification accelerates.', '随着电动化加速，汽车行业面临结构性转型。'),
