  ('a3aab252-bcf7-47cf-9c3e-6c4598f44de1-ex1', 'a3aab252-bcf7-47cf-9c3e-6c4598f44de1', 'shore', 'We walked along the shore.', '我们沿着岸边散步。'),
  ('a3aab252-bcf7-47cf-9c3e-6c4598f44de1-ex2', 'a3aab252-bcf7-47cf-9c3e-6c4598f44de1', 'shore', 'The emergency facility was deployed to shore up confidence in the banking system.', '这项紧急安排被用来支撑对银行体系的信心。'),
  ('bd8f6557-5bbd-41a2-a3cf-1cf25134ce21-ex1', 'bd8f6557-5bbd-41a2-a3cf-1cf25134ce21', 'repeatedly', 'She repeatedly asked for help.', '她一再请求帮助。'),
  ('bd8f6557-5bbd-41a2-a3cf-1cf25134ce21-ex2', 'bd8f6557-5bbd-41a2-a3cf-1cf25134ce21', 'repeatedly', 'Internal memoranda repeatedly warned of the failure that later materialized.', '内部备忘录一再警告后来发生的那种失灵。'),
  ('2d7459db-07ab-49b3-a5ad-c50c29c9497e-ex1', '2d7459db-07ab-49b3-a5ad-c50c29c9497e', 'lung', 'Smoking damages your lungs.', '吸烟会损害肺部。'),
  ('2d7459db-07ab-49b3-a5ad-c50c29c9497e-ex2', '2d7459db-07ab-49b3-a5ad-c50c29c9497e', 'lung', 'Long-term exposure to particulates measurably impairs lung function.', '长期接触颗粒物会显著损害肺功能。'),
  ('5374791e-e75e-4d88-9b1a-e27f07495e91-ex1', '5374791e-e75e-4d88-9b1a-e27f07495e91', 'running', 'Running is good exercise.', '跑步是很好的运动。'),
  ('5374791e-e75e-4d88-9b1a-e27f07495e91-ex2', '5374791e-e75e-4d88-9b1a-e27f07495e91', 'running', 'The running costs of the program far exceeded the original projections.', '该项目的运行成本远超最初预测。'),
  ('61844177-7715-4e92-aec2-85655986b582-ex1', '61844177-7715-4e92-aec2-85655986b582', 'distinct', 'The two flavors are quite distinct.', '这两种味道截然不同。'),
  ('61844177-7715-4e92-aec2-85655986b582-ex2', '61844177-7715-4e92-aec2-85655986b582', 'distinct', 'The statute creates a distinct category for systemically important intermediaries.', '该法规为具有系统重要性的中介机构设立了单独类别。'),
  ('c5f53d46-199c-4d16-8933-fc1a54657651-ex1', 'c5f53d46-199c-4d16-8933-fc1a54657651', 'artistic', 'She has great artistic talent.', '她有很高的艺术天赋。'),
  ('c5f53d46-199c-4d16-8933-fc1a54657651-ex2', 'c5f53d46-199c-4d16-8933-fc1a54657651', 'artistic', 'The work''s artistic merit did not exempt it from the defamation analysis.', '作品的艺术价值并不能使其免于诽谤分析。'),
  ('508a6a6d-7789-42bf-98da-d22e8cff2e05-ex1', '508a6a6d-7789-42bf-98da-d22e8cff2e05', 'discourse', 'The book changed public discourse.', '这本书改变了公共话语。'),
  ('508a6a6d-7789-42bf-98da-d22e8cff2e05-ex2', '508a6a6d-7789-42bf-98da-d22e8cff2e05', 'discourse', 'Media consolidation narrowed the diversity of public discourse.', '媒体兼并压缩了公共话语的多样性。'),
  ('edde7f24-026e-4c7d-b091-507c9dc6f6be-ex1', 'edde7f24-026e-4c7d-b091-507c9dc6f6be', 'basket', 'She filled the basket with apples.', '她把篮子装满了苹果。'),
  ('edde7f24-026e-4c7d-b091-507c9dc6f6be-ex2', 'edde7f24-026e-4c7d-b091-507c9dc6f6be', 'basket', 'The index tracks a basket of commodities weighted by trade volume.', '该指数追踪一篮子按贸易量加权的大宗商品。'),
  ('b8e21814-8ac5-42a6-b36a-f692879515a9-ex1', 'b8e21814-8ac5-42a6-b36a-f692879515a9', 'ah', 'Ah, now I understand!', '啊，现在我明白了！'),
