  ('4c6f3f76-1102-44f5-b8a5-3c33aaafe076-ex1', '4c6f3f76-1102-44f5-b8a5-3c33aaafe076', 'fighting', 'The fighting stopped at dawn.', '战斗在黎明时停止了。'),
