  ('7532f2fa-6eb6-4b4f-8e81-13d8edc7eb81-ex1', '7532f2fa-6eb6-4b4f-8e81-13d8edc7eb81', 'competitor', 'Our main competitor lowered prices.', '我们的主要竞争对手降价了。'),
  ('7532f2fa-6eb6-4b4f-8e81-13d8edc7eb81-ex2', '7532f2fa-6eb6-4b4f-8e81-13d8edc7eb81', 'competitor', 'The merger would eliminate the only meaningful competitor in the market.', '此次合并将消灭市场上唯一有实质意义的竞争对手。'),
  ('3d835ba1-3ffd-4a4b-8488-c6717dc75308-ex1', '3d835ba1-3ffd-4a4b-8488-c6717dc75308', 'ugly', 'That is an ugly old building.', '那是一栋丑陋的旧楼。'),
  ('3d835ba1-3ffd-4a4b-8488-c6717dc75308-ex2', '3d835ba1-3ffd-4a4b-8488-c6717dc75308', 'ugly', 'The dispute turned ugly once mutual accusations of bad faith surfaced.', '双方相互指责对方不诚信后，争端变得难看起来。'),
