  ('a7d4fe3d-8386-4cda-ab2f-ca32db816f41-ex2', 'a7d4fe3d-8386-4cda-ab2f-ca32db816f41', 'worried', 'Analysts grew worried that concentrated exposures could amplify any shock.', '分析人士越来越担心，集中的风险敞口可能放大任何冲击。'),
