  ('169f1cef-089d-413d-8706-3f072f84eb23-ex2', '169f1cef-089d-413d-8706-3f072f84eb23', 'portray', 'The testimony portrayed a governance culture bordering on negligence.', '这些证词描绘出一种近乎失职的治理文化。'),
  ('b565e1b1-4785-4581-b257-4d4ad13db1cb-ex1', 'b565e1b1-4785-4581-b257-4d4ad13db1cb', 'powder', 'Add a spoon of cocoa powder.', '加一勺可可粉。'),
  ('b565e1b1-4785-4581-b257-4d4ad13db1cb-ex2', 'b565e1b1-4785-4581-b257-4d4ad13db1cb', 'powder', 'Customs intercepted the consignment of unidentified powder for analysis.', '海关截留了这批不明粉末以供化验。'),
  ('4e30d087-854a-483e-85a8-e5fc53fae500-ex1', '4e30d087-854a-483e-85a8-e5fc53fae500', 'ghost', 'The kids told ghost stories.', '孩子们讲鬼故事。'),
  ('4e30d087-854a-483e-85a8-e5fc53fae500-ex2', '4e30d087-854a-483e-85a8-e5fc53fae500', 'ghost', 'The shell entities were ghosts existing solely to obscure ownership.', '这些空壳实体形同幽灵，存在的唯一目的就是掩盖所有权。'),
  ('c7f6c68d-b304-4f79-992f-efbf715b53d1-ex1', 'c7f6c68d-b304-4f79-992f-efbf715b53d1', 'persuade', 'I persuaded her to join us.', '我说服她加入我们。'),
  ('c7f6c68d-b304-4f79-992f-efbf715b53d1-ex2', 'c7f6c68d-b304-4f79-992f-efbf715b53d1', 'persuade', 'The submissions failed to persuade the panel that the risks were mitigated.', '提交的材料未能说服专家组相信风险已得到缓解。'),
  ('ac09ac8d-0185-4ccf-aa70-5ce17e8fe485-ex1', 'ac09ac8d-0185-4ccf-aa70-5ce17e8fe485', 'moderate', 'The weather is moderate today.', '今天天气温和。'),
  ('ac09ac8d-0185-4ccf-aa70-5ce17e8fe485-ex2', 'ac09ac8d-0185-4ccf-aa70-5ce17e8fe485', 'moderate', 'The reforms produced moderate gains far short of their stated ambitions.', '这些改革成效有限，远未达到其宣称的雄心。'),
