  ('54b1f091-6629-44f3-89f0-5f2f37df0523-ex2', '54b1f091-6629-44f3-89f0-5f2f37df0523', 'subsequent', 'Subsequent events confirmed warnings the board had dismissed as alarmist.', '后来的事件证实了董事会曾斥为危言耸听的警告。'),
  ('793fff78-0bc8-48fa-b1da-63ff67538482-ex1', '793fff78-0bc8-48fa-b1da-63ff67538482', 'continued', 'The story is continued next week.', '故事下周继续。'),
  ('793fff78-0bc8-48fa-b1da-63ff67538482-ex2', '793fff78-0bc8-48fa-b1da-63ff67538482', 'continued', 'Continued funding hinges on independently verified performance milestones.', '持续拨款取决于经独立核实的绩效节点。'),
  ('0c3e81a3-c9e8-45e5-a381-2bd280f3253a-ex1', '0c3e81a3-c9e8-45e5-a381-2bd280f3253a', 'cookie', 'Would you like a cookie?', '你想吃块饼干吗？'),
  ('0c3e81a3-c9e8-45e5-a381-2bd280f3253a-ex2', '0c3e81a3-c9e8-45e5-a381-2bd280f3253a', 'cookie', 'The privacy rules require explicit consent before non-essential cookies are set.', '隐私规则要求在设置非必要cookie之前获得明确同意。'),
  ('f9d58526-309d-4419-ae29-0b4ab4813784-ex1', 'f9d58526-309d-4419-ae29-0b4ab4813784', 'carrier', 'The carrier delivered the package.', '承运人送来了包裹。'),
  ('f9d58526-309d-4419-ae29-0b4ab4813784-ex2', 'f9d58526-309d-4419-ae29-0b4ab4813784', 'carrier', 'The carrier disclaimed liability for losses attributable to inadequate packaging.', '承运人对因包装不当造成的损失不承担责任。'),
  ('d696e091-4a8f-446f-be1b-d2573fa53eae-ex1', 'd696e091-4a8f-446f-be1b-d2573fa53eae', 'cooking', 'I enjoy cooking on weekends.', '我喜欢周末做饭。'),
  ('d696e091-4a8f-446f-be1b-d2573fa53eae-ex2', 'd696e091-4a8f-446f-be1b-d2573fa53eae', 'cooking', 'The audit revealed cooking of the books through fictitious revenue entries.', '审计揭露了通过虚构收入条目做假账的行为。'),
  ('a5df0ff6-f556-4ff2-bcc8-8f54d1d8b514-ex1', 'a5df0ff6-f556-4ff2-bcc8-8f54d1d8b514', 'frequent', 'He is a frequent visitor here.', '他是这里的常客。'),
  ('a5df0ff6-f556-4ff2-bcc8-8f54d1d8b514-ex2', 'a5df0ff6-f556-4ff2-bcc8-8f54d1d8b514', 'frequent', 'The framework mandates frequent stress testing calibrated to evolving risk.', '该框架要求根据不断变化的风险定期开展压力测试。'),
  ('7e2cc75c-346f-4b0c-954c-2b9b0f7a54cc-ex1', '7e2cc75c-346f-4b0c-954c-2b9b0f7a54cc', 'ban', 'The city placed a ban on plastic bags.', '该市颁布了塑料袋禁令。'),
  ('7e2cc75c-346f-4b0c-954c-2b9b0f7a54cc-ex2', '7e2cc75c-346f-4b0c-954c-2b9b0f7a54cc', 'ban', 'The court upheld the ban as a proportionate response to a documented harm.', '法院认定该禁令是对已记录损害的相称回应，予以维持。'),
  ('177ef430-ecff-4fc1-bef0-2f97217233aa-ex1', '177ef430-ecff-4fc1-bef0-2f97217233aa', 'awful', 'The food tasted awful.', '这食物味道糟透了。'),
  ('177ef430-ecff-4fc1-bef0-2f97217233aa-ex2', '177ef430-ecff-4fc1-bef0-2f97217233aa', 'awful', 'The inquiry documented awful conditions in the temporary holding facilities.', '调查记录了临时收容设施中恶劣的条件。'),
  ('77390d09-a479-4e43-99e3-2da1bb586b62-ex1', '77390d09-a479-4e43-99e3-2da1bb586b62', 'admire', 'I admire her courage.', '我钦佩她的勇气。'),
  ('77390d09-a479-4e43-99e3-2da1bb586b62-ex2', '77390d09-a479-4e43-99e3-2da1bb586b62', 'admire', 'Even adversaries admired the rigor with which the opinion was reasoned.', '连对手都钦佩这份判决意见说理的严谨。'),
  ('abf91ec3-b8cd-4d1b-a144-89ac0d652da0-ex1', 'abf91ec3-b8cd-4d1b-a144-89ac0d652da0', 'pet', 'Do you have any pets?', '你养宠物吗？'),
  ('abf91ec3-b8cd-4d1b-a144-89ac0d652da0-ex2', 'abf91ec3-b8cd-4d1b-a144-89ac0d652da0', 'pet', 'The ordinance regulates the keeping of pets within multi-unit residential buildings.', '该条例规范多户住宅楼内饲养宠物的行为。'),
  ('76c9948b-0844-44a5-84e4-12cde39da083-ex1', '76c9948b-0844-44a5-84e4-12cde39da083', 'miracle', 'It was a miracle no one was hurt.', '没有人受伤真是个奇迹。'),
  ('76c9948b-0844-44a5-84e4-12cde39da083-ex2', '76c9948b-0844-44a5-84e4-12cde39da083', 'miracle', 'There is no miracle cure for a crisis rooted in structural imbalance.', '对于根源在于结构性失衡的危机，并不存在奇迹般的灵药。'),
  ('b3fe46f2-7fb3-4eeb-9deb-9a3b851084da-ex1', 'b3fe46f2-7fb3-4eeb-9deb-9a3b851084da', 'exceed', 'The cost exceeded our budget.', '成本超出了我们的预算。'),
  ('b3fe46f2-7fb3-4eeb-9deb-9a3b851084da-ex2', 'b3fe46f2-7fb3-4eeb-9deb-9a3b851084da', 'exceed', 'The agency exceeded its statutory authority in promulgating the contested rule.', '该机构颁布争议规则的行为超出了其法定权限。'),
  ('f58c10d6-14ee-486f-ad0d-5fca94f14dcc-ex1', 'f58c10d6-14ee-486f-ad0d-5fca94f14dcc', 'rhythm', 'She danced to the rhythm of the music.', '她随着音乐的节奏起舞。'),
  ('f58c10d6-14ee-486f-ad0d-5fca94f14dcc-ex2', 'f58c10d6-14ee-486f-ad0d-5fca94f14dcc', 'rhythm', 'Reform proceeds at a rhythm dictated by the electoral calendar rather than need.', '改革的节奏由选举日程而非实际需要决定。'),
  ('3f7c5901-67e9-4cb6-bec5-85ba72a5169c-ex1', '3f7c5901-67e9-4cb6-bec5-85ba72a5169c', 'widespread', 'The flu was widespread that winter.', '那年冬天流感广泛流行。'),
  ('3f7c5901-67e9-4cb6-bec5-85ba72a5169c-ex2', '3f7c5901-67e9-4cb6-bec5-85ba72a5169c', 'widespread', 'The inquiry documented widespread evasion of the disclosure requirements.', '调查记录了对披露要求的普遍规避。'),
  ('ce4bfcf1-6dfb-4d61-a86e-f82fe9ad786e-ex1', 'ce4bfcf1-6dfb-4d61-a86e-f82fe9ad786e', 'killing', 'The killing shocked the community.', '这起杀人案震惊了社区。'),
  ('ce4bfcf1-6dfb-4d61-a86e-f82fe9ad786e-ex2', 'ce4bfcf1-6dfb-4d61-a86e-f82fe9ad786e', 'killing', 'The tribunal characterized the killings as crimes against humanity.', '法庭将这些杀戮认定为危害人类罪。'),
  ('bf651f0d-91a8-469d-8e14-40f57908f1fa-ex1', 'bf651f0d-91a8-469d-8e14-40f57908f1fa', 'lovely', 'What a lovely garden!', '多可爱的花园啊！'),
  ('bf651f0d-91a8-469d-8e14-40f57908f1fa-ex2', 'bf651f0d-91a8-469d-8e14-40f57908f1fa', 'lovely', 'The lovely facade masked a structure riddled with latent defects.', '漂亮的外立面掩盖了一座暗藏诸多缺陷的建筑。'),
  ('fc2cd670-8757-44e8-813f-340a6b1a7295-ex1', 'fc2cd670-8757-44e8-813f-340a6b1a7295', 'sin', 'In their faith, lying is a sin.', '在他们的信仰中，撒谎是一种罪。'),
  ('fc2cd670-8757-44e8-813f-340a6b1a7295-ex2', 'fc2cd670-8757-44e8-813f-340a6b1a7295', 'sin', 'The original sin of the framework was its reliance on industry self-regulation.', '这一框架的原罪在于它依赖行业自律。'),
  ('dfe00706-7216-42bb-9bee-d666629e47e6-ex1', 'dfe00706-7216-42bb-9bee-d666629e47e6', 'charity', 'She donates to charity every year.', '她每年都向慈善机构捐款。'),
  ('dfe00706-7216-42bb-9bee-d666629e47e6-ex2', 'dfe00706-7216-42bb-9bee-d666629e47e6', 'charity', 'The charity''s governance was overhauled after findings of financial impropriety.', '在财务不当行为被查实后，这家慈善机构的治理结构得到了彻底改革。'),
  ('bb388e03-7652-47f5-a329-93899ae57020-ex1', 'bb388e03-7652-47f5-a329-93899ae57020', 'script', 'The actor memorized the script.', '演员背熟了剧本。'),
  ('bb388e03-7652-47f5-a329-93899ae57020-ex2', 'bb388e03-7652-47f5-a329-93899ae57020', 'script', 'The witnesses appeared to follow a script of carefully rehearsed answers.', '证人们似乎在照本宣科，背诵精心排练过的答案。'),
  ('1c9c9dc4-39b9-4b4c-a5d6-8bb11c808ca2-ex1', '1c9c9dc4-39b9-4b4c-a5d6-8bb11c808ca2', 'tactic', 'That was a clever tactic.', '那是个聪明的策略。'),
  ('1c9c9dc4-39b9-4b4c-a5d6-8bb11c808ca2-ex2', '1c9c9dc4-39b9-4b4c-a5d6-8bb11c808ca2', 'tactic', 'Delay became a deliberate tactic to exhaust the claimants'' resources.', '拖延成了耗尽索赔人资源的蓄意策略。'),
  ('9c66525c-cb73-4438-b169-306e3bcfe6ad-ex1', '9c66525c-cb73-4438-b169-306e3bcfe6ad', 'identification', 'Please show some identification.', '请出示身份证件。'),
  ('9c66525c-cb73-4438-b169-306e3bcfe6ad-ex2', '9c66525c-cb73-4438-b169-306e3bcfe6ad', 'identification', 'The forensic identification of the samples proved decisive at trial.', '对样本的法证鉴定在庭审中起到了决定性作用。'),
  ('24c8d8cc-eec0-4246-8ebc-1c2c604369ad-ex1', '24c8d8cc-eec0-4246-8ebc-1c2c604369ad', 'transformation', 'The garden underwent a transformation.', '花园经历了一番改造。'),
  ('24c8d8cc-eec0-4246-8ebc-1c2c604369ad-ex2', '24c8d8cc-eec0-4246-8ebc-1c2c604369ad', 'transformation', 'The energy transformation requires grid investment on an unprecedented scale.', '能源转型需要规模空前的电网投资。'),
  ('8f0bec6a-5e3f-4192-bfe4-c1ef8213ad65-ex1', '8f0bec6a-5e3f-4192-bfe4-c1ef8213ad65', 'everyday', 'These are my everyday shoes.', '这是我平时穿的鞋。'),
  ('8f0bec6a-5e3f-4192-bfe4-c1ef8213ad65-ex2', '8f0bec6a-5e3f-4192-bfe4-c1ef8213ad65', 'everyday', 'The regulation governs everyday transactions most consumers never scrutinize.', '该法规规范大多数消费者从不细究的日常交易。'),
  ('128a520e-7bdc-4448-ab3d-4e40311acdd0-ex1', '128a520e-7bdc-4448-ab3d-4e40311acdd0', 'headline', 'The headline caught my attention.', '标题吸引了我的注意。'),
  ('128a520e-7bdc-4448-ab3d-4e40311acdd0-ex2', '128a520e-7bdc-4448-ab3d-4e40311acdd0', 'headline', 'The leaked memorandum dominated the headlines for an entire week.', '这份泄露的备忘录占据头条整整一周。'),
  ('630ad40f-efc7-44d0-a89c-9ee863b5fe56-ex1', '630ad40f-efc7-44d0-a89c-9ee863b5fe56', 'venture', 'It was a risky business venture.', '那是一次冒险的商业尝试。'),
  ('630ad40f-efc7-44d0-a89c-9ee863b5fe56-ex2', '630ad40f-efc7-44d0-a89c-9ee863b5fe56', 'venture', 'The joint venture collapsed amid disputes over technology transfer.', '这家合资企业因技术转让之争而解体。'),
  ('f5183fdc-d35d-4cec-b28e-845d13180088-ex1', 'f5183fdc-d35d-4cec-b28e-845d13180088', 'invasion', 'The invasion began at dawn.', '入侵在黎明时开始。'),
  ('f5183fdc-d35d-4cec-b28e-845d13180088-ex2', 'f5183fdc-d35d-4cec-b28e-845d13180088', 'invasion', 'The tribunal held that the incursion constituted an unlawful invasion.', '法庭裁定这次越境构成非法入侵。'),
  ('2d1eaa66-336f-4ca0-872c-e2777a68b53b-ex1', '2d1eaa66-336f-4ca0-872c-e2777a68b53b', 'nonetheless', 'It was hard; nonetheless, we finished.', '虽然很难，但我们还是完成了。'),
  ('2d1eaa66-336f-4ca0-872c-e2777a68b53b-ex2', '2d1eaa66-336f-4ca0-872c-e2777a68b53b', 'nonetheless', 'The objection was untimely; the tribunal addressed its merits nonetheless.', '该异议提出已逾期，但法庭仍审查了其实体内容。'),
  ('38ec50a5-48a9-4848-a72c-8272a48157ac-ex1', '38ec50a5-48a9-4848-a72c-8272a48157ac', 'adequate', 'Make sure you have adequate rest.', '确保你有充足的休息。'),
  ('38ec50a5-48a9-4848-a72c-8272a48157ac-ex2', '38ec50a5-48a9-4848-a72c-8272a48157ac', 'adequate', 'The safeguards proved less than adequate under correlated stress.', '事实证明，这些保障措施在关联性压力下并不充分。'),
  ('87fdbb6e-6d92-4f3c-b95e-b09955803e69-ex1', '87fdbb6e-6d92-4f3c-b95e-b09955803e69', 'piano', 'She plays the piano beautifully.', '她钢琴弹得很美。'),
  ('87fdbb6e-6d92-4f3c-b95e-b09955803e69-ex2', '87fdbb6e-6d92-4f3c-b95e-b09955803e69', 'piano', 'The estate dispute encompassed a rare piano of considerable provenance.', '这场遗产纠纷涉及一架来历非凡的稀有钢琴。'),
  ('4e8edf75-fafd-4f50-ae5f-058a5991e930-ex1', '4e8edf75-fafd-4f50-ae5f-058a5991e930', 'grocery', 'I need to buy some groceries.', '我需要买些杂货。'),
  ('4e8edf75-fafd-4f50-ae5f-058a5991e930-ex2', '4e8edf75-fafd-4f50-ae5f-058a5991e930', 'grocery', 'The merger would substantially lessen competition in the grocery sector.', '此次合并将严重削弱杂货零售行业的竞争。'),
  ('5e10bd2d-91c1-4567-8a04-86c344271b2f-ex1', '5e10bd2d-91c1-4567-8a04-86c344271b2f', 'intensity', 'The storm grew in intensity.', '暴风雨愈发猛烈。'),
  ('5e10bd2d-91c1-4567-8a04-86c344271b2f-ex2', '5e10bd2d-91c1-4567-8a04-86c344271b2f', 'intensity', 'Enforcement intensity varies widely across nominally harmonized jurisdictions.', '在名义上已统一的司法管辖区之间，执法力度差异很大。'),
  ('1bc75027-5555-40e5-8e07-aa9e2bd23f2e-ex1', '1bc75027-5555-40e5-8e07-aa9e2bd23f2e', 'exhibit', 'The museum has a new dinosaur exhibit.', '博物馆有一个新的恐龙展览。'),
  ('1bc75027-5555-40e5-8e07-aa9e2bd23f2e-ex2', '1bc75027-5555-40e5-8e07-aa9e2bd23f2e', 'exhibit', 'The transactions exhibit the hallmarks of structuring to evade reporting.', '这些交易呈现出为规避申报而进行结构化操作的特征。'),
  ('ee925d93-4a6f-4d97-9cec-2c2040b5cba0-ex1', 'ee925d93-4a6f-4d97-9cec-2c2040b5cba0', 'blanket', 'Wrap the baby in a warm blanket.', '用暖和的毯子把宝宝裹好。'),
  ('ee925d93-4a6f-4d97-9cec-2c2040b5cba0-ex2', 'ee925d93-4a6f-4d97-9cec-2c2040b5cba0', 'blanket', 'The court refused to impose a blanket ban without case-by-case assessment.', '法院拒绝在没有逐案评估的情况下实施全面禁令。'),
  ('42ac4bc8-7b89-4c01-96ad-4bec9b80a4cb-ex1', '42ac4bc8-7b89-4c01-96ad-4bec9b80a4cb', 'margin', 'Leave a margin on the left of the page.', '在页面左边留出空白。'),
  ('42ac4bc8-7b89-4c01-96ad-4bec9b80a4cb-ex2', '42ac4bc8-7b89-4c01-96ad-4bec9b80a4cb', 'margin', 'Rising input costs compressed margins across even efficient producers.', '投入成本上升压缩了即使是高效生产商的利润率。'),
  ('475b6d84-e294-438a-80cd-2304c6bde890-ex1', '475b6d84-e294-438a-80cd-2304c6bde890', 'quarterback', 'The quarterback threw a long pass.', '四分卫传出了一记长传。'),
  ('475b6d84-e294-438a-80cd-2304c6bde890-ex2', '475b6d84-e294-438a-80cd-2304c6bde890', 'quarterback', 'She quarterbacked the negotiations that salvaged the multilateral accord.', '她主导了挽救多边协定的谈判。'),
  ('e3231807-c575-47c8-94ae-4745e01dc9ff-ex1', 'e3231807-c575-47c8-94ae-4745e01dc9ff', 'mouse', 'The cat chased the mouse.', '猫追着老鼠跑。'),
  ('e3231807-c575-47c8-94ae-4745e01dc9ff-ex2', 'e3231807-c575-47c8-94ae-4745e01dc9ff', 'mouse', 'A single click of the mouse may suffice to form a binding contract.', '鼠标轻轻一点就可能构成有约束力的合同。'),
  ('746aea92-1b0e-4f4b-8ec1-6832ce73cf71-ex1', '746aea92-1b0e-4f4b-8ec1-6832ce73cf71', 'rope', 'Tie the boat with this rope.', '用这条绳子系住船。'),
  ('746aea92-1b0e-4f4b-8ec1-6832ce73cf71-ex2', '746aea92-1b0e-4f4b-8ec1-6832ce73cf71', 'rope', 'The struggling lender was given more rope before the supervisor intervened.', '在监管者介入之前，这家陷入困境的贷款机构获得了更多回旋余地。'),
  ('0f269e39-5523-413c-aa94-f11f06085536-ex1', '0f269e39-5523-413c-aa94-f11f06085536', 'concrete', 'The path is made of concrete.', '这条小路是混凝土铺的。'),
  ('0f269e39-5523-413c-aa94-f11f06085536-ex2', '0f269e39-5523-413c-aa94-f11f06085536', 'concrete', 'The pledge lacked any concrete commitments capable of being verified.', '这一承诺缺乏任何可供核查的具体保证。'),
  ('840aba62-6539-4233-ac6e-c99c9f68f650-ex1', '840aba62-6539-4233-ac6e-c99c9f68f650', 'prescription', 'The doctor wrote me a prescription.', '医生给我开了处方。'),
  ('840aba62-6539-4233-ac6e-c99c9f68f650-ex2', '840aba62-6539-4233-ac6e-c99c9f68f650', 'prescription', 'The protocol requires clinical authority to countersign every prescription amendment.', '该规程要求由临床权限人员对每处处方修改进行会签。'),
  ('c855a0f4-ce74-48e5-953c-27745e4c72e5-ex1', 'c855a0f4-ce74-48e5-953c-27745e4c72e5', 'African-American', 'The exhibit honors African-American inventors.', '这个展览纪念非裔美国发明家。'),
  ('c855a0f4-ce74-48e5-953c-27745e4c72e5-ex2', 'c855a0f4-ce74-48e5-953c-27745e4c72e5', 'African-American', 'The study documents persistent disparities affecting African-American applicants.', '该研究记录了影响非裔美国申请人的长期差距。'),
  ('5ecdcb29-8b45-4760-8a79-16267266be05-ex1', '5ecdcb29-8b45-4760-8a79-16267266be05', 'chase', 'The dog likes to chase its tail.', '这只狗喜欢追自己的尾巴。'),
  ('5ecdcb29-8b45-4760-8a79-16267266be05-ex2', '5ecdcb29-8b45-4760-8a79-16267266be05', 'chase', 'Investors who chase yield often overlook the embedded credit risk.', '追逐收益的投资者往往忽视其中蕴含的信用风险。'),
  ('9a6a2dc9-97af-4105-88aa-f705829b41f8-ex1', '9a6a2dc9-97af-4105-88aa-f705829b41f8', 'brick', 'The house is made of red brick.', '这栋房子是用红砖砌的。'),
  ('9a6a2dc9-97af-4105-88aa-f705829b41f8-ex2', '9a6a2dc9-97af-4105-88aa-f705829b41f8', 'brick', 'The reforms were built brick by brick over a decade of patient negotiation.', '这些改革是在十年的耐心谈判中一砖一瓦建立起来的。'),
  ('3715b126-5848-446a-b9bc-6f6aba612f8a-ex1', '3715b126-5848-446a-b9bc-6f6aba612f8a', 'recruit', 'The team needs to recruit new players.', '球队需要招募新球员。'),
  ('3715b126-5848-446a-b9bc-6f6aba612f8a-ex2', '3715b126-5848-446a-b9bc-6f6aba612f8a', 'recruit', 'The program recruits accomplished professionals to teach in understaffed schools.', '该项目招募资深专业人士到师资匮乏的学校任教。'),
  ('39c63b95-fd88-4152-af56-bd790b48f3f6-ex1', '39c63b95-fd88-4152-af56-bd790b48f3f6', 'patch', 'He sewed a patch on his jeans.', '他在牛仔裤上缝了块补丁。'),
  ('39c63b95-fd88-4152-af56-bd790b48f3f6-ex2', '39c63b95-fd88-4152-af56-bd790b48f3f6', 'patch', 'The security patch addressed a vulnerability already exploited in the wild.', '该安全补丁修复了一个已在实际中被利用的漏洞。'),
  ('c676b085-7609-4081-ac6c-02c73b06355c-ex1', 'c676b085-7609-4081-ac6c-02c73b06355c', 'consensus', 'We reached a consensus quickly.', '我们很快达成了共识。'),
  ('c676b085-7609-4081-ac6c-02c73b06355c-ex2', 'c676b085-7609-4081-ac6c-02c73b06355c', 'consensus', 'A scientific consensus emerged only after replicated independent studies.', '科学共识在经过重复的独立研究之后才形成。'),
  ('a7c53f5b-5d6e-426f-8a60-434b824608e4-ex1', 'a7c53f5b-5d6e-426f-8a60-434b824608e4', 'horror', 'She watched the scene in horror.', '她惊恐地看着那一幕。'),
  ('a7c53f5b-5d6e-426f-8a60-434b824608e4-ex2', 'a7c53f5b-5d6e-426f-8a60-434b824608e4', 'horror', 'The commission documented the horrors inflicted upon the detained population.', '委员会记录了被拘留人群所遭受的种种暴行。'),
  ('ad3b8d97-2f0a-427c-be84-ff9f2db6fd2c-ex1', 'ad3b8d97-2f0a-427c-be84-ff9f2db6fd2c', 'recording', 'I made a recording of the lecture.', '我录下了那场讲座。'),
  ('ad3b8d97-2f0a-427c-be84-ff9f2db6fd2c-ex2', 'ad3b8d97-2f0a-427c-be84-ff9f2db6fd2c', 'recording', 'The covert recording was excluded as evidence obtained without authorization.', '这段秘密录音因未经授权获取而被排除作为证据。'),
  ('b54985e7-511d-47ab-897d-9f1de5e32a9b-ex1', 'b54985e7-511d-47ab-897d-9f1de5e32a9b', 'changing', 'The changing seasons bring different weather.', '季节更替带来不同的天气。'),
  ('b54985e7-511d-47ab-897d-9f1de5e32a9b-ex2', 'b54985e7-511d-47ab-897d-9f1de5e32a9b', 'changing', 'Regulators struggle to keep pace with the changing architecture of finance.', '监管者难以跟上不断变化的金融架构。'),
  ('9bb3afc5-3219-41cf-a61b-4f9bf8c27902-ex1', '9bb3afc5-3219-41cf-a61b-4f9bf8c27902', 'painter', 'The painter mixed his colors carefully.', '画家仔细调配颜料。'),
  ('9bb3afc5-3219-41cf-a61b-4f9bf8c27902-ex2', '9bb3afc5-3219-41cf-a61b-4f9bf8c27902', 'painter', 'The painter''s estate disputed the unauthorized reproduction of her work.', '这位画家的遗产管理方对其作品被擅自复制提出异议。'),
  ('c7d275f2-f34f-44a8-95bb-859f014526f1-ex1', 'c7d275f2-f34f-44a8-95bb-859f014526f1', 'colonial', 'The town has colonial-era buildings.', '这个镇有殖民时期的建筑。'),
  ('c7d275f2-f34f-44a8-95bb-859f014526f1-ex2', 'c7d275f2-f34f-44a8-95bb-859f014526f1', 'colonial', 'The dispute concerns artifacts removed under colonial-era circumstances.', '这场争议涉及在殖民时期被移走的文物。'),
  ('dcc3bd8f-87d1-4b51-9237-d4174b790f0f-ex1', 'dcc3bd8f-87d1-4b51-9237-d4174b790f0f', 'pie', 'She baked an apple pie.', '她烤了一个苹果派。'),
  ('dcc3bd8f-87d1-4b51-9237-d4174b790f0f-ex2', 'dcc3bd8f-87d1-4b51-9237-d4174b790f0f', 'pie', 'Each faction sought a larger slice of a shrinking fiscal pie.', '各派系都想从不断缩水的财政蛋糕中分得更大一块。'),
  ('5144654c-18c4-4148-944c-5b89382cf13e-ex1', '5144654c-18c4-4148-944c-5b89382cf13e', 'sake', 'For your own sake, get some rest.', '为了你自己，去休息一下吧。'),
