  ('230bebe3-a36b-4b35-b40f-70855be45147-ex1', '230bebe3-a36b-4b35-b40f-70855be45147', 'pregnancy', 'She is in the early stages of pregnancy.', '她正处于怀孕初期。'),
  ('230bebe3-a36b-4b35-b40f-70855be45147-ex2', '230bebe3-a36b-4b35-b40f-70855be45147', 'pregnancy', 'The statute prohibits dismissal for reasons connected with pregnancy.', '该法规禁止以与怀孕有关的理由解雇员工。'),
  ('ae6b7bc5-3e19-4b7c-92e6-3caa1dced28b-ex1', 'ae6b7bc5-3e19-4b7c-92e6-3caa1dced28b', 'swear', 'I swear I locked the door.', '我发誓我锁门了。'),
  ('ae6b7bc5-3e19-4b7c-92e6-3caa1dced28b-ex2', 'ae6b7bc5-3e19-4b7c-92e6-3caa1dced28b', 'swear', 'Witnesses must swear to tell the truth before giving testimony.', '证人在作证前必须宣誓如实陈述。'),
  ('60c3220d-02a2-4641-b478-244bc0d03c64-ex1', '60c3220d-02a2-4641-b478-244bc0d03c64', 'defeat', 'The team accepted the defeat gracefully.', '球队大度地接受了失败。'),
  ('60c3220d-02a2-4641-b478-244bc0d03c64-ex2', '60c3220d-02a2-4641-b478-244bc0d03c64', 'defeat', 'The amendment''s defeat reflected entrenched opposition rather than fiscal concern.', '修正案被否决反映的是根深蒂固的反对，而非财政上的顾虑。'),
  ('0f51aa8d-96b5-438c-a643-8c5e88787380-ex1', '0f51aa8d-96b5-438c-a643-8c5e88787380', 'clue', 'The detective found an important clue.', '侦探找到了一条重要线索。'),
  ('0f51aa8d-96b5-438c-a643-8c5e88787380-ex2', '0f51aa8d-96b5-438c-a643-8c5e88787380', 'clue', 'The documentary trail provided the clue investigators had long sought.', '文件线索提供了调查人员长期寻找的关键线索。'),
  ('4fa3c5e4-d2ea-43c1-b64f-e4a1ce5f7aee-ex1', '4fa3c5e4-d2ea-43c1-b64f-e4a1ce5f7aee', 'reinforce', 'They reinforced the bridge with steel.', '他们用钢材加固了桥梁。'),
