  ('557fdff3-6e82-423e-b779-ae7ca52b2f2d-ex1', '557fdff3-6e82-423e-b779-ae7ca52b2f2d', 'dear', 'She is a dear friend of mine.', '她是我的一位挚友。'),
  ('557fdff3-6e82-423e-b779-ae7ca52b2f2d-ex2', '557fdff3-6e82-423e-b779-ae7ca52b2f2d', 'dear', 'Delayed remediation proved dear, far exceeding the cost of timely compliance.', '事实证明，延迟整改代价高昂，远超及时合规的成本。'),
  ('33fd4ad9-3252-4bbd-bcdb-cd0fb2b895cb-ex1', '33fd4ad9-3252-4bbd-bcdb-cd0fb2b895cb', 'coal', 'The factory still burns coal.', '这家工厂仍在烧煤。'),
  ('33fd4ad9-3252-4bbd-bcdb-cd0fb2b895cb-ex2', '33fd4ad9-3252-4bbd-bcdb-cd0fb2b895cb', 'coal', 'The phase-out of coal generation demands a credible transition for affected workers.', '逐步淘汰燃煤发电需要为受影响的工人提供可信的转型安排。'),
  ('f18119ba-aebd-4842-a35d-b0683ec636a7-ex1', 'f18119ba-aebd-4842-a35d-b0683ec636a7', 'sacred', 'The temple is a sacred place.', '这座庙宇是一处圣地。'),
  ('f18119ba-aebd-4842-a35d-b0683ec636a7-ex2', 'f18119ba-aebd-4842-a35d-b0683ec636a7', 'sacred', 'Access to the sacred sites is governed by a delicate status quo arrangement.', '圣地的进入由一项微妙的现状安排所规范。'),
