  ('1159b852-d803-45be-a326-2f7531a54927-ex2', '1159b852-d803-45be-a326-2f7531a54927', 'formula', 'Benefits are uprated under the statutory indexation formula each year.', '福利金每年按法定指数化公式上调。'),
  ('7a7f7dc9-ac7a-4569-b298-aa9ad8230579-ex1', '7a7f7dc9-ac7a-4569-b298-aa9ad8230579', 'cognitive', 'Puzzles improve cognitive skills.', '益智游戏能提升认知能力。'),
  ('7a7f7dc9-ac7a-4569-b298-aa9ad8230579-ex2', '7a7f7dc9-ac7a-4569-b298-aa9ad8230579', 'cognitive', 'Chronic exposure measurably impairs cognitive and regulatory function.', '长期接触会显著损害认知和调节功能。'),
