  ('a6ef3479-696e-4abc-a93d-cc9c318690c4-ex2', 'a6ef3479-696e-4abc-a93d-cc9c318690c4', 'collective', 'The statute protects the collective bargaining rights of all workers.', '该法规保护所有劳动者的集体谈判权。'),
