  ('60b67f6e-e512-49b8-bfda-bc5b9532d044-ex1', '60b67f6e-e512-49b8-bfda-bc5b9532d044', 'captain', 'The captain steered the ship safely.', '船长安全地驾驶着船。'),
  ('60b67f6e-e512-49b8-bfda-bc5b9532d044-ex2', '60b67f6e-e512-49b8-bfda-bc5b9532d044', 'captain', 'The captain bears ultimate responsibility for the vessel''s compliance with the rules.', '船长对船舶遵守规则负有最终责任。'),
  ('32e50547-8e5f-4885-93ec-4a63a0d64840-ex1', '32e50547-8e5f-4885-93ec-4a63a0d64840', 'sigh', 'She let out a tired sigh.', '她疲惫地叹了口气。'),
