  ('ab81a054-f89e-48f7-bf9c-d6797488d45e-ex2', 'ab81a054-f89e-48f7-bf9c-d6797488d45e', 'lap', 'The final lap of the negotiations addressed the contentious enforcement annex.', '谈判的最后一程处理了争议性的执行附件。'),
