  ('9461278c-64fd-442d-a513-feaf7b5c781d-ex2', '9461278c-64fd-442d-a513-feaf7b5c781d', 'container', 'Customs inspected every container for undeclared contraband.', '海关检查了每一个集装箱，查找未申报的违禁品。'),
