  ('4675ebac-3151-4d8a-acec-e0f84e401a62-ex2', '4675ebac-3151-4d8a-acec-e0f84e401a62', 'abroad', 'The screening regime scrutinizes assets relocated abroad for tax motives.', '该审查制度审查为税务目的而转移至海外的资产。'),
