  ('75aef74a-5239-4108-a53e-753992723ab5-ex2', '75aef74a-5239-4108-a53e-753992723ab5', 'architect', 'He is regarded as the principal architect of the postwar settlement.', '他被视为战后体制的主要缔造者。'),
  ('d6abb28e-eeb9-4166-a3ba-4a43ea51ba2e-ex1', 'd6abb28e-eeb9-4166-a3ba-4a43ea51ba2e', 'dramatically', 'Prices rose dramatically last month.', '上个月物价急剧上涨。'),
