  ('4449493b-1336-4689-90f4-96fa8105205c-ex1', '4449493b-1336-4689-90f4-96fa8105205c', 'makeup', 'She wears very little makeup.', '她几乎不化妆。'),
  ('4449493b-1336-4689-90f4-96fa8105205c-ex2', '4449493b-1336-4689-90f4-96fa8105205c', 'makeup', 'The makeup of the panel was challenged for apparent bias.', '专家组的人员构成因明显偏袒而受到质疑。'),
