  ('88d40063-8164-4ddf-a75d-43254aae86f3-ex2', '88d40063-8164-4ddf-a75d-43254aae86f3', 'alliance', 'The alliance committed members to mutual defense upon armed attack.', '该联盟要求成员在遭受武装攻击时履行共同防御义务。'),
